    1265,
    'https://us02web.zoom.us/j/81421883896?pwd=9iHNOeWOt9gp3Uqm9ajWXxGhOvoFVO.1',
    '{"id":"01KE5AQ6Y89WCYW7ZV5DZ603Y6","title":"BioSAFE Weekly Meeting","summary":{"notes":"## **Marketing Automation and Notification Cleanup**\n\nThe team identified and prioritized fixing the excessive email notifications caused by outdated automation in HubSpot.\n\n- **Dan Nelsen reported receiving over 100 erroneous ABM campaign emails daily** due to old automation still running despite no recent campaign launches (01:31).  \n    - Baylee Gunnell confirmed this is likely residual automation from about two years ago and committed to investigate immediately after the call.  \n    - The automation was originally set to notify K. Ross, who has now been removed from the HubSpot account to stop further notifications.  \n    - Baylee disabled the problematic automation before the meeting ended, ensuring Dan should no longer receive these emails.  \n    - This cleanup will restore Dan’s ability to turn mail notifications back on, improving his workflow and reducing distractions.\n\n- **Taylor Doerbaum and Baylee will monitor any further faulty notifications** and requested Dan forward any future erroneous emails for quick resolution (18:54).  \n    - This proactive approach aims to maintain clean, relevant communication streams linked to active campaigns.  \n    - Resolving these notification issues supports better engagement tracking and follow-up by the marketing team.  \n\n## **Website Content and Visual Updates**\n\nThe website update process is progressing with key copy and visual assets being finalized and integrated.\n\n- **Dan provided updated copy for the services product tab, covering five sections, delivered earlier that day for immediate integration** (05:13).  \n    - Taylor confirmed headings are ready and the team will add the new copy into Bug Herd for review.  \n    - Dan requested generally stock photos to fill out the page visually, which will be sourced accordingly.  \n    - Once the service validation copy is fully integrated, Dan’s team will conduct a final review to catch any last edits or issues (15:29).\n\n- **The poster artwork required formatting and content tweaks focusing on the features column and text alignment** (07:04).  \n    - Dan identified inconsistencies in justification across feature items and requested uniform formatting for a polished appearance (08:33).  \n    - The team agreed to provide both a high-resolution and a compressed low-resolution version of the updated poster for versatile use (08:54).  \n    - These updates will align marketing collateral with the latest branding and product messaging.\n\n- **Outstanding image assets remain for three website sections: wet vs. dry discharge, thermic vs. stick agitators, and building integrated vs. standalone digesters** (10:46).  \n    - Dan will supply photos clarifying inside agitator differences and visual examples of discharge types to enhance user understanding (11:31).  \n    - For building integration visuals, Dan explained the concept of digesters sunk into floors moving waste from hot to cold zones within facilities, and promised to provide related images (13:42).  \n    - These images are the last blocking items before the website updates can be fully implemented (20:03).\n\n## **Marketing Collateral Consistency and Data Accuracy**\n\nA focus on ensuring all marketing materials use consistent, up-to-date data to maintain credibility and clarity.\n\n- **Dan flagged outdated cost figures on carousel ads and requested updated numbers be checked and applied across all marketing assets** (16:48).  \n    - Taylor committed to verifying the source of existing numbers on the website and replacing them with Dan’s more current, defensible data sets (17:44).  \n    - This effort aims to prevent discrepancies that confuse potential customers or weaken the company’s value proposition.  \n    - Dan plans to review remaining ads in the carousel and send further comments as needed to maintain accuracy (18:19).\n\n- **Taylor confirmed ongoing coordination to ensure that all web and ad content reflects the latest validated data and messaging** (19:33).  \n    - This alignment will help unify the company’s public-facing materials and reduce risks of outdated or conflicting information.\n\n## **Process and Communication Improvements**\n\nThe discussion revealed areas for improving internal workflows and communication clarity.\n\n- **Dan emphasized the importance of centralized, updated collateral to avoid multiple versions causing confusion or misplacement** (20:22).  \n    - Taylor agreed to audit and update all relevant links and files to ensure only the newest poster and website content are accessible.  \n    - This reduces the risk of team members or Dan himself accidentally using outdated materials in presentations or client outreach.\n\n- **The team reinforced clear ownership and timely follow-up on deliverables, with Taylor leading updates in Bug Herd and Dan providing final media assets soon** (20:50).  \n    - This structured approach supports efficient iteration and quality control before public release.  \n    - Baylee and Taylor’s close collaboration on technical cleanup and content updates demonstrates improved coordination across marketing and operations teams.","outline":null,"keywords":["HubSpot Automation","Website Updates","Poster Design","ABM Campaign","Carousel Ads","Image Assets"],"overview":"- **Email Notification Cleanup:** Excessive erroneous emails were fixed; problematic automation disabled to improve Dan''s workflow.  \n- **Website Content Updates:** Updated copy for services section integrated; stock photos to be sourced to enhance visual appeal.  \n- **Poster Artwork Adjustments:** Inconsistencies resolved; both high and low-resolution versions to be provided for marketing use.  \n- **Image Assets Remaining:** Final images needed for key website sections before updates can be fully implemented.  \n- **Marketing Data Accuracy:** Outdated cost figures will be updated to maintain credibility and consistency across all marketing materials.  \n- **Internal Workflow Improvements:** Centralized collateral and clear ownership established to reduce confusion and enhance communication efficiency.","action_items":"\n**Dan Nelsen**\nForward representative emails of the erroneous HubSpot notifications to Baylee and Taylor for troubleshooting (01:30)\nProvide photos illustrating the internal difference between thermic and stick agitators for website image inclusion (12:00)\nLocate and send images showing “wet versus dry discharge” and “building integrated versus standalone” system layouts, including through-floor digesters (13:30)\nHave team conduct a final review of the new service/product tab copy once it is incorporated into Bug Herd and notify marketing of any further comments (15:40)\nSend updated treatment cost figures and confirm data sources in the carousel ads and website for consistency (16:45)\nContinue reviewing remaining carousel ads and provide additional feedback in due course (18:20)\nEnsure there is a single, updated version of the SVG poster shared among all teams (20:30)\n\n**Taylor Doerbaum**\nReview and clarify source of treatment cost numbers on carousel ads and website, then update materials with Dan’s provided figures (17:00)\nImplement requested copy changes and formatting fixes on the poster, producing both high-res and compressed versions for Dan’s use (08:55)\nCoordinate integration of new service/product tab copy in Bug Herd and notify Dan when ready for team review (15:25)\nWork on requested updates and ensure image placements as soon as Dan supplies photos (10:30)\nCommunicate with Dan to confirm resolution of HubSpot automation and stop of excessive email notifications (19:00)\nSend Dan updated pages via Bug Herd as they are completed (19:40)\n\n**Baylee Gunnell**\nInvestigate and disable old HubSpot automation triggering excessive ABM campaign emails; remove K. Ross user from HubSpot to prevent future alerts (02:00)\nNotify Dan when automation is successfully turned off to stop unwanted emails (19:00)\nAssist Taylor with coordination and follow-up for website and HubSpot notification issues (00:00)\n"},"duration":21.079999923706055,"speakers":[{"id":0,"name":"Dan Nelsen"},{"id":1,"name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"id":2,"name":"Baylee Gunnell"}],"sentences":[{"text":"Years.","index":0,"end_time":0.4,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":0.16,"speaker_name":"Dan Nelsen"},{"text":"Good.","index":1,"end_time":1.36,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":0.96,"speaker_name":"Dan Nelsen"},{"text":"Yeah, well, sort of good.","index":2,"end_time":3.04,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1.44,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"We all got sick over here, so it was.","index":3,"end_time":5.2,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":3.12,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Oh no, the best.","index":4,"end_time":6.32,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":5.2,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Still recovering but.","index":5,"end_time":8.64,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":7.36,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"But the time off was nice.","index":6,"end_time":11.04,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":9.6,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Good.","index":7,"end_time":12.16,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":11.76,"speaker_name":"Dan Nelsen"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":8,"end_time":12.6,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":12.24,"speaker_name":"Dan Nelsen"},{"text":"That''s tough.","index":9,"end_time":13.2,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":12.6,"speaker_name":"Dan Nelsen"},{"text":"Well, good.","index":10,"end_time":13.8,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":13.36,"speaker_name":"Dan Nelsen"},{"text":"I''m glad you had a nice holiday.","index":11,"end_time":15.04,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":13.8,"speaker_name":"Dan Nelsen"},{"text":"Yes.","index":12,"end_time":16.399,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":15.84,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"So I see that you''re sending a couple different things in from just Deliverables over the past couple months.","index":13,"end_time":24.56,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":18.4,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Was there.","index":14,"end_time":25.44,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":24.88,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"I didn''t get a chance to look at all your STI comments for the LinkedIn carousel yet, but was there something in particular you wanted to focus on for our meeting today?","index":15,"end_time":32.94,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":25.44,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"The website maybe.","index":16,"end_time":33.98,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":32.94,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Kind of going on website was the main piece.","index":17,"end_time":37.22,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":34.06,"speaker_name":"Dan Nelsen"},{"text":"I wanted to talk a little bit through the ABM campaign that''s going now and just have you kind of talk me through what I''m seeing on HubSpot.","index":18,"end_time":46.3,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":37.22,"speaker_name":"Dan Nelsen"},{"text":"We.","index":19,"end_time":48.38,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":47.98,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"The.","index":20,"end_time":48.74,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":48.38,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"So we didn''t launch the ABM campaign yet.","index":21,"end_time":50.54,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":48.74,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"That was the Life Sciences one that we''re hoping to launch that has that.","index":22,"end_time":55.74,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":50.54,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Okay.","index":23,"end_time":56.78,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":56.54,"speaker_name":"Dan Nelsen"},{"text":"So I. I wanted to ask what am I.","index":24,"end_time":58.3,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":56.78,"speaker_name":"Dan Nelsen"},{"text":"So I''m getting like a hundred emails a day plus through HubSpot tagged ABM Campaign.","index":25,"end_time":66.3,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":58.38,"speaker_name":"Dan Nelsen"},{"text":"So I think something''s not set up.","index":26,"end_time":70.1,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":67.66,"speaker_name":"Dan Nelsen"},{"text":"Right.","index":27,"end_time":70.3,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":70.1,"speaker_name":"Dan Nelsen"},{"text":"And when I go in, I''m seeing a weird.","index":28,"end_time":72.14,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":70.3,"speaker_name":"Dan Nelsen"},{"text":"There was an issue sending an email to this contact message and I''d been getting notes nominally from you guys saying, hey, highly suggest following up on these guys.","index":29,"end_time":83.38,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":72.54,"speaker_name":"Dan Nelsen"},{"text":"Is that a new just notification from an old.","index":30,"end_time":87.21,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":83.38,"speaker_name":"Dan Nelsen"},{"text":"From a previous ABM campaign that we''ve been looking at.","index":31,"end_time":89.93,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":87.21,"speaker_name":"Dan Nelsen"},{"text":"What''s kind of driving that?","index":32,"end_time":91.33,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":89.93,"speaker_name":"Dan Nelsen"},{"text":"Can you forward us the emails you''re getting?","index":33,"end_time":94.13,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":91.81,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"I don''t see anything.","index":34,"end_time":96.29,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":95.17,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Yeah, because we haven''t set anything up recently, so maybe it''s an old thing or it could be, I don''t know.","index":35,"end_time":103.57,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":96.29,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":36,"end_time":105.57,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":105.17,"speaker_name":"Dan Nelsen"},{"text":"So here''s one.","index":37,"end_time":106.53,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":105.57,"speaker_name":"Dan Nelsen"},{"text":"I''m getting 40 of them, 100 of them like every two hours.","index":38,"end_time":112.37,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":106.61,"speaker_name":"Dan Nelsen"},{"text":"You just forwarded one.","index":39,"end_time":116.68,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":115.4,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":40,"end_time":117.16,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":116.68,"speaker_name":"Dan Nelsen"},{"text":"And this has been going.","index":41,"end_time":128.52,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":127.16,"speaker_name":"Dan Nelsen"},{"text":"Been going for a bit now.","index":42,"end_time":130.04,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":128.68,"speaker_name":"Dan Nelsen"},{"text":"I kind of put it to the back of my mind during the holiday period, but then as it was, you know, I figured I''d chat through it with you guys.","index":43,"end_time":139.72,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":130.04,"speaker_name":"Dan Nelsen"},{"text":"But I''m getting a couple hundred of these emails a day.","index":44,"end_time":144.03,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":140.11,"speaker_name":"Dan Nelsen"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":45,"end_time":145.27,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":144.91,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"This might be just some old automation.","index":46,"end_time":148.11,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":145.27,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"We''ve been cleaning up a lot of things, so maybe just something slipped through the cracks because we didn''t launch anything new in the last few weeks.","index":47,"end_time":156.51,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":148.99,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":48,"end_time":157.31,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":156.91,"speaker_name":"Dan Nelsen"},{"text":"And here, let me drop this into the chat so you can see this.","index":49,"end_time":161.47,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":157.31,"speaker_name":"Dan Nelsen"},{"text":"Why.","index":50,"end_time":163.87,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":163.47,"speaker_name":"Dan Nelsen"},{"text":"Why do I. Admin restrictions aren''t letting me share a file.","index":51,"end_time":168.55,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":163.87,"speaker_name":"Dan Nelsen"},{"text":"So I''ll just send it via email.","index":52,"end_time":169.87,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":168.55,"speaker_name":"Dan Nelsen"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":53,"end_time":175.16,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":174.96,"speaker_name":"Dan Nelsen"},{"text":"And then when I go into HubSpot to look at what is driving this.","index":54,"end_time":186.24,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":175.16,"speaker_name":"Dan Nelsen"},{"text":"This is kind of what I see.","index":55,"end_time":188,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":186.4,"speaker_name":"Dan Nelsen"},{"text":"Which is also weird because K''s.","index":56,"end_time":192.28,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":189.12,"speaker_name":"Dan Nelsen"},{"text":"I''m curious why K''s login is showing as having dropped notes on all of these.","index":57,"end_time":197.68,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":192.28,"speaker_name":"Dan Nelsen"},{"text":"Yeah, there''s honestly probably just some automation in the back end that needs to be cleaned up.","index":58,"end_time":222.31,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":216.87,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"That.","index":59,"end_time":223.19,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":222.87,"speaker_name":"Dan Nelsen"},{"text":"That should be a pretty simple fix.","index":60,"end_time":224.87,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":223.19,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"Cool.","index":61,"end_time":225.98,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":225.66,"speaker_name":"Dan Nelsen"},{"text":"That would be great.","index":62,"end_time":227.42,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":226.46,"speaker_name":"Dan Nelsen"},{"text":"Obviously sooner the better would be preferred because I''ve got.","index":63,"end_time":232.22,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":227.5,"speaker_name":"Dan Nelsen"},{"text":"I just.","index":64,"end_time":234.02,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":233.5,"speaker_name":"Dan Nelsen"},{"text":"I would like to be able to turn my mail notifications back on.","index":65,"end_time":237.42,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":234.02,"speaker_name":"Dan Nelsen"},{"text":"Yes.","index":66,"end_time":238.22,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":237.74,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"Yep.","index":67,"end_time":240.3,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":239.74,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"I''ll look into it after the call, see what''s going on there.","index":68,"end_time":243.42,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":240.38,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"Thank you.","index":69,"end_time":244.7,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":244.06,"speaker_name":"Dan Nelsen"},{"text":"As far as the website specifics, do you want me to pull up Bug Herd?","index":70,"end_time":257.23,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":253.83,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Do you want to pull up Bug Hurt on your end and explain a couple of the new things you just sent over via email?","index":71,"end_time":261.67,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":257.23,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Why don''t you drive Bugh Herd?","index":72,"end_time":265.35,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":263.43,"speaker_name":"Dan Nelsen"},{"text":"I think I''ve got.","index":73,"end_time":267.67,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":266.15,"speaker_name":"Dan Nelsen"},{"text":"And I can have those kind of pieces up on my side and be talking to them.","index":74,"end_time":273.67,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":269.59,"speaker_name":"Dan Nelsen"},{"text":"Cool.","index":75,"end_time":287.2,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":286.96,"speaker_name":"Dan Nelsen"},{"text":"So I think there are two or a couple pieces here.","index":76,"end_time":291.04,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":287.2,"speaker_name":"Dan Nelsen"},{"text":"So the first is the copy for kind of the services product tab.","index":77,"end_time":295.36,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":291.04,"speaker_name":"Dan Nelsen"},{"text":"Which.","index":78,"end_time":299.36,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":298.96,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Where are you for this page?","index":79,"end_time":306.56,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":302.08,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Yes.","index":80,"end_time":310.72,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":310.24,"speaker_name":"Dan Nelsen"},{"text":"Okay.","index":81,"end_time":312,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":311.36,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"I said that''s a Word document that came over a little bit earlier today.","index":82,"end_time":319.12,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":313.28,"speaker_name":"Dan Nelsen"},{"text":"That should have all of the copy for those three sections.","index":83,"end_time":322.24,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":319.12,"speaker_name":"Dan Nelsen"},{"text":"Okay.","index":84,"end_time":323.52,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":322.96,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"That was the 1212 email.","index":85,"end_time":334.01,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":331.69,"speaker_name":"Dan Nelsen"},{"text":"Okay.","index":86,"end_time":352.99,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":335.77,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Okay, I see that here.","index":87,"end_time":362.58,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":361.54,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"So there''ll be five sections for this page.","index":88,"end_time":378.34,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":376.26,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":89,"end_time":379.85,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":379.45,"speaker_name":"Dan Nelsen"},{"text":"Okay.","index":90,"end_time":380.81,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":380.25,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"Yep.","index":91,"end_time":382.21,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":381.77,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"We have the headings ready to go so we can add that in here.","index":92,"end_time":385.45,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":382.21,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Perfect.","index":93,"end_time":389.69,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":389.05,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"And these should all be fun for kind of generally stock photos to fill out the page.","index":94,"end_time":399.61,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":391.77,"speaker_name":"Dan Nelsen"},{"text":"Okay, good.","index":95,"end_time":404.58,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":400.81,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"And then I think you sent like a couple of.","index":96,"end_time":417.7,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":415.86,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":97,"end_time":419.22,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":418.9,"speaker_name":"Dan Nelsen"},{"text":"So this is for the poster.","index":98,"end_time":422.1,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":419.22,"speaker_name":"Dan Nelsen"},{"text":"Okay.","index":99,"end_time":423.62,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":422.98,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"So I think a while ago there was a version confusion on the poster.","index":100,"end_time":432.82,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":424.26,"speaker_name":"Dan Nelsen"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":101,"end_time":435.38,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":434.9,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"So that was.","index":102,"end_time":436.66,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":435.46,"speaker_name":"Dan Nelsen"},{"text":"I believe that is the correct one.","index":103,"end_time":438.66,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":436.74,"speaker_name":"Dan Nelsen"},{"text":"It''s the high res version.","index":104,"end_time":440.02,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":438.66,"speaker_name":"Dan Nelsen"},{"text":"It has the 150 on it.","index":105,"end_time":441.78,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":440.02,"speaker_name":"Dan Nelsen"},{"text":"You''ll note if you go look under features, I think the second item has text placeholder under it.","index":106,"end_time":450.82,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":443.38,"speaker_name":"Dan Nelsen"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":107,"end_time":451.54,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":450.9,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"So that email I sent is really just looking at that feature.","index":108,"end_time":457.18,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":453.86,"speaker_name":"Dan Nelsen"},{"text":"Feature section.","index":109,"end_time":458.13,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":457.33,"speaker_name":"Dan Nelsen"},{"text":"Okay.","index":110,"end_time":459.89,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":459.25,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"There were a couple things I wanted changed around a little bit and then just some changes for like where it had that placeholder there.","index":111,"end_time":472.05,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":461.01,"speaker_name":"Dan Nelsen"},{"text":"But I think all of the tweaks are kind of confined to that column.","index":112,"end_time":475.65,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":472.13,"speaker_name":"Dan Nelsen"},{"text":"And then there were a couple of notes on.","index":113,"end_time":477.85,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":475.89,"speaker_name":"Dan Nelsen"},{"text":"If you take a look at the second to last and fourth from last items on the poster you at the.","index":114,"end_time":490.46,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":477.85,"speaker_name":"Dan Nelsen"},{"text":"In the middle and features.","index":115,"end_time":491.9,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":490.46,"speaker_name":"Dan Nelsen"},{"text":"So two of those.","index":116,"end_time":494.78,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":493.9,"speaker_name":"Dan Nelsen"},{"text":"The way they''re justified is kind of off from the rest or now that I Look at the third one is kind of two.","index":117,"end_time":501.34,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":494.78,"speaker_name":"Dan Nelsen"},{"text":"So control systems has that kind of indent to its left and then low speed continuous feed steam auger looks like it adds like a couple spaces.","index":118,"end_time":513.35,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":503.34,"speaker_name":"Dan Nelsen"},{"text":"Right.","index":119,"end_time":514.15,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":513.75,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"So if we could.","index":120,"end_time":515.59,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":514.71,"speaker_name":"Dan Nelsen"},{"text":"Whatever, you know, whatever the better looking formatting is, just unify that across those.","index":121,"end_time":523.59,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":516.15,"speaker_name":"Dan Nelsen"},{"text":"Okay, Good.","index":122,"end_time":530.07,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":524.149,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"And then if when that''s those changes are made, if you could send me both high res version like we''re looking at there and then also a compressed lower res version that would be helpful to have.","index":123,"end_time":548.32,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":534.72,"speaker_name":"Dan Nelsen"},{"text":"Okay, we''ll do those edits.","index":124,"end_time":552.16,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":548.88,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Was there anything else specific to that website, edits that you had sent over that you wanted to review with us on the call?","index":125,"end_time":570.81,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":565.05,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Trying to think of what.","index":126,"end_time":573.29,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":572.01,"speaker_name":"Dan Nelsen"},{"text":"I know you sent the videos to into that folder.","index":127,"end_time":578.09,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":575.209,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":128,"end_time":579.13,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":578.65,"speaker_name":"Dan Nelsen"},{"text":"And I don''t think there was anything else on the website that wasn''t that we either hadn''t gone through or wasn''t self explanatory.","index":129,"end_time":588.01,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":580.89,"speaker_name":"Dan Nelsen"},{"text":"I''m not seeing.","index":130,"end_time":591.23,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":590.27,"speaker_name":"Dan Nelsen"},{"text":"Let me pull back up that tab for myself.","index":131,"end_time":597.47,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":594.83,"speaker_name":"Dan Nelsen"},{"text":"Are there any other areas that you that that you think that you think are identified would be helpful to go through?","index":132,"end_time":604.91,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":599.63,"speaker_name":"Dan Nelsen"},{"text":"Let me just double check the email I had sent you originally on the website updates.","index":133,"end_time":610.99,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":606.03,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"We went over the STI poster.","index":134,"end_time":614.27,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":612.35,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"There''s a couple of sections where you wanted specific images and bug heard that you left comments on.","index":135,"end_time":624.14,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":616.38,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"But is the video that you sent today separate from that?","index":136,"end_time":628.06,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":624.78,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Yeah, that was a. I''m trying to remember.","index":137,"end_time":632.54,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":629.18,"speaker_name":"Dan Nelsen"},{"text":"Let me see if I can get these comments back up in front of me.","index":138,"end_time":635.98,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":633.18,"speaker_name":"Dan Nelsen"},{"text":"Is that what this one is this comment here?","index":139,"end_time":645.55,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":643.63,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"The live operation?","index":140,"end_time":646.47,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":645.55,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":141,"end_time":646.83,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":646.47,"speaker_name":"Dan Nelsen"},{"text":"Yes, yes, perfect.","index":142,"end_time":648.59,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":646.83,"speaker_name":"Dan Nelsen"},{"text":"And then yeah, there''s just these kind of specific images for the sections here.","index":143,"end_time":656.83,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":649.79,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Let me check your comment.","index":144,"end_time":659.47,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":658.35,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Yeah, so we just wanted to make sure we had the right image to place in a couple of these comments that you had left.","index":145,"end_time":668.64,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":662.67,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"There''s that one and then the wet versus dry and then the integrated contamination standalone.","index":146,"end_time":676,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":669.52,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Those are the three outstanding ones.","index":147,"end_time":678.96,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":676.96,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":148,"end_time":682.16,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":681.6,"speaker_name":"Dan Nelsen"},{"text":"So.","index":149,"end_time":682.8,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":682.4,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"What the.","index":150,"end_time":691.92,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":691.2,"speaker_name":"Dan Nelsen"},{"text":"The for the second and third ones there, the wet versus dry discharge and thermic versus stick.","index":151,"end_time":698.62,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":691.92,"speaker_name":"Dan Nelsen"},{"text":"Oh and I have a comment on thermic as well.","index":152,"end_time":701.82,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":698.62,"speaker_name":"Dan Nelsen"},{"text":"So I''ll circle back to that in a sec.","index":153,"end_time":703.5,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":701.82,"speaker_name":"Dan Nelsen"},{"text":"That''s not going to be.","index":154,"end_time":705.26,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":704.22,"speaker_name":"Dan Nelsen"},{"text":"There''s not.","index":155,"end_time":705.82,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":705.34,"speaker_name":"Dan Nelsen"},{"text":"That''s not going to be hugely visibly apparent from like the outside.","index":156,"end_time":710.86,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":705.82,"speaker_name":"Dan Nelsen"},{"text":"They look different if you look inside of them.","index":157,"end_time":715.66,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":712.7,"speaker_name":"Dan Nelsen"},{"text":"One''s got like a big metal ring that kind of sweeps around the inside, the other doesn''t.","index":158,"end_time":720.62,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":715.98,"speaker_name":"Dan Nelsen"},{"text":"But that''s going to be the main difference.","index":159,"end_time":723.1,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":721.34,"speaker_name":"Dan Nelsen"},{"text":"I think I''ve got a photo of that agitator ring Somewhere that that would probably be the right thing to include there.","index":160,"end_time":729.41,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":723.1,"speaker_name":"Dan Nelsen"},{"text":"I will make a note and try and try to pull that over for you guys shortly.","index":161,"end_time":734.17,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":729.41,"speaker_name":"Dan Nelsen"},{"text":"Okay.","index":162,"end_time":735.21,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":734.65,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"And then do you have thing for the other two or.","index":163,"end_time":740.13,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":738.33,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Yeah, one sec, one sec, one sec.","index":164,"end_time":742.01,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":740.13,"speaker_name":"Dan Nelsen"},{"text":"I just want to get a note on this.","index":165,"end_time":744.25,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":742.01,"speaker_name":"Dan Nelsen"},{"text":"Okay.","index":166,"end_time":759.46,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":758.98,"speaker_name":"Dan Nelsen"},{"text":"That I might have some pictures of.","index":167,"end_time":765.14,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":761.46,"speaker_name":"Dan Nelsen"},{"text":"So I mean, so that might be like a picture of like almost a hose pipe, like a, like you know, just water running out of a pipe versus like a block of wax.","index":168,"end_time":777.78,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":766.58,"speaker_name":"Dan Nelsen"},{"text":"I''ll see it.","index":169,"end_time":782.01,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":781.37,"speaker_name":"Dan Nelsen"},{"text":"Let me see if we have any pictures of that kind of dry discharge block.","index":170,"end_time":786.73,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":782.01,"speaker_name":"Dan Nelsen"},{"text":"Okay, I''m gonna.","index":171,"end_time":796.65,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":787.53,"speaker_name":"Dan Nelsen"},{"text":"So I, I may have to dig around for something that will work there.","index":172,"end_time":802.01,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":797.53,"speaker_name":"Dan Nelsen"},{"text":"As I''m sure you can imagine, not all the pictures we get of the solidified remains of tissue waste that has been digested are necessarily super fun to look at pictures.","index":173,"end_time":818.42,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":802.01,"speaker_name":"Dan Nelsen"},{"text":"Understandable.","index":174,"end_time":821.3,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":820.42,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Now building integrated or standalone?","index":175,"end_time":825.18,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":822.9,"speaker_name":"Dan Nelsen"},{"text":"This is going to be.","index":176,"end_time":826.34,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":825.18,"speaker_name":"Dan Nelsen"},{"text":"So if you go back to like that top graphic on the web, on the website page you were just on.","index":177,"end_time":833.06,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":826.9,"speaker_name":"Dan Nelsen"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":178,"end_time":834.8,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":834.4,"speaker_name":"Dan Nelsen"},{"text":"So that''s like a standalone.","index":179,"end_time":836.48,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":834.88,"speaker_name":"Dan Nelsen"},{"text":"And then if you come down.","index":180,"end_time":839.44,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":837.68,"speaker_name":"Dan Nelsen"},{"text":"Keep coming, keep coming.","index":181,"end_time":842.96,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":841.44,"speaker_name":"Dan Nelsen"},{"text":"So that would be like a standalone.","index":182,"end_time":846.4,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":844.64,"speaker_name":"Dan Nelsen"},{"text":"Keep coming, keep coming.","index":183,"end_time":849.84,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":847.36,"speaker_name":"Dan Nelsen"},{"text":"Yeah, keep going, keep going.","index":184,"end_time":855.28,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":854,"speaker_name":"Dan Nelsen"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":185,"end_time":860.89,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":860.49,"speaker_name":"Dan Nelsen"},{"text":"So what I''m looking for and I can, I''ll pull a couple of these is what we''re basically saying is if it''s building integrated, it''s going to be like sunk into the floor.","index":186,"end_time":871.61,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":860.97,"speaker_name":"Dan Nelsen"},{"text":"And so it would get like loaded on the third floor, which is going to be the dirty floor.","index":187,"end_time":876.09,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":872.09,"speaker_name":"Dan Nelsen"},{"text":"And then it would get unloaded on like the first or second floor.","index":188,"end_time":879.37,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":876.09,"speaker_name":"Dan Nelsen"},{"text":"And those are like clean or non hot floors.","index":189,"end_time":882.49,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":879.53,"speaker_name":"Dan Nelsen"},{"text":"So the idea is that you have the top one end in containment, the other end out of containment.","index":190,"end_time":887.98,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":882.73,"speaker_name":"Dan Nelsen"},{"text":"And as it is processed, it goes from the hot side of the building to the cold side of the building.","index":191,"end_time":893.1,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":888.22,"speaker_name":"Dan Nelsen"},{"text":"Okay.","index":192,"end_time":894.78,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":894.14,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"So I''ll see if I can get some pictures of like through floor digesters.","index":193,"end_time":900.54,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":895.98,"speaker_name":"Dan Nelsen"},{"text":"Okay.","index":194,"end_time":901.66,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":901.1,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"I think those are the only outstanding ones.","index":195,"end_time":906.74,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":905.1,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Then just the images and then you sent us what we needed for these two here.","index":196,"end_time":912.42,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":906.74,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"So we, we will be able to get to those.","index":197,"end_time":914.06,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":912.42,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"So we''ll work on these two things and then updating the poster so we can get that.","index":198,"end_time":918.06,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":914.06,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"But we did go ahead and make those other adjustments too.","index":199,"end_time":923.56,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":921.08,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"If you have a chance to look at those and you have any additional edits, you can let us know.","index":200,"end_time":927.72,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":923.64,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"We can work on those too.","index":201,"end_time":928.92,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":927.72,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Right.","index":202,"end_time":929.96,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":929.64,"speaker_name":"Dan Nelsen"},{"text":"I think as soon, as soon as you drop me a note that you have the service validation, the service kind of copy in there, I''ll have the rest of My team do a last review on it.","index":203,"end_time":943.8,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":929.96,"speaker_name":"Dan Nelsen"},{"text":"I don''t think I have any more comments from this.","index":204,"end_time":947.7,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":945.7,"speaker_name":"Dan Nelsen"},{"text":"Okay.","index":205,"end_time":948.74,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":948.18,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"But I want to make sure they have eyes on it and you know, they''ve looked at it, you know, before this most recent round of iterations.","index":206,"end_time":957.7,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":949.86,"speaker_name":"Dan Nelsen"},{"text":"So I''m sure they won''t be particularly extensive if they have any.","index":207,"end_time":961.46,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":957.7,"speaker_name":"Dan Nelsen"},{"text":"Okay, great.","index":208,"end_time":962.98,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":961.94,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"And then the only other thing I know you had sent over was just some comments on the carousel ads that we sent over.","index":209,"end_time":971.07,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":964.5,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"So it looks like you just have a couple of edits that we can make and implement into those.","index":210,"end_time":975.31,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":971.15,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Yeah, there were one or two things on there I wanted to take a quick minute with.","index":211,"end_time":984.59,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":976.11,"speaker_name":"Dan Nelsen"},{"text":"So let me pull that one back up.","index":212,"end_time":988.51,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":986.03,"speaker_name":"Dan Nelsen"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":213,"end_time":994.51,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":994.11,"speaker_name":"Dan Nelsen"},{"text":"So the carousel three slide two, the different treatment cost options.","index":214,"end_time":1000.31,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":994.51,"speaker_name":"Dan Nelsen"},{"text":"Do you know where you pulled the numbers that were on that ad on here from?","index":215,"end_time":1007.03,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1000.47,"speaker_name":"Dan Nelsen"},{"text":"I want to say we pulled it from the website, but I can double check on that.","index":216,"end_time":1013.91,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1008.71,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Yeah, let''s double check.","index":217,"end_time":1015.79,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1014.15,"speaker_name":"Dan Nelsen"},{"text":"Just because, you know, there are, you know, we redo these every few years because, you know, if nothing else, just inflation, the numbers are going to get a little bit stale after some time.","index":218,"end_time":1026.71,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1015.79,"speaker_name":"Dan Nelsen"},{"text":"I think.","index":219,"end_time":1027.51,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1026.87,"speaker_name":"Dan Nelsen"},{"text":"I think these are older numbers.","index":220,"end_time":1029.75,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1027.59,"speaker_name":"Dan Nelsen"},{"text":"Okay.","index":221,"end_time":1031.41,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1031.01,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"I sent over kind of a.","index":222,"end_time":1034.53,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1032.85,"speaker_name":"Dan Nelsen"},{"text":"Kind of a more updated, at least I feel, more defensible set of numbers.","index":223,"end_time":1041.17,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1035.73,"speaker_name":"Dan Nelsen"},{"text":"Okay.","index":224,"end_time":1041.97,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1041.41,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Kind of same general outline.","index":225,"end_time":1043.41,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1041.97,"speaker_name":"Dan Nelsen"},{"text":"It should just be one to one plugin.","index":226,"end_time":1045.41,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1043.41,"speaker_name":"Dan Nelsen"},{"text":"But if you can see if the, if those other numbers are anywhere on the website, I would just want to take a look at it.","index":227,"end_time":1052.21,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1045.49,"speaker_name":"Dan Nelsen"},{"text":"Like I could see them being in like one of the comparison tables or something.","index":228,"end_time":1055.49,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1052.21,"speaker_name":"Dan Nelsen"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":229,"end_time":1056.09,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1055.73,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"And I just want to go through and make sure that those are all updated.","index":230,"end_time":1059.29,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1056.09,"speaker_name":"Dan Nelsen"},{"text":"So we kind of have a single set of numbers we''re showing on the website.","index":231,"end_time":1063.67,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1059.29,"speaker_name":"Dan Nelsen"},{"text":"Okay.","index":232,"end_time":1064.91,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1064.47,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Yeah, we''ll double check that and switch these out for this, these numbers you sent here.","index":233,"end_time":1069.51,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1064.91,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"And then I think the same one for four.","index":234,"end_time":1073.99,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1071.59,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"And then you''re also wondering about this figure here.","index":235,"end_time":1076.95,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1073.99,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Yeah, Looks directionally.","index":236,"end_time":1082.63,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1078.07,"speaker_name":"Dan Nelsen"},{"text":"Right.","index":237,"end_time":1082.95,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1082.63,"speaker_name":"Dan Nelsen"},{"text":"Just kind of curious where.","index":238,"end_time":1084.91,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1083.75,"speaker_name":"Dan Nelsen"},{"text":"Where that''s coming from or where else that might be on the website.","index":239,"end_time":1087.43,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1084.91,"speaker_name":"Dan Nelsen"},{"text":"Okay.","index":240,"end_time":1088.7,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1088.26,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Yeah, we will go double check that, where that was pulled from and make those changes.","index":241,"end_time":1094.26,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1088.7,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Did you have any other comments on the other ones, the EDS and tissue digester?","index":242,"end_time":1098.26,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1094.26,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"No, I haven''t gone through.","index":243,"end_time":1100.42,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1099.38,"speaker_name":"Dan Nelsen"},{"text":"I haven''t gotten all the way through all them yet.","index":244,"end_time":1102.26,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1100.42,"speaker_name":"Dan Nelsen"},{"text":"I''ll have more comments coming through shortly.","index":245,"end_time":1104.34,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1102.58,"speaker_name":"Dan Nelsen"},{"text":"Okay, yeah, that sounds good.","index":246,"end_time":1106.06,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1104.9,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Yeah, we''ll go double check and reference where those were pulled and I''ll let you know.","index":247,"end_time":1110.5,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1106.06,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Perfect.","index":248,"end_time":1111.62,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1111.06,"speaker_name":"Dan Nelsen"},{"text":"That would be great.","index":249,"end_time":1114.91,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1114.35,"speaker_name":"Dan Nelsen"},{"text":"Yeah, I''m just, I''m trying to get kind of a sense of where all that.","index":250,"end_time":1118.15,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1114.91,"speaker_name":"Dan Nelsen"},{"text":"Where all that''s living.","index":251,"end_time":1119.23,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1118.15,"speaker_name":"Dan Nelsen"},{"text":"So as we kind of go through on, you know, every few year basis or whatever, you know, all gets updated and we don''t have things that are just kind of not never getting looked at and slipping through.","index":252,"end_time":1129.79,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1119.23,"speaker_name":"Dan Nelsen"},{"text":"Right.","index":253,"end_time":1131.07,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1130.67,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Yeah, understandable.","index":254,"end_time":1132.43,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1131.15,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"And then just a quick note on those notifications you were getting, it just looked like there was an old automation.","index":255,"end_time":1140.35,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1134.51,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"So there''s some stuff going in.","index":256,"end_time":1142.15,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1140.67,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"I''ve turned it off so you shouldn''t get any emails moving forward.","index":257,"end_time":1144.99,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1142.15,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"If you do, just forward them to us and we''ll look into that.","index":258,"end_time":1148.65,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1145.69,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"Perfect.","index":259,"end_time":1149.61,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1149.13,"speaker_name":"Dan Nelsen"},{"text":"And then.","index":260,"end_time":1150.09,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1149.61,"speaker_name":"Dan Nelsen"},{"text":"And the note by K. Ross, do you know why that''s.","index":261,"end_time":1153.69,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1150.17,"speaker_name":"Dan Nelsen"},{"text":"Was the automated automation set up by her?","index":262,"end_time":1156.65,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1153.85,"speaker_name":"Dan Nelsen"},{"text":"Do you know what that.","index":263,"end_time":1157.85,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1156.97,"speaker_name":"Dan Nelsen"},{"text":"No, it was set up by us.","index":264,"end_time":1159.53,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1157.85,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"But this was like probably two years ago it was set up.","index":265,"end_time":1162.93,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1159.53,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"It was just set to go to her.","index":266,"end_time":1164.33,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1162.93,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"But I actually just removed her from your HubSpot account, so that won''t happen again.","index":267,"end_time":1168.97,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1164.33,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"Perfect.","index":268,"end_time":1170.89,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1170.33,"speaker_name":"Dan Nelsen"},{"text":"Awesome.","index":269,"end_time":1173.91,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1173.43,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Well, I will go ahead and look into those things and we''ll get those edits in progress for the couple of things that you had sent over and I''ll let you know when we have any updates there on those.","index":270,"end_time":1181.99,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1174.23,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"And we''ll send you all the new pages too when we have those included into the new bugh Herd, the Bug Herd site.","index":271,"end_time":1189.83,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1182.07,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"So send that over to you.","index":272,"end_time":1191.51,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1189.83,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Perfect.","index":273,"end_time":1192.39,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1191.91,"speaker_name":"Dan Nelsen"},{"text":"So right now, in terms of the website, the only blocking pieces are a couple of these pictures.","index":274,"end_time":1202.4,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1192.47,"speaker_name":"Dan Nelsen"},{"text":"Yep.","index":275,"end_time":1203.6,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1203.12,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"A couple of the images.","index":276,"end_time":1204.56,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1203.6,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"And now that we have the other two things, the videos from you and the.","index":277,"end_time":1208.16,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1204.56,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"The copy for those subheadings, we should be good to go.","index":278,"end_time":1213.6,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1210.48,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Those are the only outstanding ones we have.","index":279,"end_time":1214.92,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1213.6,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"So there were the five perfect and.","index":280,"end_time":1218.68,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1214.92,"speaker_name":"Dan Nelsen"},{"text":"The STI page that we''ll update too.","index":281,"end_time":1221.76,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1218.68,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Right.","index":282,"end_time":1223.21,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1222.97,"speaker_name":"Dan Nelsen"},{"text":"And then I''m trying to think if there''s anywhere else we''re using that poster or bits of that poster.","index":283,"end_time":1233.33,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1224.09,"speaker_name":"Dan Nelsen"},{"text":"Let''s just make sure to get kind of it updated over with this newest version so that we have, you know, we don''t have multiple versions stacked up somewhere that someone myself might accidentally grab at some point.","index":284,"end_time":1245.69,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1233.33,"speaker_name":"Dan Nelsen"},{"text":"Okay, yeah, we can check and make sure that those are updated, those links.","index":285,"end_time":1249.01,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1245.93,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Perfect.","index":286,"end_time":1249.88,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1249.48,"speaker_name":"Dan Nelsen"},{"text":"Awesome.","index":287,"end_time":1251.48,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1250.84,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Well, great.","index":288,"end_time":1252.12,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1251.56,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"We''ll get working on this.","index":289,"end_time":1253.12,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1252.12,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Thank you, Dan.","index":290,"end_time":1253.8,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1253.12,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"All right, thank you guys.","index":291,"end_time":1255.2,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1254.28,"speaker_name":"Dan Nelsen"},{"text":"I''ll try to get you over those pictures shortly.","index":292,"end_time":1257.48,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1255.2,"speaker_name":"Dan Nelsen"},{"text":"Sounds good.","index":293,"end_time":1258.36,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1257.72,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"Bye.","index":294,"end_time":1259.36,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1259,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Thank you.","index":295,"end_time":1259.8,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1259.36,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"}],"dateString":"2026-01-06T18:30:00.000Z","host_email":"taylor.doerbaum@marketersindemand.com","meeting_link":"https://us02web.zoom.us/j/81421883896?pwd=9iHNOeWOt9gp3Uqm9ajWXxGhOvoFVO.1","participants":["taylor.doerbaum@marketersindemand.com,baylee.g