paign emails; remove K. Ross user from HubSpot to prevent future alerts (02:00)","completed":false},{"text":"Notify Dan when automation is successfully turned off to stop unwanted emails (19:00)","completed":false},{"text":"Assist Taylor with coordination and follow-up for website and HubSpot notification issues (00:00)","completed":false}]'::jsonb,
