    'https://us02web.zoom.us/j/88927304763?pwd=asbbQolEtVpMuYX5uccJpOibhnlog1.1',
    '{"id":"01KE7J4EB9EZ2XDBP9XEKRAWR5","title":"New North x Sedra Solutions: Weekly Meeting","summary":{"notes":"## **Content Planning and Website Updates**\n\nThe team is focused on maintaining content momentum with new posts and website improvements to support product promotion.\n\n- **Content schedules are set through January 15 on Fahad’s page and January 8 on the main page, requiring fresh topics next week** to sustain engagement (00:42)  \n    - Jackie contributed a blog and LinkedIn post about the new **AI Investigator**, encouraging Fahad to share his perspective for promotion.  \n    - The content angle emphasizes conversational data querying to ease the complexity of investigations.  \n    - An upcoming **ebook** is on hold pending funding finalization but will add value once released.  \n    - Taylor will send Fahad a document to suggest new topic ideas to keep the schedule full.\n\n- **Jackie overhauled the features and functionalities page to improve stability and ease of updates, including AI Investigator content** (02:45)  \n    - The redesign fixed previous brittleness and ensures responsive display across tablets and phones.  \n    - This update supports smoother content additions and ultimately a better user experience.\n\n- **Arabic translations are needed for the website content, but UI chat features’ Arabic compatibility requires testing before promotion** (03:29)  \n    - Fahad noted that the chat system should handle Arabic inputs as it supports multilingual queries, but confirmation is pending.  \n    - Showing Arabic input and output in promotional screenshots could enhance market appeal if it works.\n\n- **Management reset the monthly point allocation to the original 75 points, removing prior over-delivery burdens and allowing flexibility for new initiatives** (04:30)  \n    - This reset reflects appreciation for the partnership and opens the door to additional project work beyond the base allocation.\n\n## **Web Traffic and Analytics Insights**\n\nWeb analytics show strong growth after launching the ABM campaign and paid social efforts, with a focus on refining traffic data quality.\n\n- **The ABM campaign launched in July 2025 has driven significant increases in paid social traffic, with about 1,500 landing page visits recorded since then** (06:46)  \n    - Organic search and direct traffic also increased, indicating strong keyword targeting and brand recognition.  \n    - Email traffic began only after the ABM campaign started, contributing to click volume.  \n\n- **Taylor proposed filtering out non-target geographic traffic, specifically recommending excluding China due to likely spam traffic** (07:48)  \n    - Fahad confirmed China traffic should be filtered out, while Singapore is a valid financial hub and should remain included.  \n    - This filter will be implemented in both Google Analytics and the client dashboard to improve data accuracy.  \n    - Monthly traffic reviews will be conducted in weekly meetings to track engagement trends effectively.\n\n## **ABM Campaign Performance and Lead Generation Challenges**\n\nDespite good engagement metrics, converting demo landing page visits into scheduled demos remains difficult, prompting ideas for more compelling outreach.\n\n- **The December-launched paid media demo campaign has generated 492 clicks but no confirmed demo schedules yet** (18:41)  \n    - Taylor emphasized that cold emails often struggle without a strong incentive, suggesting a demo video focusing solely on the AI Investigator as a teaser.  \n    - Jackie agreed on producing a short demo video highlighting the AI Investigator’s data querying interface to increase interest.\n\n- **Taylor shared a concept for a private market snapshot tool tailored to Cedra’s industry, designed to offer prospects personalized insights as a lead magnet** (14:44)  \n    - This AI-driven snapshot would provide prospects with a quick, relevant report to increase engagement and provide tangible value.  \n    - Jackie noted it may not align perfectly with Cedra’s core business, indicating cautious interest.  \n    - Taylor suggested testing the tool with a small contact list to measure effectiveness before wider rollout.\n\n- **A new ABM expert has joined Taylor’s team, exploring strategies like targeted paid media and retargeting to improve conversion rates** (16:50)  \n    - The focus is on refining messaging and offers to overcome cold email fatigue and generate higher quality leads.\n\n## **Sales Cycle Realities and Strategic Targeting**\n\nThe sales cycle for large law firms remains lengthy, requiring sustained engagement and precise targeting to reach decision-makers.\n\n- **Fahad described the ongoing sales process with a $2 billion law firm that took over a year to move from proof of concept to scheduling a demo** (20:10)  \n    - The firm is still regrouping post-holidays, illustrating the slow pace typical of this market.  \n    - Fahad and Jackie agreed an 18-month sales cycle is standard for this audience, especially for large contracts involving over 100 licenses.\n\n- **Taylor highlighted that despite high campaign impressions and clicks, converting interest into demos is hindered by the long sales cycle and complex buyer environments** (19:51)  \n    - Fahad emphasized the importance of “air cover” through ongoing outreach to keep the product top of mind until firms are ready.  \n    - The challenge is identifying and reaching the right stakeholders who see the product as a solution to their pain points.\n\n- **Fahad secured a demo with Quinn Emanuel, a major U.S. law firm involved in a $2.5 billion embezzlement case, after persistent effort spanning over a year** (25:04)  \n    - This demo represents a strategic opportunity given the firm’s focus on large litigation.  \n    - Fahad’s proactive approach included connecting demo invitations with relevant legal teams to maximize impact.\n\n## **Partnership Dynamics and Next Steps**\n\nThe team is aligned on continuing efforts with optimism for gaining traction in the new year.\n\n- **Taylor and Jackie expressed confidence that momentum will build in the coming weeks as contacts return from holidays and outreach efforts continue** (28:07)  \n    - Fahad remains committed to key opportunities and is pursuing additional contacts within law firms to expand interest.  \n    - The partnership shows strong communication and responsiveness, with Taylor offering to provide updated analytics and campaign adjustments weekly.","outline":null,"keywords":["AI Investigator","ABM campaign","demo landing page","law firm sales cycle","Google Analytics filtering","private market snapshot"],"overview":"- **Content Schedule:** Posts planned through January 15 for Fahad''s page, January 8 for main page; fresh topics needed.  \n- **Website Update:** Revamped features page for stability, better user experience; includes mobile-friendly AI Investigator content.  \n- **Traffic Growth:** ABM campaign launched in July 2025; 1,500 paid landing page visits, increased organic search and email traffic.  \n- **Demo Challenges:** December demo campaign generated 492 clicks but no scheduled demos; suggestions for demo video to boost interest.  \n- **Sales Cycle Insight:** Year-long sales cycle noted for large firms; ongoing outreach crucial for keeping product on decision-makers'' radar.  \n- **Optimistic Outlook:** Team confident momentum will build post-holidays; focus on expanding contacts within law firms for better engagement.","action_items":"\n**Fahad A Al Mutawa**\nVerify Arabic language compatibility for the chat feature in the product UI to support Arabic market promotions (03:49)\nFollow up internally and externally regarding Richard Evans and London event participation decision (09:18)\nContinue nurturing long sales cycle leads, including the major law firm proof of concept and scheduled demos such as Quinn Emanuel (20:10)\nSearch emails and reconnect with Brown Rudnick contact from 2019 to explore opportunities (27:25)\n\n**Jackie Wheeler**\nShare new blog post about AI Investigator for promotion; coordinate with Fahad for adding his input and social shares (01:41)\nFinalize demo video focused on AI Investigator feature as a campaign teaser (12:31)\nProvide Arabic translations for updated website features and functionalities page after confirming chat feature support (03:27)\n\n**Taylor Doerbaum**\nSend topic ideas document to Fahad for upcoming posts to sustain social momentum (01:00)\nImplement China traffic filter in Google Analytics and dashboards for cleaner data reporting (08:50)\nPull and share detailed December campaign conversion data post-meeting (18:52)\nPrepare to review monthly traffic data with team in weekly meetings including after China filter applied (07:48)\nArrange follow-up call with Tristan to explore private market snapshot report tool and its suitability for Cedra campaigns (15:30)\nCollaborate with ABM expert to develop refined cold email approaches and targeted paid media retargeting campaigns (16:45)\nMonitor campaign improvements and advise on adjustments based on lead generation progress (12:58)\n"},"duration":28.56999969482422,"speakers":[{"id":0,"name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"id":1,"name":"Fahad A Al Mutawa"},{"id":2,"name":"Jackie Wheeler"}],"sentences":[{"text":"Holiday break?","index":0,"end_time":1.2,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":0.48,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":1,"end_time":2.08,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1.6,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Absolutely.","index":2,"end_time":4.64,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":3.84,"speaker_name":"Fahad A Al Mutawa"},{"text":"How about you, Taylor?","index":3,"end_time":5.84,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":4.72,"speaker_name":"Jackie Wheeler"},{"text":"It wasn''t the best.","index":4,"end_time":7.44,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":6.4,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Me and my whole family pretty much got sick.","index":5,"end_time":9.44,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":7.52,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"No, no.","index":6,"end_time":12.24,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":9.84,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"So we, we had to cancel a lot of things we were gonna do and everybody was staying in our house, so it was a bummer.","index":7,"end_time":18.12,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":12.64,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"But it''s only.","index":8,"end_time":19.4,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":18.12,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"It always happens like that, doesn''t it?","index":9,"end_time":20.96,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":19.4,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Never at a good time.","index":10,"end_time":22.96,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":21.84,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"But it was okay.","index":11,"end_time":25.36,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":24,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"We were all together.","index":12,"end_time":26.04,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":25.36,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"At least the silver lining.","index":13,"end_time":29.08,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":26.04,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"We''ll stick together.","index":14,"end_time":29.96,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":29.08,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":15,"end_time":30.4,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":29.96,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"But no, it was good to just have the time off too, just to rest and relax.","index":16,"end_time":35.15,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":31.55,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Good to reset before the new year for sure.","index":17,"end_time":39.39,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":36.51,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"I''m glad you''re feeling better.","index":18,"end_time":41.95,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":40.51,"speaker_name":"Fahad A Al Mutawa"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":19,"end_time":42.55,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":42.11,"speaker_name":"Jackie Wheeler"},{"text":"Thank you.","index":20,"end_time":43.23,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":42.55,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Thank you.","index":21,"end_time":43.95,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":43.31,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"All right, so just a couple of things wanted to go through today as we''re hopping into the new year.","index":22,"end_time":52.99,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":45.07,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"But just to start out, I wanted to let you know kind of what''s upcoming for this month that we have planned.","index":23,"end_time":59.11,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":52.99,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"So we''re going to right now Fahad has post scheduled until the 15th of January, but if we want to continue to keep those scheduled out with that momentum, we want to get some new topic ideas to begin some new post creation and design.","index":24,"end_time":71.29,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":59.11,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"And so I''ll send you another one of those documents, Fahad, where you can like give just some in input as to what you think we should talk about off of your page and then we can work from there.","index":25,"end_time":79.85,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":71.45,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"And then the main page only has posts until the 8th, so that ends tomorrow.","index":26,"end_time":85.05,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":80.65,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"So by next week we''d like to have some new things done.","index":27,"end_time":88.39,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":85.05,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"We have a couple things we can pull from or we rework from previous weeks, but I can pull from things on the website quite easily.","index":28,"end_time":95.83,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":88.39,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"But was there anything new?","index":29,"end_time":97.11,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":95.83,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"I don''t know, Jackie, if you''ve worked on anything that you''ve added that we can go ahead and pull from, that would be great.","index":30,"end_time":101.909,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":97.43,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Yeah, I actually just posted because I wrote a blog post about our new AI investigator and so I just wrote a. I wrote a blog post about that that went live this morning and then I wrote a LinkedIn post about that, so.","index":31,"end_time":113.56,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":101.909,"speaker_name":"Jackie Wheeler"},{"text":"So Fahad will share that post with his own hot take on it.","index":32,"end_time":117.39,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":113.63,"speaker_name":"Jackie Wheeler"},{"text":"So that''s one thing we want to try and I''m thinking we should probably promote that post, but maybe there''s some other follow up we can do with it.","index":33,"end_time":125.91,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":118.19,"speaker_name":"Jackie Wheeler"},{"text":"But kind of the angle I''m taking with it is what if you could just ask your data questions.","index":34,"end_time":130.75,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":125.91,"speaker_name":"Jackie Wheeler"},{"text":"What if you could.","index":35,"end_time":131.55,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":130.83,"speaker_name":"Jackie Wheeler"},{"text":"It''s all about having a conversation with your data, which is kind of like hitting into the key pain point of trying to find a needle in a haystack.","index":36,"end_time":139.75,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":131.71,"speaker_name":"Jackie Wheeler"},{"text":"Which is what these investigations usually look like.","index":37,"end_time":141.71,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":139.75,"speaker_name":"Jackie Wheeler"},{"text":"Right.","index":38,"end_time":142.51,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":142.27,"speaker_name":"Jackie Wheeler"},{"text":"So that''s one thing.","index":39,"end_time":143.79,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":142.83,"speaker_name":"Jackie Wheeler"},{"text":"The other thing is that there''s an ebook coming soon that we''ll be sending over to you guys, but we''re just waiting to finalize funding and stuff, so we''re just gonna.","index":40,"end_time":154.27,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":143.95,"speaker_name":"Jackie Wheeler"},{"text":"We''re just gonna put that on hold just for.","index":41,"end_time":155.95,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":154.27,"speaker_name":"Jackie Wheeler"},{"text":"For a little bit.","index":42,"end_time":157.07,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":156.19,"speaker_name":"Jackie Wheeler"},{"text":"Okay.","index":43,"end_time":157.91,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":157.39,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":44,"end_time":158.23,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":157.91,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"That''s exciting though.","index":45,"end_time":159.15,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":158.23,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":46,"end_time":159.79,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":159.31,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"It''s always good to have additional content to add to the page that we can promote.","index":47,"end_time":164.03,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":159.95,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"So that''ll be good.","index":48,"end_time":164.83,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":164.03,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"And then the other thing I wanted to let you know is I made some tweaks to the features and functionalities page on the website and to the home.","index":49,"end_time":171.63,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":165.15,"speaker_name":"Jackie Wheeler"},{"text":"I overhauled the features and functionalities page a little bit because I had a bunch of artifacts.","index":50,"end_time":177.49,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":173.93,"speaker_name":"Jackie Wheeler"},{"text":"It was really brittle the way it had been originally designed.","index":51,"end_time":179.85,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":177.49,"speaker_name":"Jackie Wheeler"},{"text":"And so I actually just recreated the page from scratch.","index":52,"end_time":182.89,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":180.01,"speaker_name":"Jackie Wheeler"},{"text":"And so now it''s easier to add content to it.","index":53,"end_time":185.45,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":183.05,"speaker_name":"Jackie Wheeler"},{"text":"It doesn''t break.","index":54,"end_time":186.25,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":185.45,"speaker_name":"Jackie Wheeler"},{"text":"And I tested it out on the tablets and phones and all the different formats to make sure it wasn''t getting screwed up on the different formats.","index":55,"end_time":194.57,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":186.73,"speaker_name":"Jackie Wheeler"},{"text":"So that one''s overhauled now.","index":56,"end_time":196.09,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":194.57,"speaker_name":"Jackie Wheeler"},{"text":"And it mentions the AI Investigator.","index":57,"end_time":197.73,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":196.09,"speaker_name":"Jackie Wheeler"},{"text":"That''s what drove this, is I wanted to add content about the AI Investigator and things were just breaking.","index":58,"end_time":203.13,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":197.73,"speaker_name":"Jackie Wheeler"},{"text":"So that has nothing to do with you, Gu.","index":59,"end_time":205.68,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":203.21,"speaker_name":"Jackie Wheeler"},{"text":"That''s the way it was originally designed.","index":60,"end_time":207.19,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":205.83,"speaker_name":"Jackie Wheeler"},{"text":"So.","index":61,"end_time":207.51,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":207.19,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Okay.","index":62,"end_time":207.95,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":207.51,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Yeah, good to know.","index":63,"end_time":208.71,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":207.95,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Thank you.","index":64,"end_time":209.19,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":208.71,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"And so the next thing I''m going to do is I''ll need to get the Arabic translations.","index":65,"end_time":214.55,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":209.67,"speaker_name":"Jackie Wheeler"},{"text":"Although Fahad, so our UI of our app, of our interface for the product that''s not available in Arabic.","index":66,"end_time":221.989,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":214.55,"speaker_name":"Jackie Wheeler"},{"text":"Right.","index":67,"end_time":222.23,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":221.989,"speaker_name":"Jackie Wheeler"},{"text":"It''s just like the chat feature is not available in Arabic.","index":68,"end_time":225.51,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":222.23,"speaker_name":"Jackie Wheeler"},{"text":"I haven''t tried.","index":69,"end_time":230.67,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":229.83,"speaker_name":"Fahad A Al Mutawa"},{"text":"Would be worth looking into that before we start promoting it in Arabic.","index":70,"end_time":237.88,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":233.68,"speaker_name":"Jackie Wheeler"},{"text":"Because if we''re promoting it in Arabic, but it can only be done in English, I don''t know.","index":71,"end_time":241.84,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":237.88,"speaker_name":"Jackie Wheeler"},{"text":"In theory it should be able to do any language because even with ChatGPT, Google, Gemini, if you have an Arabic keyboard, you could ask the questions in Arabic and you get a response.","index":72,"end_time":253.2,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":243.36,"speaker_name":"Fahad A Al Mutawa"},{"text":"Okay.","index":73,"end_time":253.92,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":253.36,"speaker_name":"Jackie Wheeler"},{"text":"So it would be cool if that does work and we could actually show screenshots of the question in Arabic and the response in Arabic, like, that would be amazing.","index":74,"end_time":262.6,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":254.08,"speaker_name":"Jackie Wheeler"},{"text":"So I just wanted to follow up with you on that before I go down that road.","index":75,"end_time":266.84,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":262.76,"speaker_name":"Jackie Wheeler"},{"text":"Yeah, we''ll have to double check.","index":76,"end_time":269.8,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":267.56,"speaker_name":"Fahad A Al Mutawa"},{"text":"So.","index":77,"end_time":270.16,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":269.8,"speaker_name":"Fahad A Al Mutawa"},{"text":"Okay, cool, sounds good.","index":78,"end_time":274.44,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":270.16,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"And then just additional tasks that we have that we do, just management tasks that will continue as normal.","index":79,"end_time":280.84,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":275.88,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"And something I also want to just point out is I know we''ve talked about this before and how we had over delivered on points and we kind of had that burden there for a while.","index":80,"end_time":288.28,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":281.32,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"But my management team actually let me know that they went ahead and gifted you guys those points.","index":81,"end_time":292.81,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":288.28,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"So now we''re all reset back to original.","index":82,"end_time":295.73,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":292.81,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Now we''re at our normal thing because we really appreciate our partnership with you guys and you guys are awesome to work with.","index":83,"end_time":300.17,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":295.81,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"So I just want to let you know that you don''t need to worry about that burden before they just went ahead and gifted those.","index":84,"end_time":305.01,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":300.17,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"So we''ll just go with our normal 75 points a month that we have starting now fresh.","index":85,"end_time":310.77,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":305.81,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"And then if there''s any additional things that you guys have coming up or like projects or initiatives you want to work on, we could definitely work those in.","index":86,"end_time":317.33,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":310.85,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"It doesn''t have to stay within that.","index":87,"end_time":318.77,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":317.33,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"We could work work something out.","index":88,"end_time":320.18,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":318.77,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"So just wanted to let you know about that.","index":89,"end_time":322.14,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":320.18,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Yes, really appreciate that.","index":90,"end_time":325.26,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":322.7,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Fahad, you also had a question about the.","index":91,"end_time":328.38,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":326.22,"speaker_name":"Jackie Wheeler"},{"text":"The campaign?","index":92,"end_time":330.14,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":329.42,"speaker_name":"Jackie Wheeler"},{"text":"Yeah, I had a question about the campaign, the one we initiated mid December.","index":93,"end_time":337.98,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":331.9,"speaker_name":"Fahad A Al Mutawa"},{"text":"Oh yeah, the.","index":94,"end_time":339.9,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":339.18,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"The demo landing page specific one.","index":95,"end_time":341.74,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":339.9,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Yeah, yeah.","index":96,"end_time":343.18,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":342.06,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"So just want to see how that''s performing.","index":97,"end_time":345.66,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":343.9,"speaker_name":"Jackie Wheeler"},{"text":"Oh yeah, yeah, I can pull those statistics up.","index":98,"end_time":348.5,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":346.02,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Just I''ll get to this first and I''ll go over there.","index":99,"end_time":352.34,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":350.02,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"But I just wanted to also talk to you about web updates specifically.","index":100,"end_time":355.5,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":352.34,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"I went through and pulled what we saw from the previous year.","index":101,"end_time":359.02,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":355.5,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"So now that we''re starting a new year, I just wanted to go back and show you.","index":102,"end_time":361.78,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":359.02,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"So really a lot of good, a lot of green here.","index":103,"end_time":365.02,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":362.58,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"And just for reference, we had launched the ABM campaign back in July of 2025 and so what I did is I just broke up January through June and I compared the Google Analytics stocks to July through December.","index":104,"end_time":377.27,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":365.02,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"So the homepage demo landing page contact us and the features were amongst the top performing changes that we saw, which is really good specifically to see, excuse me, the demo landing page and then also user acquisition.","index":105,"end_time":392.309,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":377.75,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"So kind of getting into what we''re talking about with paid when paid began we started in July and we''ve continued that effort up with different campaigns that we''ve had running.","index":106,"end_time":400.79,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":392.39,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"We''ve seen it increase because there was no paid social traffic before the January to June and then it increased to about 1500 landing page visits from our paid social, which is good to see.","index":107,"end_time":414.11,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":401.35,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"And then organic search and direct traffic are also high, which means that people had landed on your page just from specific keywords and then unidentified traffic as well was a large increase from the two months difference.","index":108,"end_time":428.35,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":414.11,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"And then also email traffic began there Wasn''t any email traffic before, obviously.","index":109,"end_time":433.64,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":428.91,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"And so once we had the ABM campaign running, we''re seeing those clicks landing.","index":110,"end_time":437.08,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":433.64,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"So I just want to share with you that the web traffic is looking really good.","index":111,"end_time":441.64,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":438.04,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"I don''t know if there''s any specific.","index":112,"end_time":443.64,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":441.88,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Something that I''ve been doing with a couple of my clients is they want to filter out certain traffics from different geographical locations.","index":113,"end_time":450,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":443.72,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Is there any that you guys would say, can we start taking this out of the statistics and analytics moving forward?","index":114,"end_time":456.6,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":450,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Are you open to all across, globally?","index":115,"end_time":459.73,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":456.76,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"I don''t know if there''s like a specific region, you''re like, we''re never going to get business there.","index":116,"end_time":464.37,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":461.01,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Let''s filter out that traffic in case there''s any, you know, spam.","index":117,"end_time":467.97,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":464.37,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Would be good to know which jurisdictions this is coming from.","index":118,"end_time":472.53,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":468.61,"speaker_name":"Fahad A Al Mutawa"},{"text":"More than I actually pulled this up so we could look at it too.","index":119,"end_time":477.57,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":472.93,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"But this is just like the direct traffic from those two months.","index":120,"end_time":481.57,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":477.57,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"I was showing a comparison there.","index":121,"end_time":483.97,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":481.57,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"There is some China traffic coming through, but there''s also U.S. traffic and Canada traffic.","index":122,"end_time":490.7,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":484.13,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"We have London and Toronto down here.","index":123,"end_time":492.86,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":491.1,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"So it''s not a significant like pull away, but there, there is a good number coming from China.","index":124,"end_time":500.3,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":493.18,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"So one of my other clients.","index":125,"end_time":501.98,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":500.7,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"And sometimes that happens with some spam.","index":126,"end_time":504.62,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":501.98,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"One of my other clients, we''ve decided to filter that out completely.","index":127,"end_time":507.54,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":504.7,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"So we just have like a filter in Google Analytics that doesn''t include any traffic coming from China or that region over there.","index":128,"end_time":514.539,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":507.54,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"I''m not sure if that''s something you''re interested in.","index":129,"end_time":515.899,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":514.539,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"If you have business coming from there though, we wouldn''t want to do that.","index":130,"end_time":518.739,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":515.899,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"But it''s kind of just what you''ve seen in your industry.","index":131,"end_time":522.099,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":519.059,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Is that, is that a target market that you have seen people engage with?","index":132,"end_time":526.179,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":522.099,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"If it''s not at all, then we would want to filter that out.","index":133,"end_time":529.779,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":526.499,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Yeah, I think China can be filtered out.","index":134,"end_time":532.419,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":530.259,"speaker_name":"Fahad A Al Mutawa"},{"text":"Okay.","index":135,"end_time":533.299,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":532.739,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Yeah, that''s a.","index":136,"end_time":534.419,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":533.379,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"That''s something that we can add to both your Google Analytics page and also this dashboard that we have for you as well.","index":137,"end_time":540.99,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":534.579,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"You can see though our top locations do try.","index":138,"end_time":544.99,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":541.79,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"United States is a top location.","index":139,"end_time":547.07,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":545.39,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"This is just a comparison over the last month, but we do have China and Singapore popping up here as well.","index":140,"end_time":554.43,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":547.31,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Singapore is okay.","index":141,"end_time":555.71,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":554.67,"speaker_name":"Fahad A Al Mutawa"},{"text":"It''s a financial hub.","index":142,"end_time":556.83,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":555.71,"speaker_name":"Fahad A Al Mutawa"},{"text":"Yeah, Singapore is good.","index":143,"end_time":558.43,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":557.07,"speaker_name":"Jackie Wheeler"},{"text":"Okay, so just we could filter out China then.","index":144,"end_time":561.15,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":558.83,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"We can do that on both this dashboard then a and the Google Analytics.","index":145,"end_time":564.63,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":561.95,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"That way we can.","index":146,"end_time":565.55,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":564.63,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Each week we can look at them too.","index":147,"end_time":567.48,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":565.92,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Sometimes.","index":148,"end_time":568.08,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":567.48,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"A lot of my clients prefer to look at them like month over month though, because not a ton can change the Week.","index":149,"end_time":572.56,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":568.08,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"So what I consider doing in our weekly meetings if you''re interested, is we can look at the month to month traffic to see kind of what, where we''re seeing that engagement come from.","index":150,"end_time":580,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":572.72,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Yeah, I think that would just be beneficial to look through.","index":151,"end_time":583.36,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":580.16,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"And then next week even I can do that filter out of China.","index":152,"end_time":586.28,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":583.36,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"We can revisit the staff.","index":153,"end_time":587.6,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":586.28,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"But like I said, a lot of the things we are seeing are coming from United States or Canada and things like that.","index":154,"end_time":594.25,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":587.68,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"So it''s not all skewed.","index":155,"end_time":596.25,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":594.33,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"But yes.","index":156,"end_time":597.77,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":596.25,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Just wanted to, to let you know about that.","index":157,"end_time":600.01,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":597.77,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Good.","index":158,"end_time":601.37,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":600.97,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"So we can continue to keep an eye on that and then getting to just talking about ABM as well.","index":159,"end_time":611.05,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":601.85,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"So I just wanted to follow up with you.","index":160,"end_time":612.57,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":611.13,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"There is somebody, Richard Evans, who I know we''ve mentioned it before.","index":161,"end_time":615.45,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":612.57,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"He has been.","index":162,"end_time":617.29,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":616.01,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"He contacted originally.","index":163,"end_time":619.81,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":617.85,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"I put it on the spreadsheet.","index":164,"end_time":621.25,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":619.89,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"He had just reached out again I think Monday and asked if you had changed something in London.","index":165,"end_time":628.77,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":621.25,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"I don''t know if you''ve been in contact with him or had like an appointment with him or if this is something you know about but, or you guys were going back and forth.","index":166,"end_time":637.29,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":628.77,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"But he''s been like following up on this.","index":167,"end_time":639.93,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":637.29,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"So I don''t know if this is something we need to pay attention to.","index":168,"end_time":642.37,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":639.93,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"He''s been contacting me through email, WhatsApp and LinkedIn.","index":169,"end_time":647.76,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":642.53,"speaker_name":"Fahad A Al Mutawa"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":170,"end_time":649.12,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":648.64,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Oh my goodness.","index":171,"end_time":650,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":649.12,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"So I, I guess I didn''t see the message on LinkedIn recently.","index":172,"end_time":655.2,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":651.68,"speaker_name":"Fahad A Al Mutawa"},{"text":"It just came through this week.","index":173,"end_time":656.68,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":655.36,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"So I just.","index":174,"end_time":657.28,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":656.68,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"So there''s a, a one day conference in London.","index":175,"end_time":661.36,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":658.24,"speaker_name":"Fahad A Al Mutawa"},{"text":"Okay.","index":176,"end_time":662.4,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":661.76,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"What I told him is if I am in London during that day it will be interesting for me to attend and I can''t commit to that date.","index":177,"end_time":669.96,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":662.64,"speaker_name":"Fahad A Al Mutawa"},{"text":"So I''m just.","index":178,"end_time":670.64,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":669.96,"speaker_name":"Fahad A Al Mutawa"},{"text":"He''s, he''s a salesperson.","index":179,"end_time":673.7,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":672.34,"speaker_name":"Fahad A Al Mutawa"},{"text":"He keeps on pushing, pushing, pushing.","index":180,"end_time":675.22,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":673.7,"speaker_name":"Fahad A Al Mutawa"},{"text":"We need to hire him.","index":181,"end_time":677.3,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":676.1,"speaker_name":"Fahad A Al Mutawa"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":182,"end_time":680.9,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":680.42,"speaker_name":"Fahad A Al Mutawa"},{"text":"He doesn''t seem to.","index":183,"end_time":682.9,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":681.62,"speaker_name":"Fahad A Al Mutawa"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":184,"end_time":685.46,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":685.06,"speaker_name":"Fahad A Al Mutawa"},{"text":"So.","index":185,"end_time":685.7,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":685.46,"speaker_name":"Fahad A Al Mutawa"},{"text":"But, but it''s, it''s, it''s not.","index":186,"end_time":687.62,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":685.7,"speaker_name":"Fahad A Al Mutawa"},{"text":"They want us to, they have an event in London I think specifically for the procurement solution where they have procurement managers coming in, 40 of them, one on one meetings with major companies.","index":187,"end_time":703.59,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":689.94,"speaker_name":"Fahad A Al Mutawa"},{"text":"But I still can''t commit to the date so.","index":188,"end_time":709.35,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":706.47,"speaker_name":"Fahad A Al Mutawa"},{"text":"But it''s not even.","index":189,"end_time":710.87,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":709.43,"speaker_name":"Fahad A Al Mutawa"},{"text":"I wish it was a lead.","index":190,"end_time":711.83,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":710.87,"speaker_name":"Fahad A Al Mutawa"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":191,"end_time":714.39,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":713.91,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"I just want to double check.","index":192,"end_time":715.87,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":714.71,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"I figured that was the case but I just want to double check with you there about the specifics.","index":193,"end_time":720.79,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":715.87,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Want to make sure we''re letting it go.","index":194,"end_time":722.35,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":720.79,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"And then I know we originally had a demo scheduled and then that didn''t happen.","index":195,"end_time":725.6,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":722.35,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"I don''t know if there was any follow up there as far as that guy that originally had a booking to talk.","index":196,"end_time":731.4,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":725.6,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Okay.","index":197,"end_time":732.16,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":731.72,"speaker_name":"Jackie Wheeler"},{"text":"No, nothing happened there.","index":198,"end_time":734.28,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":732.16,"speaker_name":"Fahad A Al Mutawa"},{"text":"So just looking through, I''ve been thinking through a couple of things that we could do as far as the ABM update.","index":199,"end_time":739.88,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":735.08,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"So since we''ve had it running and now we''ve shifted to those two emails, we''ve simplified it now where it''s like, check out this case study how we''ve saved time.","index":200,"end_time":746.6,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":739.88,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"But here''s a link to schedule a demo.","index":201,"end_time":748.6,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":746.6,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Um, I was talking with my internal teams this week too and just cold emails in general are a difficult thing to, to get through to people, but if there''s not some kind of compelling thing that would make them want to do it, it''s going to be tougher to get those in.","index":202,"end_time":761.82,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":749.1,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"So I know we''ve talked before about kind of that AI thing that you mentioned earlier, Jackie, and like the beta testing idea is that something you guys would still be interested in is like offering as an, some kind of offer for the sequence.","index":203,"end_time":774.78,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":761.82,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Yeah, we haven''t really figured out a good way to do that and the, the AI Investigator is live now on the platform.","index":204,"end_time":784.62,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":778.46,"speaker_name":"Jackie Wheeler"},{"text":"So.","index":205,"end_time":786.22,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":785.82,"speaker_name":"Jackie Wheeler"},{"text":"Yeah, I, I don''t know.","index":206,"end_time":788.42,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":786.78,"speaker_name":"Jackie Wheeler"},{"text":"I think maybe so.","index":207,"end_time":792.06,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":788.42,"speaker_name":"Jackie Wheeler"},{"text":"You know, I''ve been talking about doing a quick demo video and yes, you know, and including that would be cool, but I think actually I could shorten the scope of that and just make it about the AI Investigator.","index":208,"end_time":805.84,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":792.06,"speaker_name":"Jackie Wheeler"},{"text":"That could be the teaser and just show asking questions of data, show the results and then you''re going to see the, the UI in that demo and you''ll see what the tabs look like and everything.","index":209,"end_time":818.92,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":805.84,"speaker_name":"Jackie Wheeler"},{"text":"And rather than going through the whole use case, I could just preview that and that would be something we can send out.","index":210,"end_time":825.48,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":818.92,"speaker_name":"Jackie Wheeler"},{"text":"Okay, yeah, that might be an option.","index":211,"end_time":827.96,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":826.04,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Something that would just make it like more of a compelling reason to pursue it.","index":212,"end_time":832.71,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":828.51,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Yeah, I know we talked about a couple different things like pricing model and things like that, but yeah, that would be good if we could update it a little bit.","index":213,"end_time":841.23,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":832.71,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Just because we''ve seen those two new emails now coming through and we haven''t had a big change or noticed anything.","index":214,"end_time":847.31,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":841.23,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"And so when that happens, we want to kind of fix it and figure out something else.","index":215,"end_time":851.63,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":847.31,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"There is something one of our owners has been working on.","index":216,"end_time":855.39,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":852.03,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"I was talking to Bailey about this yesterday.","index":217,"end_time":857.55,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":855.79,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Basically he''s been working on this thing where you can offer like a private market snapshot for your specific like industry.","index":218,"end_time":867.44,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":857.55,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"This is right now specific to what we''re talking about with marketing.","index":219,"end_time":870.64,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":867.52,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"But basically Bailey was telling me about this Monday something that they''re offering now is we could build one for Cedra where somebody could, like, put their information in and it would kind of give them like a snapshot or like, analysis, and we could cater it to the specifics of your industry.","index":220,"end_time":887.2,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":870.88,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"It could just be something that we put in the ABM campaign emails that kind of makes it more like what they''re getting out of it.","index":221,"end_time":893.61,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":887.36,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"If that''s something that sounds interesting to you, I can have maybe Tristan hop on the call who''s been building it, and we could talk about it a little bit more.","index":222,"end_time":901.29,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":894.97,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"But I''m sorry, I''m not.","index":223,"end_time":902.85,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":901.45,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"I''m not following this market snapshot.","index":224,"end_time":905.21,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":902.85,"speaker_name":"Jackie Wheeler"},{"text":"So that would be like, this is something we''d be offering our customer or our prospects about their market.","index":225,"end_time":912.65,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":905.21,"speaker_name":"Jackie Wheeler"},{"text":"So it would be like a quick, like, overview of their company that you could, like, see, say, the specifics of what would be, like, beneficial of your industry.","index":226,"end_time":920.9,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":913.13,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Bailey has a lot more information on this.","index":227,"end_time":924.7,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":922.98,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"She just told me about it on Monday.","index":228,"end_time":925.86,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":924.7,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"But it''s like, just throw it out to Cedra and let me know what they say.","index":229,"end_time":928.74,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":925.86,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"But basically it''s.","index":230,"end_time":931.58,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":929.94,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"You would input, like, what specific things would be make sense for their industry.","index":231,"end_time":936.34,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":931.58,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"And it would be like some kind of like, AI snapshot or report.","index":232,"end_time":939.38,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":936.42,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Again, more information would be coming from Tristan.","index":233,"end_time":943.67,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":940.98,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"He''s just now building this.","index":234,"end_time":944.87,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":943.67,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"But it''s like an idea that we have to kind of get the users in a campaign to get something out of it.","index":235,"end_time":950.47,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":944.87,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"But also then you''d get like a return of like a lead out of it.","index":236,"end_time":954.63,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":950.47,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"But I can have them join the call maybe next week and we could talk about it a little bit more.","index":237,"end_time":958.59,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":955.27,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"But it''s just an idea that we''re trying to get more engagement.","index":238,"end_time":961.11,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":958.59,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"A lot of people are dealing with the cold email.","index":239,"end_time":963.35,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":961.27,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"You know, it''s hard to get people to even schedule a demo, but if they can receive like something to take away with, kind of like goes hand in hand with that.","index":240,"end_time":971.01,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":963.51,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"But I can get more details on that and share it with you.","index":241,"end_time":973.77,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":971.01,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"But it''s just like an overview of, like, an idea of something that you can offer that can be catered for Cedra''s, like, clientele specifically.","index":242,"end_time":981.13,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":973.77,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Yeah, it seems a little tangential to Cedra''s business, but, yeah, it may not be a fit.","index":243,"end_time":988.97,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":982.57,"speaker_name":"Jackie Wheeler"},{"text":"It''s just something that we''re seeing.","index":244,"end_time":990.45,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":988.97,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"If anybody might be interested in testing out, we could create even like a, like a beta version and see how it looks.","index":245,"end_time":996.17,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":990.45,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"We could all try it out.","index":246,"end_time":997.13,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":996.17,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"And then if we don''t think the results would work necessarily for a group of contacts, something else we''ve been talking about Doing too, internally, is using like a smaller group of people to test like these kinds of things on.","index":247,"end_time":1008.24,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":997.21,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"So if there''s like a list of a hundred contacts, we wanted to just send it out to them specifically.","index":248,"end_time":1012.4,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1008.24,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"That way we''re not sending it to the 4,000 contacts that we''ve acquired over the course and then something else.","index":249,"end_time":1019.32,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1012.4,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Just doing specific.","index":250,"end_time":1020.88,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1019.32,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"The paid media targeting and then retargeting through an email campaign to smaller groups.","index":251,"end_time":1026.66,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1020.88,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"We just brought on somebody new to our team that''s like an expert in abm.","index":252,"end_time":1030.02,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1026.66,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"And I''ve been meeting with him about your campaign and a couple other of my clients just because I''ve been telling him, like, honestly, it''s so hard to get people from a cold email, you know, to be like, yes, I want your business and sign this massive contract and things like that.","index":253,"end_time":1043.34,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1030.02,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"So he''s been kind of working through some ideas of how you can hook more people and to get more leads, whether it''s redirecting them from a paid media campaign or something like this where they get an offer out of it.","index":254,"end_time":1053.74,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1043.5,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"So more to come on that.","index":255,"end_time":1055.82,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1054.3,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"But if you''re open to maybe a couple new ideas, like you said that I think that video would be good.","index":256,"end_time":1059.74,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1055.82,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Just kind of change it up a little bit.","index":257,"end_time":1062.46,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1060.46,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"It''s just, you know, with.","index":258,"end_time":1064.3,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1062.62,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"With the way we''ve seen it go so far, I think we need to just adjust the messaging that we have to make it a little bit more of like, compelling thing instead of like a link that says schedule time to, you know, here, see a demo, something like that.","index":259,"end_time":1077.82,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1064.3,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Dab.","index":260,"end_time":1078.78,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1078.22,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"But.","index":261,"end_time":1079.91,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1079.67,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"But yes, I will come with a couple more details next week.","index":262,"end_time":1084.47,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1080.39,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"That guy again.","index":263,"end_time":1086.23,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1085.51,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"But yeah, we just have a couple ideas we''re trying to work through to get everybody, you know, some additional leads.","index":264,"end_time":1091.99,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1086.23,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Excellent, Perfect.","index":265,"end_time":1095.03,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1092.47,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"So now let me pull up the paid media you were talking about for that new campaign.","index":266,"end_time":1099.99,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1095.91,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"So this has only been running since December.","index":267,"end_time":1103.27,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1100.87,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"So I''m just going to pull up the actual campaign manager for you here so you can see.","index":268,"end_time":1108.23,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1103.35,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"So specifically, we just want that demo scheduling so we have 492 clicks already, which is great.","index":269,"end_time":1114.31,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1108.79,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"So that means those people have gone to that landing page, which is probably another reason we saw that spike in the website performance that I showed you earlier to the demo landing page.","index":270,"end_time":1125.27,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1116.79,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"So what I can do too is after this call is I''ll go pull the exact December traffic from when we launch this ad.","index":271,"end_time":1132.07,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1125.67,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"So we can see how much that has affected the IT as well.","index":272,"end_time":1135.35,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1132.47,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"The tricky thing though is I imagine you haven''t got anybody to actual schedule it yet.","index":273,"end_time":1140.31,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1135.75,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"We''ve just had people visiting the site.","index":274,"end_time":1142.15,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1140.31,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Is that correct?","index":275,"end_time":1143.03,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1142.15,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"That''s correct, yeah.","index":276,"end_time":1144.95,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1143.35,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"That''s the thing that we''ve seen with a lot of the.","index":277,"end_time":1148.95,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1145.27,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"I have another client that has the same thing where we have, like, a free assessment page where they do the same thing, and we have a ton of people that get to the page and they just don''t finish, you know, go the full mile.","index":278,"end_time":1159.45,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1149.43,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"And it''s.","index":279,"end_time":1159.89,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1159.45,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"It''s funny to me because I wouldn''t click on a link for a demo if I didn''t want to do it.","index":280,"end_time":1163.65,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1159.89,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"But I think people, like, explore the options or they''re not quite ready to get there yet.","index":281,"end_time":1168.01,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1163.65,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Which is kind of how we approach the ABM campaign offer is people might be.","index":282,"end_time":1171.97,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1168.01,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Might not exactly be ready for that step yet, and they kind of want to learn more, which is why I think, like you said, Jackie, that video would be helpful to kind of like assist and aid in that and kind of show them without committing to, like, a scheduled call.","index":283,"end_time":1183.25,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1172.13,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Right.","index":284,"end_time":1183.89,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1183.49,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"But it''s crazy because we have very high impressions and clicks on this already that we''ve just launched for a month.","index":285,"end_time":1190.32,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1185.12,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"It''s getting them over that finish line that we need to get to be more compelling for somebody to schedule that demo.","index":286,"end_time":1197.92,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1191.6,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"I know you had said before that there was one particular contact that you had that you had scheduled demo for, but we couldn''t find the email.","index":287,"end_time":1205.92,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1198.8,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"But they ended up turning into a client, is that correct?","index":288,"end_time":1209.6,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1207.12,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Not a client yet, but we did do a proof of concept.","index":289,"end_time":1212.48,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1210.28,"speaker_name":"Fahad A Al Mutawa"},{"text":"So that''s still a work in progress.","index":290,"end_time":1216.48,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1212.48,"speaker_name":"Fahad A Al Mutawa"},{"text":"But not a client yet, but we''re still like, you know, conversation is still moving forward.","index":291,"end_time":1222.36,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1216.48,"speaker_name":"Fahad A Al Mutawa"},{"text":"Okay.","index":292,"end_time":1223.52,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1223,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Is there anything specific that you would say, you know, to your ICP that would make them kind of get to that point of scheduling the demo of where they would be at?","index":293,"end_time":1232.36,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1223.52,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Just because, like, on a marketing standpoint, we''re doing all the things.","index":294,"end_time":1235.48,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1232.6,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"We''re doing the paid media, we''re doing the ABM or redirecting traffic, and they''re coming to the page.","index":295,"end_time":1239.88,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1235.48,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Is there something you would say that about the industry specifically?","index":296,"end_time":1243.86,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1240.12,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"That we can create a better hook or kind of get them across that finish line or what stage they''re in and stuff like that?","index":297,"end_time":1250.9,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1243.86,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"The funny thing about this, this law firm was a, you know, a cold reach.","index":298,"end_time":1258.7,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1251.62,"speaker_name":"Fahad A Al Mutawa"},{"text":"I don''t Remember there was LinkedIn message from the R or an email, but they contacted us through the website back in November last year.","index":299,"end_time":1268.56,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1258.7,"speaker_name":"Fahad A Al Mutawa"},{"text":"So not this November 24th.","index":300,"end_time":1272.64,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1269.52,"speaker_name":"Fahad A Al Mutawa"},{"text":"And now it''s been over 12 months.","index":301,"end_time":1276.32,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1273.36,"speaker_name":"Fahad A Al Mutawa"},{"text":"During that 12 months, we''ve done a proof of concept We''ve circled back, showed them the AI investigator back in, I think it was October right before or November before Thanksgiving.","index":302,"end_time":1288,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1276.96,"speaker_name":"Fahad A Al Mutawa"},{"text":"I followed up with them earlier this morning and just got an email before this meeting that, you know, they''re still regrouping after the holidays and.","index":303,"end_time":1297.33,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1290.08,"speaker_name":"Fahad A Al Mutawa"},{"text":"And they''ll get back to us.","index":304,"end_time":1298.4,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1297.4,"speaker_name":"Fahad A Al Mutawa"},{"text":"So it''s a long sales cycle.","index":305,"end_time":1300.52,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1298.4,"speaker_name":"Fahad A Al Mutawa"},{"text":"Very long.","index":306,"end_time":1301.24,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1300.6,"speaker_name":"Jackie Wheeler"},{"text":"Really is.","index":307,"end_time":1301.88,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1301.24,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"That''s great.","index":308,"end_time":1303.08,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1302.36,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Because we''re trying to sell to the law firm and for them to buy over 100 licenses.","index":309,"end_time":1310.68,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1304.84,"speaker_name":"Fahad A Al Mutawa"},{"text":"So the proof of concept is complete.","index":310,"end_time":1313.4,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1311.4,"speaker_name":"Fahad A Al Mutawa"},{"text":"The pricing.","index":311,"end_time":1314.84,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1314.04,"speaker_name":"Fahad A Al Mutawa"},{"text":"We have the new pricing matrix which they have received.","index":312,"end_time":1317.24,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1314.84,"speaker_name":"Fahad A Al Mutawa"},{"text":"And now it''s a matter of six weeks, six months, I''ve got no idea.","index":313,"end_time":1325.6,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1318.2,"speaker_name":"Fahad A Al Mutawa"},{"text":"But you know, it''s a $2 billion law firm.","index":314,"end_time":1327.87,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1325.6,"speaker_name":"Fahad A Al Mutawa"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":315,"end_time":1328.98,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1328.66,"speaker_name":"Fahad A Al Mutawa"},{"text":"It''s not, you know, a small boutique law firm that has a couple of decision makers.","index":316,"end_time":1334.34,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1329.22,"speaker_name":"Fahad A Al Mutawa"},{"text":"I like this.","index":317,"end_time":1334.98,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1334.34,"speaker_name":"Fahad A Al Mutawa"},{"text":"I want to buy this.","index":318,"end_time":1335.78,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1334.98,"speaker_name":"Fahad A Al Mutawa"},{"text":"And it''s going to be the same across the board in most of these industries.","index":319,"end_time":1339.54,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1336.1,"speaker_name":"Fahad A Al Mutawa"},{"text":"Even our KOC took a year and a half to close that deal.","index":320,"end_time":1343.38,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1340.02,"speaker_name":"Fahad A Al Mutawa"},{"text":"I was going to say 18 months seems like the standard cycle for.","index":321,"end_time":1346.82,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1343.46,"speaker_name":"Jackie Wheeler"},{"text":"For this target audience.","index":322,"end_time":1348.34,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1347.06,"speaker_name":"Jackie Wheeler"},{"text":"Yep.","index":323,"end_time":1349.22,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1348.66,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"So.","index":324,"end_time":1350.5,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1350.1,"speaker_name":"Fahad A Al Mutawa"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":325,"end_time":1351.58,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1351.22,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"But.","index":326,"end_time":1351.74,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1351.58,"speaker_name":"Fahad A Al Mutawa"},{"text":"But with.","index":327,"end_time":1352.18,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1351.74,"speaker_name":"Fahad A Al Mutawa"},{"text":"While that 18 months started a year ago.","index":328,"end_time":1354.18,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1352.18,"speaker_name":"Fahad A Al Mutawa"},{"text":"So now it sounds.","index":329,"end_time":1355.92,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1354.64,"speaker_name":"Fahad A Al Mutawa"},{"text":"And we went through all the hurdles, you know, the proof of concept, that first contract with them to get the POC in place.","index":330,"end_time":1362.88,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1355.92,"speaker_name":"Fahad A Al Mutawa"},{"text":"They tried it out, they trained on it, they like it circled back.","index":331,"end_time":1367,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1363.28,"speaker_name":"Fahad A Al Mutawa"},{"text":"The conversation is still open, but with others, we didn''t even start that dialogue.","index":332,"end_time":1372.48,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1367,"speaker_name":"Fahad A Al Mutawa"},{"text":"So even if they do come back, if that.","index":333,"end_time":1374.92,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1372.8,"speaker_name":"Fahad A Al Mutawa"},{"text":"If it''s a.","index":334,"end_time":1375.4,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1374.92,"speaker_name":"Fahad A Al Mutawa"},{"text":"Besides, if it''s a sizable law firm or even, for example, this.","index":335,"end_time":1384.09,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1375.4,"speaker_name":"Fahad A Al Mutawa"},{"text":"The case that we''re trying to get the.","index":336,"end_time":1387.13,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1384.89,"speaker_name":"Fahad A Al Mutawa"},{"text":"What is it called?","index":337,"end_time":1387.85,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1387.13,"speaker_name":"Fahad A Al Mutawa"},{"text":"New first brands.","index":338,"end_time":1390.41,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1388.09,"speaker_name":"Fahad A Al Mutawa"},{"text":"First brands.","index":339,"end_time":1391.57,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1390.81,"speaker_name":"Fahad A Al Mutawa"},{"text":"Yeah, first brands.","index":340,"end_time":1393.29,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1391.57,"speaker_name":"Fahad A Al Mutawa"},{"text":"For them it would be more of an urgency because it''s a life case right now.","index":341,"end_time":1397.53,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1393.61,"speaker_name":"Fahad A Al Mutawa"},{"text":"So there is that, you know, that.","index":342,"end_time":1400.73,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1398.33,"speaker_name":"Fahad A Al Mutawa"},{"text":"That urgency in and utilizing it.","index":343,"end_time":1404.53,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1400.73,"speaker_name":"Fahad A Al Mutawa"},{"text":"So if they want to utilize it, it would not be a long or a.","index":344,"end_time":1407.85,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1404.53,"speaker_name":"Fahad A Al Mutawa"},{"text":"A very long sales cycle.","index":345,"end_time":1409.51,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1408.15,"speaker_name":"Fahad A Al Mutawa"},{"text":"Right.","index":346,"end_time":1409.83,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1409.51,"speaker_name":"Fahad A Al Mutawa"},{"text":"So it''s a matter of how do you get to the right people within these companies.","index":347,"end_time":1414.15,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1411.03,"speaker_name":"Fahad A Al Mutawa"},{"text":"And a lot of them, there''s a lot of companies that have problems and how do you get to the right people?","index":348,"end_time":1418.23,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1414.15,"speaker_name":"Fahad A Al Mutawa"},{"text":"And for them say, this could solve my problem.","index":349,"end_time":1420.31,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1418.23,"speaker_name":"Fahad A Al Mutawa"},{"text":"I would be able to do something with this.","index":350,"end_time":1422.31,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1420.31,"speaker_name":"Fahad A Al Mutawa"},{"text":"So while we''re doing a lot of messaging, but with law firm, it''s going to be a long sales cycle with organizations just how much pain they''re in and did the right person see it?","index":351,"end_time":1436.16,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1423.03,"speaker_name":"Fahad A Al Mutawa"},{"text":"Right.","index":352,"end_time":1437.36,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1436.96,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"And I know we''ve these new ads, the demo landing specific we were using that spreadsheet, too, that Anas had sent over that you guys worked on the specific individuals, too.","index":353,"end_time":1447,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1438.16,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"And I know you pulled law firm.","index":354,"end_time":1448.28,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1447,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"So it''s getting in front of the people, too.","index":355,"end_time":1450.6,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1448.28,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"You know, these specific people are seeing it.","index":356,"end_time":1452.56,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1450.6,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Like you said, it''s just a matter of getting them.","index":357,"end_time":1454.96,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1453.12,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Getting them there.","index":358,"end_time":1455.92,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1455.04,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"But it''s good.","index":359,"end_time":1457.4,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1456.8,"speaker_name":"Fahad A Al Mutawa"},{"text":"You know, as Jackie was, you know, talking to me on Monday, there still air cover, because we''re still trying to reach out in other ways, and if they''ve seen it, maybe it will resonate when we actually finally do get to them.","index":360,"end_time":1468.73,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1457.4,"speaker_name":"Fahad A Al Mutawa"},{"text":"So I had a call today with one of the partners and also a major law firm out of the U.S. quinn Emanuel, who, funny enough, are the lawyers for the defendant in.","index":361,"end_time":1482.45,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1470.65,"speaker_name":"Fahad A Al Mutawa"},{"text":"In this.","index":362,"end_time":1482.97,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1482.45,"speaker_name":"Fahad A Al Mutawa"},{"text":"Way.","index":363,"end_time":1485.29,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1484.89,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"They are.","index":364,"end_time":1487.01,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1486.41,"speaker_name":"Fahad A Al Mutawa"},{"text":"They, they.","index":365,"end_time":1487.53,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1487.01,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"They.","index":366,"end_time":1487.85,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1487.53,"speaker_name":"Fahad A Al Mutawa"},{"text":"One of the lawyers.","index":367,"end_time":1488.97,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1488.01,"speaker_name":"Fahad A Al Mutawa"},{"text":"They have like a thousand lawyers.","index":368,"end_time":1490.41,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1489.05,"speaker_name":"Fahad A Al Mutawa"},{"text":"One of the lawyers is the.","index":369,"end_time":1491.75,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1490.41,"speaker_name":"Fahad A Al Mutawa"},{"text":"Is the lawyer for the defendant that''s been accused of embezzling $2.5 billion.","index":370,"end_time":1499.43,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1494.23,"speaker_name":"Fahad A Al Mutawa"},{"text":"I''m sure they''re gonna make quite a few million dollars on legal fees on that.","index":371,"end_time":1502.95,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1499.43,"speaker_name":"Fahad A Al Mutawa"},{"text":"So.","index":372,"end_time":1503.35,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1502.95,"speaker_name":"Fahad A Al Mutawa"},{"text":"But.","index":373,"end_time":1504.15,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1503.75,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"And we have a demo scheduled for the firm either next Thursday or the following Thursday that took me a year to get to.","index":374,"end_time":1514.71,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1504.39,"speaker_name":"Fahad A Al Mutawa"},{"text":"Right.","index":375,"end_time":1515.35,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1514.95,"speaker_name":"Fahad A Al Mutawa"},{"text":"It''s actually more than a year and a half to get to.","index":376,"end_time":1520.2,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1517.44,"speaker_name":"Fahad A Al Mutawa"},{"text":"This first meeting was in London.","index":377,"end_time":1522.32,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1520.2,"speaker_name":"Fahad A Al Mutawa"},{"text":"Second meeting was in London.","index":378,"end_time":1523.52,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1522.32,"speaker_name":"Fahad A Al Mutawa"},{"text":"Third meeting was in London.","index":379,"end_time":1524.96,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1523.52,"speaker_name":"Fahad A Al Mutawa"},{"text":"Fourth meeting.","index":380,"end_time":1525.92,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1525.2,"speaker_name":"Fahad A Al Mutawa"},{"text":"The managing partner or the founder of the law firm, believe John Quinn, was in Kuwait last September.","index":381,"end_time":1533.68,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1526,"speaker_name":"Fahad A Al Mutawa"},{"text":"And I took him to a meeting.","index":382,"end_time":1536.44,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1534.56,"speaker_name":"Fahad A Al Mutawa"},{"text":"I introduced him to a couple of clients, and towards the end, he was thanking me.","index":383,"end_time":1540.56,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1536.44,"speaker_name":"Fahad A Al Mutawa"},{"text":"I was like, all I need from you is a demo for the rest of your team.","index":384,"end_time":1543.19,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1540.56,"speaker_name":"Fahad A Al Mutawa"},{"text":"And it took me from September till January to get somebody to call me back to say, let''s do this next Thursday or the following Thursday, the date I''ll be available.","index":385,"end_time":1554.14,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1544.22,"speaker_name":"Fahad A Al Mutawa"},{"text":"Just, you know, try to do it during Eastern morning time, not too late in the evening.","index":386,"end_time":1560.54,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1554.22,"speaker_name":"Fahad A Al Mutawa"},{"text":"So hopefully, somebody out of that law firm will resonate on one of their cases, because that''s the right kind of law firm, because all they deal with is litigation and very large litigation, whether it''s a bankruptcy, whether somebody''s being accused of something.","index":387,"end_time":1579.58,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1562.38,"speaker_name":"Fahad A Al Mutawa"},{"text":"Again, if Queen Emanuel is buying the product, who they onboard as their client?","index":388,"end_time":1587.66,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1582.14,"speaker_name":"Fahad A Al Mutawa"},{"text":"I wouldn''t even know.","index":389,"end_time":1588.86,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1587.82,"speaker_name":"Fahad A Al Mutawa"},{"text":"It wouldn''t.","index":390,"end_time":1589.42,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1588.86,"speaker_name":"Fahad A Al Mutawa"},{"text":"Something does not concern me because we would not work on that project.","index":391,"end_time":1592.54,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1589.42,"speaker_name":"Fahad A Al Mutawa"},{"text":"We''re just the technology.","index":392,"end_time":1594.78,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1592.78,"speaker_name":"Fahad A Al Mutawa"},{"text":"So we wouldn''t know which cases would come in neither from Weil or Quinn Emmanuel.","index":393,"end_time":1599.97,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1595.42,"speaker_name":"Fahad A Al Mutawa"},{"text":"But I didn''t make the point to this lady.","index":394,"end_time":1603.77,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1601.81,"speaker_name":"Fahad A Al Mutawa"},{"text":"Her name is Melis I told her, by the way, your firm is representing a founder and CEO that embezzled $2.5 billion.","index":395,"end_time":1609.73,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1603.77,"speaker_name":"Fahad A Al Mutawa"},{"text":"Maybe that team of lawyers should be on that demo call.","index":396,"end_time":1612.69,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1610.13,"speaker_name":"Fahad A Al Mutawa"},{"text":"And I just left.","index":397,"end_time":1613.81,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1612.93,"speaker_name":"Fahad A Al Mutawa"},{"text":"Nice.","index":398,"end_time":1615.81,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1615.33,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Smart.","index":399,"end_time":1617.25,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1616.69,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Send me that information.","index":400,"end_time":1622.53,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1621.49,"speaker_name":"Fahad A Al Mutawa"},{"text":"So I looked up my slack.","index":401,"end_time":1624.13,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1622.77,"speaker_name":"Fahad A Al Mutawa"},{"text":"I, you know, copied that link I sent to everybody, and I sent it to her.","index":402,"end_time":1627.22,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1624.13,"speaker_name":"Fahad A Al Mutawa"},{"text":"It''s like, I''ll find out who it is, and I''ll make sure somebody from that team would be on that call.","index":403,"end_time":1632.05,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1627.93,"speaker_name":"Fahad A Al Mutawa"},{"text":"It''s like, thank you.","index":404,"end_time":1633.05,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1632.05,"speaker_name":"Fahad A Al Mutawa"},{"text":"Well done.","index":405,"end_time":1634.01,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1633.37,"speaker_name":"Jackie Wheeler"},{"text":"Perfect.","index":406,"end_time":1634.81,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1634.17,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"I''m not giving up on this case.","index":407,"end_time":1639.37,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1637.93,"speaker_name":"Fahad A Al Mutawa"},{"text":"I want to get somebody from any.","index":408,"end_time":1642.09,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1639.37,"speaker_name":"Fahad A Al Mutawa"},{"text":"Of the part of it.","index":409,"end_time":1643.29,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1642.09,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":410,"end_time":1644.65,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1644.09,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"I remember a contact from back in 2019 from Brown Rudnick, which is a law firm representing the.","index":411,"end_time":1650.97,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1645.05,"speaker_name":"Fahad A Al Mutawa"},{"text":"The creditors, the banks.","index":412,"end_time":1654.7,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1652.49,"speaker_name":"Fahad A Al Mutawa"},{"text":"I met one of their senior partners out of their Boston office.","index":413,"end_time":1659.42,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1655.98,"speaker_name":"Fahad A Al Mutawa"},{"text":"I know I have his email somewhere, but I cannot remember his name.","index":414,"end_time":1662.82,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1659.98,"speaker_name":"Fahad A Al Mutawa"},{"text":"So I have to dig through those emails and try to find him and send him an email, see if he remembers me, because I''ve only met him twice.","index":415,"end_time":1669.979,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1662.82,"speaker_name":"Fahad A Al Mutawa"},{"text":"Yeah, it was years back now.","index":416,"end_time":1673.18,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1671.5,"speaker_name":"Fahad A Al Mutawa"},{"text":"So if he does remember me, maybe he''ll be able to either lead us to the lawyer handling that case or also.","index":417,"end_time":1679.87,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1674.22,"speaker_name":"Fahad A Al Mutawa"},{"text":"So we could demonstrate to Brown Rudnick.","index":418,"end_time":1681.87,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1679.95,"speaker_name":"Fahad A Al Mutawa"},{"text":"Yeah, we''ll see what happens.","index":419,"end_time":1684.83,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1683.63,"speaker_name":"Fahad A Al Mutawa"},{"text":"Good stuff.","index":420,"end_time":1685.87,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1685.07,"speaker_name":"Jackie Wheeler"},{"text":"Yeah, good stuff.","index":421,"end_time":1687.71,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1686.03,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Well, we''re putting all the pieces in place, and, yeah, now that it''s the new year, I think in the next couple of weeks, we''re probably going to start getting some traction, but we''ll see.","index":422,"end_time":1695.629,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1687.71,"speaker_name":"Jackie Wheeler"},{"text":"Fingers crossed.","index":423,"end_time":1697.95,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1696.91,"speaker_name":"Fahad A Al Mutawa"},{"text":"Fingers crossed.","index":424,"end_time":1698.83,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1697.95,"speaker_name":"Jackie Wheeler"},{"text":"Back from the holidays.","index":425,"end_time":1700.63,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1699.55,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Everyone''s rearing to go.","index":426,"end_time":1701.63,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1700.63,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":427,"end_time":1702.19,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1701.71,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Excellent.","index":428,"end_time":1704.03,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1703.47,"speaker_name":"Fahad A Al Mutawa"},{"text":"Thank you, ladies.","index":429,"end_time":1704.99,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1704.03,"speaker_name":"Fahad A Al Mutawa"},{"text":"Thank you so much.","index":430,"end_time":1706.11,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1705.31,"speaker_name":"Jackie Wheeler"},{"text":"Have a good rest of your day.","index":431,"end_time":1707.79,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1706.59,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"You, too.","index":432,"end_time":1708.35,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1707.79,"speaker_name":"Jackie Wheeler"}],"dateString":"2026-01-07T16:30:00.000Z","host_email":"taylor.doerbaum@marketersindemand.com","meeting_link":"https://us02web.zoom.us/j/88927304763?pwd=asbbQolEtVpMuYX5uccJpOibhnlog1.1","participants":["taylor.doerbaum@marketersindemand.com,baylee.gunnell@marketersindemand.com,j.wheeler@sedrasolutions.com,i.hamshari@sedrasolutions.com,f.almutawa@sedrasolutions.com","baylee.gunnell@marketersindemand.com","j.wheeler@sedrasolutions.com","i.hamshari@sedrasolutions.com","f.almutawa@sedrasolutions.com"],"transcript_url":"https://app.fireflies.ai/view/01KE7J4EB9EZ2XDBP9XEKRAWR5","organizer_email":"taylor.doerbaum@marketersindemand.com"}'::jsonb,
    '{"label":"positive","confidence":0.92,"bullets":["Confirmed December campaign drove 492 demo page visits; no conversions yet but strong traction.","Overhauled features page now stable across devices; highlights new AI Investigator tool.","Gifted overage points reset monthly quota; team now operating on standard 75-point plan.","Agreed to filter China traffic from analytics; U.S. and Canada remain primary geo sources.","Planned teaser video on AI tool to improve ABM email engagement and demo conversions."],"highlights":[{"quote":"The AI Investigator is live now on the platform.","speaker":"Jackie Wheeler"},{"quote":"We have 492 clicks already, which is great.","speaker":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"quote":"It''s a long sales cycle... even our KOC took a year and a half to close that deal.","speaker":"Fahad A Al Mutawa"}],"topics":["marketing","ABM","analytics","campaign","AI"],"model":"openai/gpt-4-0613","version":1,"generated_at":"2026-01-09T00:00:00Z"}'::jsonb,
    '{"fireflies_summary":{"notes":"## **Content Planning and Website Updates**\n\nThe team is focused on maintaining content momentum with new posts and website improvements to support product promotion.\n\n- **Content schedules are set through January 15 on Fahad’s page and January 8 on the main page, requiring fresh topics next week** to sustain engagement (00:42)  \n    - Jackie contributed a blog and LinkedIn post about the new **AI Investigator**, encouraging Fahad to share his perspective for promotion.  \n    - The content angle emphasizes conversational data querying to ease the complexity of investigations.  \n    - An upcoming **ebook** is on hold pending funding finalization but will add value once released.  \n    - Taylor will send Fahad a document to suggest new topic ideas to keep the schedule full.\n\n- **Jackie overhauled the features and functionalities page to improve stability and ease of updates, including AI Investigator content** (02:45)  \n    - The redesign fixed previous brittleness and ensures responsive display across tablets and phones.  \n    - This update supports smoother content additions and ultimately a better user experience.\n\n- **Arabic translations are needed for the website content, but UI chat features’ Arabic compatibility requires testing before promotion** (03:29)  \n    - Fahad noted that the chat system should handle Arabic inputs as it supports multilingual queries, but confirmation is pending.  \n    - Showing Arabic input and output in promotional screenshots could enhance market appeal if it works.\n\n- **Management reset the monthly point allocation to the original 75 points, removing prior over-delivery burdens and allowing flexibility for new initiatives** (04:30)  \n    - This reset reflects appreciation for the partnership and opens the door to additional project work beyond the base allocation.\n\n## **Web Traffic and Analytics Insights**\n\nWeb analytics show strong growth after launching the ABM campaign and paid social efforts, with a focus on refining traffic data quality.\n\n- **The ABM campaign launched in July 2025 has driven significant increases in paid social traffic, with about 1,500 landing page visits recorded since then** (06:46)  \n    - Organic search and direct traffic also increased, indicating strong keyword targeting and brand recognition.  \n    - Email traffic began only after the ABM campaign started, contributing to click volume.  \n\n- **Taylor proposed filtering out non-target geographic traffic, specifically recommending excluding China due to likely spam traffic** (07:48)  \n    - Fahad confirmed China traffic should be filtered out, while Singapore is a valid financial hub and should remain included.  \n    - This filter will be implemented in both Google Analytics and the client dashboard to improve data accuracy.  \n    - Monthly traffic reviews will be conducted in weekly meetings to track engagement trends effectively.\n\n## **ABM Campaign Performance and Lead Generation Challenges**\n\nDespite good engagement metrics, converting demo landing page visits into scheduled demos remains difficult, prompting ideas for more compelling outreach.\n\n- **The December-launched paid media demo campaign has generated 492 clicks but no confirmed demo schedules yet** (18:41)  \n    - Taylor emphasized that cold emails often struggle without a strong incentive, suggesting a demo video focusing solely on the AI Investigator as a teaser.  \n    - Jackie agreed on producing a short demo video highlighting the AI Investigator’s data querying interface to increase interest.\n\n- **Taylor shared a concept for a private market snapshot tool tailored to Cedra’s industry, designed to offer prospects personalized insights as a lead magnet** (14:44)  \n    - This AI-driven snapshot would provide prospects with a quick, relevant report to increase engagement and provide tangible value.  \n    - Jackie noted it may not align perfectly with Cedra’s core business, indicating cautious interest.  \n    - Taylor suggested testing the tool with a small contact list to measure effectiveness before wider rollout.\n\n- **A new ABM expert has joined Taylor’s team, exploring strategies like targeted paid media and retargeting to improve conversion rates** (16:50)  \n    - The focus is on refining messaging and offers to overcome cold email fatigue and generate higher quality leads.\n\n## **Sales Cycle Realities and Strategic Targeting**\n\nThe sales cycle for large law firms remains lengthy, requiring sustained engagement and precise targeting to reach decision-makers.\n\n- **Fahad described the ongoing sales process with a $2 billion law firm that took over a year to move from proof of concept to scheduling a demo** (20:10)  \n    - The firm is still regrouping post-holidays, illustrating the slow pace typical of this market.  \n    - Fahad and Jackie agreed an 18-month sales cycle is standard for this audience, especially for large contracts involving over 100 licenses.\n\n- **Taylor highlighted that despite high campaign impressions and clicks, converting interest into demos is hindered by the long sales cycle and complex buyer environments** (19:51)  \n    - Fahad emphasized the importance of “air cover” through ongoing outreach to keep the product top of mind until firms are ready.  \n    - The challenge is identifying and reaching the right stakeholders who see the product as a solution to their pain points.\n\n- **Fahad secured a demo with Quinn Emanuel, a major U.S. law firm involved in a $2.5 billion embezzlement case, after persistent effort spanning over a year** (25:04)  \n    - This demo represents a strategic opportunity given the firm’s focus on large litigation.  \n    - Fahad’s proactive approach included connecting demo invitations with relevant legal teams to maximize impact.\n\n## **Partnership Dynamics and Next Steps**\n\nThe team is aligned on continuing efforts with optimism for gaining traction in the new year.\n\n- **Taylor and Jackie expressed confidence that momentum will build in the coming weeks as contacts return from holidays and outreach efforts continue** (28:07)  \n    - Fahad remains committed to key opportunities and is pursuing additional contacts within law firms to expand interest.  \n    - The partnership shows strong communication and responsiveness, with Taylor offering to provide updated analytics and campaign adjustments weekly.","outline":null,"keywords":["AI Investigator","ABM campaign","demo landing page","law firm sales cycle","Google Analytics filtering","private market snapshot"],"overview":"- **Content Schedule:** Posts planned through January 15 for Fahad''s page, January 8 for main page; fresh topics needed.  \n- **Website Update:** Revamped features page for stability, better user experience; includes mobile-friendly AI Investigator content.  \n- **Traffic Growth:** ABM campaign launched in July 2025; 1,500 paid landing page visits, increased organic search and email traffic.  \n- **Demo Challenges:** December demo campaign generated 492 clicks but no scheduled demos; suggestions for demo video to boost interest.  \n- **Sales Cycle Insight:** Year-long sales cycle noted for large firms; ongoing outreach crucial for keeping product on decision-makers'' radar.  \n- **Optimistic Outlook:** Team confident momentum will build post-holidays; focus on expanding contacts within law firms for better engagement.","action_items":"\n**Fahad A Al Mutawa**\nVerify Arabic language compatibility for the chat feature in the product UI to support Arabic market promotions (03:49)\nFollow up internally and externally regarding Richard Evans and London event participation decision (09:18)\nContinue nurturing long sales cycle leads, including the major law firm proof of concept and scheduled demos such as Quinn Emanuel (20:10)\nSearch emails and reconnect with Brown Rudnick contact from 2019 to explore opportunities (27:25)\n\n**Jackie Wheeler**\nShare new blog post about AI Investigator for promotion; coordinate with Fahad for adding his input and social shares (01:41)\nFinalize demo video focused on AI Investigator feature as a campaign teaser (12:31)\nProvide Arabic translations for updated website features and functionalities page after confirming chat feature support (03:27)\n\n**Taylor Doerbaum**\nSend topic ideas document to Fahad for upcoming posts to sustain social momentum (01:00)\nImplement China traffic filter in Google Analytics and dashboards for cleaner data reporting (08:50)\nPull and share detailed December campaign conversion data post-meeting (18:52)\nPrepare to review monthly traffic data with team in weekly meetings including after China filter applied (07:48)\nArrange follow-up call with Tristan to explore private market snapshot report tool and its suitability for Cedra campaigns (15:30)\nCollaborate with ABM expert to develop refined cold email approaches and targeted paid media retargeting campaigns (16:45)\nMonitor campaign improvements and advise on adjustments based on lead generation progress (12:58)\n"},"migrated_from":"contract_meetings","original_id":"3403894e-2756-4951-bf44-9d3402a04b99","master_marketer":{"status":"migrated"}}'::jsonb,
