  '[{"text":"Verify Arabic language compatibility for the chat feature in the product UI to support Arabic market promotions (03:49)","completed":false},{"text":"Follow up internally and externally regarding Richard Evans and London event participation decision (09:18)","completed":false},{"text":"Continue nurturing long sales cycle leads, including the major law firm proof of concept and scheduled demos such as Quinn Emanuel (20:10)","completed":false},{"text":"Search emails and reconnect with Brown Rudnick contact from 2019 to explore opportunities (27:25)","completed":false},{"text":"Share new blog post about AI Investigator for promotion; coordinate with Fahad for adding his input and social shares (01:41)","completed":false},{"text":"Finalize demo video focused on AI Investigator feature as a campaign teaser (12:31)","completed":false},{"text":"Provide Arabic translations for updated website features and functionalities page after confirming chat feature support (03:27)","completed":false},{"text":"Send topic ideas document to Fahad for upcoming posts to sustain social momentum (01:00)","completed":false},{"text":"Implement China traffic filter in Google Analytics and dashboards for cleaner data reporting (08:50)","completed":false},{"text":"Pull and share detailed December campaign conversion data post-meeting (18:52)","completed":false},{"text":"Prepare to review monthly traffic data with team in weekly meetings including after China filter applied (07:48)","completed":false},{"text":"Arrange follow-up call with Tristan to explore private market snapshot report tool and its suitability for Cedra campaigns (15:30)","completed":false},{"text":"Collaborate with ABM expert to develop refined cold email approaches and targeted paid media retargeting campaigns (16:45)","completed":false},{"text":"Monitor campaign improvements and advise on adjustments based on lead generation progress (12:58)","completed":false}]'::jsonb,
