    594,
    'https://us02web.zoom.us/j/83554814286?pwd=CdVF8IPCUBu1PT4HM51g2XqaHTZxDK.1',
    '{"id":"01KECPXV0WGW62ZXVM574R9D7N","title":"Taylor Doerbaum and Nigel Sapp","summary":{"notes":"## **SEO Performance and Traffic Trends**\n\nThe December SEO report showed mixed results influenced by the holiday season, with notable gains in engagement despite overall traffic dips (02:24).\n\n- **Time on page increased significantly in December**, signaling stronger user engagement despite typical holiday slowdowns.\n    - Direct traffic dipped slightly compared to November’s high, reflecting expected seasonal behavior.\n    - Page traffic on main landing pages decreased, but many blog pages saw solid increases.\n    - The new Christmas merchandise page recorded an extraordinary **84,000% traffic increase**, likely due to it being new and highly relevant.\n- **Year-over-year comparison for 2025 versus 2024 revealed broad growth across most pages**, except a minor drop on the homepage.\n    - Top-performing pages saw significant gains, supporting a positive trend in organic reach.\n    - A new blog launched in 2025 attracted high traffic, but lacked prior-year data for comparison.\n- **SEO score improved by one point from the previous month**, with ongoing developer recommendations provided to maintain optimization.\n    - Taylor emphasized continuing to monitor and apply these developer recommendations for steady SEO health.\n\n## **Podcast Production and Publishing Strategy**\n\nPodcast efforts are undergoing a staffing shift and a temporary slowdown in new content, with plans to delegate tasks and adjust meeting cadence (05:34).\n\n- **Nigel introduced an intern, Nikki, who will manage podcast publishing and coordination**, reducing Nigel’s direct involvement.\n    - Nigel plans to have Nikki handle backlog episode reviews and new publishing tasks starting mid-January.\n    - Podcast output in Q1 2025 may be limited as Nigel focuses on other priorities and Nikki ramps up.\n- **Meeting frequency will shift from weekly to biweekly, focusing on the first and third weeks of each month**, aligning with SEO reporting and workload.\n    - Taylor will update calendar invites accordingly and include Nikki in communications.\n- **Publishing of backlog podcast episodes is paused temporarily until Nikki completes listening and editing**, with updates forthcoming.\n    - This approach aims to ensure quality control as the intern acclimates and takes ownership.\n    - Nigel expressed appreciation for the added support, highlighting operational bandwidth constraints.\n\n## **Communication and Workflow Adjustments**\n\nThe team is streamlining communication and task ownership to improve efficiency amid shifting responsibilities (07:47).\n\n- **Taylor will tag Nikki alongside Nigel on Slack messages related to the careers board and podcast updates**, ensuring smooth handoff.\n    - Nigel confirmed Nikki is already actively handling assigned tasks and will continue to do so.\n- **Nigel will attend an offsite next week, so Nikki will represent him in meetings starting the week after**, maintaining continuity.\n- **This structured delegation reflects a broader effort to balance workload while sustaining content delivery and SEO monitoring.**\n\n## **Strategic Outlook and Resource Allocation**\n\nLeadership is prioritizing resource shifts and process adjustments to maintain growth momentum with limited capacity (06:01).\n\n- **Nigel’s decision to onboard an intern reflects a strategic choice to delegate operational tasks**, allowing him to focus on higher-level priorities.\n    - This aligns with plans to slow new podcast production temporarily without sacrificing quality.\n- **The SEO and content teams remain aligned on maintaining steady progress through ongoing monitoring and incremental improvements**, as evidenced by the modest SEO score increase.\n- **Biweekly check-ins and clearer task ownership aim to improve coordination and responsiveness during this transition period.**","outline":null,"keywords":["SEO report","podcast publishing","intern onboarding","website traffic","content updates","meeting schedule"],"overview":"- **SEO Traffic Trends:** December saw mixed SEO results; engagement up, but direct traffic dipped slightly during holidays.  \n- **Notable Traffic Increase:** New Christmas merchandise page had an **84,000% traffic increase**, with solid gains on many blog pages.  \n- **Year-Over-Year Growth:** 2025 showed broad growth in most areas except homepage; new blog attracted high traffic with no prior data.  \n- **Podcast Staffing Changes:** Intern Nikki will manage podcast tasks, reducing Nigel''s involvement as they adjust meeting frequency to biweekly.  \n- **Communication Improvements:** Nikki will tag alongside Nigel on relevant communications, ensuring smooth transitions during staffing changes.  \n- **Strategic Resource Allocation:** Leadership focuses on delegating tasks to maintain growth, while monitoring SEO health amid operational adjustments.","action_items":"\n**Taylor Doerbaum**\nAdjust meeting calendar invitations to biweekly occurrence on the first and third weeks of the month (07:36)\nContinue tagging Nikki and Nigel on Slack when sending over career board related communications (08:25)\nMonitor and await podcast updates for new episode publishing decisions (08:59)\n\n**Nigel Sapp**\nSend over the recorded podcast episode with Alan from Slack to the team for production (05:55)\nBegin onboarding intern Nikki to handle podcast publishing, editing, and related New North tasks, and keep Taylor informed (06:18)\nTransition meeting participation and communications to include Nikki, especially for content and career board matters (08:13)\nUpdate on podcast backlog episode review progress and potential publishing schedule (08:50)\n"},"duration":9.899999618530273,"speakers":[{"id":0,"name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"id":1,"name":"Nigel Sapp"}],"sentences":[{"text":"Hello.","index":0,"end_time":15.92,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":15.6,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Hey, Taylor.","index":1,"end_time":17.16,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":16.4,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Happy New Year.","index":2,"end_time":17.84,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":17.16,"speaker_name":"Nigel Sapp"},{"text":"Happy New Year.","index":3,"end_time":19.2,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":18.16,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"How was your holidays?","index":4,"end_time":20.48,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":19.2,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Christmas, New Year''s?","index":5,"end_time":21.84,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":20.48,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Yeah, they were good.","index":6,"end_time":23.6,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":22.48,"speaker_name":"Nigel Sapp"},{"text":"I was.","index":7,"end_time":24.6,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":24.08,"speaker_name":"Nigel Sapp"},{"text":"I was home.","index":8,"end_time":25.28,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":24.6,"speaker_name":"Nigel Sapp"},{"text":"It was really nice, and.","index":9,"end_time":27.04,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":25.36,"speaker_name":"Nigel Sapp"},{"text":"Yeah, very, very relaxing and just, like, able to kind of decompress and get away from work, which is all very, very good.","index":10,"end_time":33.24,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":27.8,"speaker_name":"Nigel Sapp"},{"text":"That is great.","index":11,"end_time":34.52,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":33.64,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Thank you.","index":12,"end_time":36.04,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":35.48,"speaker_name":"Nigel Sapp"},{"text":"How.","index":13,"end_time":36.52,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":36.12,"speaker_name":"Nigel Sapp"},{"text":"How are yours?","index":14,"end_time":37.4,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":36.52,"speaker_name":"Nigel Sapp"},{"text":"We all got sick, so it was different than planned.","index":15,"end_time":41.04,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":38.52,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":16,"end_time":41.4,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":41.04,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Okay.","index":17,"end_time":42.16,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":41.56,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Apologies.","index":18,"end_time":42.8,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":42.16,"speaker_name":"Nigel Sapp"},{"text":"I''m sorry.","index":19,"end_time":43.32,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":42.8,"speaker_name":"Nigel Sapp"},{"text":"I feel like so many people did, though.","index":20,"end_time":44.96,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":43.559,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"I feel like it was kind of a thing this year, but.","index":21,"end_time":46.64,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":44.96,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Yeah, pretty much like a flu.","index":22,"end_time":48.12,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":46.64,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"There''s, like, a flu going around.","index":23,"end_time":49.2,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":48.12,"speaker_name":"Nigel Sapp"},{"text":"I remember.","index":24,"end_time":49.76,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":49.2,"speaker_name":"Nigel Sapp"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":25,"end_time":50.2,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":49.76,"speaker_name":"Nigel Sapp"},{"text":"Yeah, it''s.","index":26,"end_time":51.24,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":50.44,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"It was awful.","index":27,"end_time":52.12,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":51.24,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"We were all together at least, so that''s good.","index":28,"end_time":53.88,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":52.12,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"But.","index":29,"end_time":54.28,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":53.88,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Yeah, that''s good.","index":30,"end_time":55.64,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":54.68,"speaker_name":"Nigel Sapp"},{"text":"Were all spruting it to each other.","index":31,"end_time":57.58,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":56.26,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"No, exactly.","index":32,"end_time":58.74,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":57.58,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"It was good.","index":33,"end_time":59.62,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":58.9,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"No, but, yeah.","index":34,"end_time":61.22,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":59.62,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"And now I live in Texas, and the cedar allergies right now are, like, insane.","index":35,"end_time":65.5,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":61.22,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"And so, like, even though I''ve recovered from being sick, I.","index":36,"end_time":68.74,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":65.5,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Me and my husband have both been, like, sneezing, like, 30 times a day.","index":37,"end_time":71.78,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":68.74,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"It''s just.","index":38,"end_time":72.42,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":71.78,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Yeah, that.","index":39,"end_time":75.02,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":74.42,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"That.","index":40,"end_time":75.34,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":75.02,"speaker_name":"Nigel Sapp"},{"text":"That''s tough.","index":41,"end_time":76.14,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":75.34,"speaker_name":"Nigel Sapp"},{"text":"That''s tough, Chief.","index":42,"end_time":76.98,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":76.14,"speaker_name":"Nigel Sapp"},{"text":"I know.","index":43,"end_time":77.58,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":77.06,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"I need it to, like, get colder here because it''s been so warm, like, abnormally.","index":44,"end_time":81.46,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":77.58,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"It''s been in the 80s that I''m like, come on.","index":45,"end_time":83.54,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":81.46,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"So everything''s just floating around.","index":46,"end_time":85.46,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":83.62,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":47,"end_time":86.42,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":86.02,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"All the pollen.","index":48,"end_time":87.26,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":86.42,"speaker_name":"Nigel Sapp"},{"text":"I. I mean, that.","index":49,"end_time":88.01,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":87.26,"speaker_name":"Nigel Sapp"},{"text":"The thing I feel like living in the south is like, yes.","index":50,"end_time":90.48,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":88.16,"speaker_name":"Nigel Sapp"},{"text":"You''ll see more pollen than you ever thought you could in your life.","index":51,"end_time":94.24,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":90.72,"speaker_name":"Nigel Sapp"},{"text":"Everything is yellow.","index":52,"end_time":95.52,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":94.48,"speaker_name":"Nigel Sapp"},{"text":"It''s awful.","index":53,"end_time":96.8,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":96,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Yeah, it.","index":54,"end_time":98.4,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":97.68,"speaker_name":"Nigel Sapp"},{"text":"It.","index":55,"end_time":98.68,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":98.4,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"It.","index":56,"end_time":99.04,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":98.68,"speaker_name":"Nigel Sapp"},{"text":"I remember as a kid, like, the kids who.","index":57,"end_time":101.44,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":99.12,"speaker_name":"Nigel Sapp"},{"text":"Like, there were kids who just couldn''t even go out to recess because the pollen was too bad, and I was like, yeah.","index":58,"end_time":106.24,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":101.52,"speaker_name":"Nigel Sapp"},{"text":"And I''ve never.","index":59,"end_time":107.28,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":106.4,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"I''ve never really experienced that, being from New York.","index":60,"end_time":109.92,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":107.36,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Like, it''s like you had a couple of things pop up, but, geez, this is kicking my butt.","index":61,"end_time":114.24,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":109.92,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"And we moved, and there''s way more, like, green space behind us in this new house, and so I think that that''s contributing to this.","index":62,"end_time":122.22,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":114.56,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"So that''s a bummer.","index":63,"end_time":125.74,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":122.78,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"But it''s all good.","index":64,"end_time":127.42,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":125.74,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Totally.","index":65,"end_time":129.62,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":129.02,"speaker_name":"Nigel Sapp"},{"text":"Well, hey, I hope.","index":66,"end_time":132.86,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":129.62,"speaker_name":"Nigel Sapp"},{"text":"I hope you''re getting beyond it a little bit, and thank you.","index":67,"end_time":135.78,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":132.86,"speaker_name":"Nigel Sapp"},{"text":"Me too.","index":68,"end_time":136.22,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":135.78,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Yeah, things happen.","index":69,"end_time":138.38,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":136.62,"speaker_name":"Nigel Sapp"},{"text":"We''ll see.","index":70,"end_time":139.18,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":138.62,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"There could be worse things.","index":71,"end_time":140.74,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":139.66,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"So I''m all good.","index":72,"end_time":141.58,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":140.74,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Completely.","index":73,"end_time":142.62,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":142.06,"speaker_name":"Nigel Sapp"},{"text":"Yeah, completely.","index":74,"end_time":143.5,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":142.62,"speaker_name":"Nigel Sapp"},{"text":"Great.","index":75,"end_time":144.69,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":144.45,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Well, I have the December SEO report for you today.","index":76,"end_time":147.97,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":144.85,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"And then I also went ahead and compiled data from just full 20, 25 and did a comparison from the previous year, so we can go.","index":77,"end_time":155.73,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":147.97,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Right on.","index":78,"end_time":157.01,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":156.45,"speaker_name":"Nigel Sapp"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":79,"end_time":157.73,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":157.25,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"So just getting into December, the time on page increased significantly, which was interesting to see because as you''ll notice as we go through the December report, there was a lot of decrease because of the holidays, which is something we always notice across the board.","index":80,"end_time":172.29,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":157.97,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Yeah, time on page did increase pretty significantly, so that''s just something good to note.","index":81,"end_time":177.99,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":172.69,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"But yeah, like I said, we have a note in here.","index":82,"end_time":181.55,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":179.59,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"We just tell all of our clients usually in December that''s when web traffic goes down because nobody''s really looking to do anything during the holidays.","index":83,"end_time":188.63,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":181.55,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"The direct traffic did increase a little bit, but just compared to the previous month in November, which was pretty high.","index":84,"end_time":195.31,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":189.51,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"We had a lot of increase that month.","index":85,"end_time":196.75,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":195.31,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"It just dipped a little bit lower.","index":86,"end_time":198.31,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":196.75,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Nice.","index":87,"end_time":199.27,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":198.79,"speaker_name":"Nigel Sapp"},{"text":"And then same for page traffic.","index":88,"end_time":202.27,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":199.59,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"We did have a lot of blogs though that had an increase.","index":89,"end_time":204.55,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":202.27,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Some were higher than others obviously.","index":90,"end_time":207.12,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":204.63,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"But yeah, a lot of those just main landing pages got a little bit lower due to the holiday season.","index":91,"end_time":213.84,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":207.76,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"But again, to be expected.","index":92,"end_time":215.28,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":213.84,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"This Christmas page though, 84,000%.","index":93,"end_time":220.4,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":215.92,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"I know, I was looking at it and it''s cool.","index":94,"end_time":223.24,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":221.28,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"I didn''t know you guys like had merch, so that''s awesome.","index":95,"end_time":226.8,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":223.24,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Yeah, yeah.","index":96,"end_time":228,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":226.96,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Tyranny.","index":97,"end_time":228.96,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":228.32,"speaker_name":"Nigel Sapp"},{"text":"Put.","index":98,"end_time":229.28,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":228.96,"speaker_name":"Nigel Sapp"},{"text":"Put all that together.","index":99,"end_time":230.48,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":229.44,"speaker_name":"Nigel Sapp"},{"text":"That''s really cool though, to see.","index":100,"end_time":232.4,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":231.04,"speaker_name":"Nigel Sapp"},{"text":"Yes.","index":101,"end_time":233.46,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":233.18,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":102,"end_time":233.82,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":233.46,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"So I just wanted to provide that statistic.","index":103,"end_time":235.66,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":233.82,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"I know it''s probably a new page, that''s why I had such a big increase.","index":104,"end_time":238.3,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":235.82,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"But I thought it was just cool to.","index":105,"end_time":240.22,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":238.3,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"To give you that data so you could see how that looks.","index":106,"end_time":244.22,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":240.22,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"But.","index":107,"end_time":244.54,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":244.22,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"But yeah, so that''s for December.","index":108,"end_time":248.14,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":244.62,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"And so then just going into 2025, I did a comparison of the stats just from 2024.","index":109,"end_time":255.26,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":248.94,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"So I did January to December of 25 and then it just.","index":110,"end_time":258.06,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":255.26,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Yeah, the data from 24 so direct was a little bit lower, but all the other pages increased very significantly over here.","index":111,"end_time":265.89,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":258.06,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"That''s great to see.","index":112,"end_time":267.93,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":266.93,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"And then I also just went through a couple of pages.","index":113,"end_time":270.53,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":267.93,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"I didn''t do like specific pages all in all, but I pulled a few just off the top.","index":114,"end_time":274.73,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":270.53,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Google Analytics sorted it for me, like the top performing pages.","index":115,"end_time":278.05,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":274.73,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"So I pulled it this way.","index":116,"end_time":280.05,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":278.45,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"So the only small, small decrease was the homepage.","index":117,"end_time":283.85,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":280.77,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Everything else had a big improvement over year to year.","index":118,"end_time":287.2,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":283.85,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"And then I know this new blog was a huge one, but it was new so there was no data to pull from previous years.","index":119,"end_time":293.24,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":287.68,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"But I just wanted to notate that one had really high traffic this year.","index":120,"end_time":297.28,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":293.24,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Let''s go.","index":121,"end_time":297.84,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":297.28,"speaker_name":"Nigel Sapp"},{"text":"That''s hype.","index":122,"end_time":298.96,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":298.24,"speaker_name":"Nigel Sapp"},{"text":"That''s awesome.","index":123,"end_time":299.68,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":298.96,"speaker_name":"Nigel Sapp"},{"text":"Yeah, so just wanted to show you that as far as the 2025 traffic.","index":124,"end_time":304.6,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":300,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"And then I have your AI overviews here.","index":125,"end_time":306.4,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":304.6,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"No change really here as well.","index":126,"end_time":309.92,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":308.24,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"And then SEO recommendations, the score went up.","index":127,"end_time":312.56,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":310.08,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Just one from our previous month, but that''s still good.","index":128,"end_time":315.69,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":312.56,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"And then we just included these recommendations again from our developer and he just sent these over to me again yesterday, so nothing really new to change there.","index":129,"end_time":322.57,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":315.69,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"And if you guys had made any of.","index":130,"end_time":324.33,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":322.57,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Make any of these, we''ll notice it.","index":131,"end_time":326.77,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":324.89,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"But just wanted to continue to give you these in case it was something you guys want to update on your end.","index":132,"end_time":332.01,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":326.77,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"For sure.","index":133,"end_time":332.93,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":332.33,"speaker_name":"Nigel Sapp"},{"text":"No, I appreciate that.","index":134,"end_time":334.01,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":332.93,"speaker_name":"Nigel Sapp"},{"text":"Yeah, of course.","index":135,"end_time":335.37,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":334.49,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"And then just as far as additional updates, I just didn''t know if you got a chance to look at the compilation video, if there was anything you wanted to edit there or around podcasts in general, if you had any updates or new or what.","index":136,"end_time":347.71,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":336.65,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"You want us to get publishing in the new year?","index":137,"end_time":349.59,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":347.71,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Totally.","index":138,"end_time":350.59,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":350.07,"speaker_name":"Nigel Sapp"},{"text":"I think, yes.","index":139,"end_time":351.23,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":350.59,"speaker_name":"Nigel Sapp"},{"text":"I do have an episode that we recorded with with our friend Alan from Slack, so.","index":140,"end_time":358.23,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":351.23,"speaker_name":"Nigel Sapp"},{"text":"So that''s what I need to still send over.","index":141,"end_time":361.15,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":358.95,"speaker_name":"Nigel Sapp"},{"text":"For sure.","index":142,"end_time":361.67,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":361.15,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"We are.","index":143,"end_time":363.35,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":362.71,"speaker_name":"Nigel Sapp"},{"text":"I think it''s possible.","index":144,"end_time":364.83,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":363.51,"speaker_name":"Nigel Sapp"},{"text":"It''s, like, looking pretty likely that.","index":145,"end_time":366.47,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":364.83,"speaker_name":"Nigel Sapp"},{"text":"Well, we''ll see.","index":146,"end_time":367.43,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":366.71,"speaker_name":"Nigel Sapp"},{"text":"I don''t know how many new episodes there will be in Q1, because I think our focus is gonna be mostly like.","index":147,"end_time":377.9,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":367.43,"speaker_name":"Nigel Sapp"},{"text":"Well, we''ll see because my focus will be in a lot of other places, but I have an intern now, as I''m sure you kind of saw, and so.","index":148,"end_time":384.3,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":377.98,"speaker_name":"Nigel Sapp"},{"text":"Thank you.","index":149,"end_time":385.1,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":384.54,"speaker_name":"Nigel Sapp"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":150,"end_time":385.38,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":385.1,"speaker_name":"Nigel Sapp"},{"text":"And so she''s gonna be helping out, actually, with a lot of stuff with like, New north, right.","index":151,"end_time":388.98,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":385.38,"speaker_name":"Nigel Sapp"},{"text":"Where it''s like, okay, how do we put you in charge of going to.","index":152,"end_time":394.06,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":388.98,"speaker_name":"Nigel Sapp"},{"text":"Making sure that all these things happen and we''re able to publish and so on and so on and so forth.","index":153,"end_time":400.3,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":395.98,"speaker_name":"Nigel Sapp"},{"text":"So.","index":154,"end_time":400.55,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":400.39,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"So, yeah, stay tuned for more updates from me there because I think next week and especially the week after is when I will start to, like, yeah, I''ll start to have her working on some of this stuff.","index":155,"end_time":422.54,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":400.78,"speaker_name":"Nigel Sapp"},{"text":"On that note, I think also too, in that case, for the time being, I don''t know if we really need to meet weekly.","index":156,"end_time":428.99,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":423.18,"speaker_name":"Nigel Sapp"},{"text":"I think we could probably meet every two weeks because I think.","index":157,"end_time":432.87,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":428.99,"speaker_name":"Nigel Sapp"},{"text":"Yeah, I just think until you, like, ramp up or ramp back up on, like, podcast, like, we''re kind of, you know, it''s like we''re kind of good for the time being, so.","index":158,"end_time":444.63,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":432.87,"speaker_name":"Nigel Sapp"},{"text":"So, yeah, I think continuing to send over, like, the careers board stuff is helpful.","index":159,"end_time":450.71,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":445.83,"speaker_name":"Nigel Sapp"},{"text":"But, yeah, I think we can meet every two weeks and that would probably be best.","index":160,"end_time":455.67,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":451.11,"speaker_name":"Nigel Sapp"},{"text":"Okay.","index":161,"end_time":456.71,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":456.15,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Yeah, we can adjust that.","index":162,"end_time":457.83,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":456.71,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Do you want it to be the first and third week?","index":163,"end_time":459.87,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":457.83,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"The second.","index":164,"end_time":460.35,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":459.87,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"And yeah, I think.","index":165,"end_time":462.31,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":460.35,"speaker_name":"Nigel Sapp"},{"text":"I think first and third.","index":166,"end_time":464.31,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":463.03,"speaker_name":"Nigel Sapp"},{"text":"Okay, perfect.","index":167,"end_time":465.67,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":464.71,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Because then we can do the SEO report and everything the first week.","index":168,"end_time":467.95,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":465.67,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Exactly.","index":169,"end_time":468.35,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":467.95,"speaker_name":"Nigel Sapp"},{"text":"On the first week.","index":170,"end_time":468.95,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":468.35,"speaker_name":"Nigel Sapp"},{"text":"Yep, that''s.","index":171,"end_time":469.51,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":468.95,"speaker_name":"Nigel Sapp"},{"text":"That''s what I was thinking as well.","index":172,"end_time":470.63,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":469.51,"speaker_name":"Nigel Sapp"},{"text":"But that''s really it on my end.","index":173,"end_time":473.27,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":471.83,"speaker_name":"Nigel Sapp"},{"text":"So I don''t really have any updates for anything here except for, like, I have that one new episode for you guys to go spin up.","index":174,"end_time":478.07,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":473.27,"speaker_name":"Nigel Sapp"},{"text":"But again, a lot of the communication going forward will, I think, be happening with.","index":175,"end_time":484.48,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":479.68,"speaker_name":"Nigel Sapp"},{"text":"And I''ll invite Nikki the intern as well to the meeting.","index":176,"end_time":489.8,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":485.04,"speaker_name":"Nigel Sapp"},{"text":"So, for example, next week, like, I''ll be at an off site, so I actually can''t even meet next week.","index":177,"end_time":494.16,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":489.8,"speaker_name":"Nigel Sapp"},{"text":"So they will be able to meet the week after, you know?","index":178,"end_time":497.52,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":495.119,"speaker_name":"Nigel Sapp"},{"text":"Right, yeah, that makes sense.","index":179,"end_time":499.6,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":497.84,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"When we send over the careers board things and stuff like that through Slack.","index":180,"end_time":503.4,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":499.68,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Do you want me to just tag her?","index":181,"end_time":504.48,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":503.4,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Do you want me to keep tagging you or.","index":182,"end_time":506,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":504.48,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Yep, tag.","index":183,"end_time":506.96,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":506.4,"speaker_name":"Nigel Sapp"},{"text":"Tag Nikki as well.","index":184,"end_time":508.32,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":506.96,"speaker_name":"Nigel Sapp"},{"text":"Because.","index":185,"end_time":509.72,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":509.36,"speaker_name":"Nigel Sapp"},{"text":"Yeah, that''s kind of.","index":186,"end_time":510.8,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":509.72,"speaker_name":"Nigel Sapp"},{"text":"She''ll know, like.","index":187,"end_time":511.64,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":510.88,"speaker_name":"Nigel Sapp"},{"text":"Okay, cool.","index":188,"end_time":512.4,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":511.64,"speaker_name":"Nigel Sapp"},{"text":"You know, she just.","index":189,"end_time":513.64,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":512.88,"speaker_name":"Nigel Sapp"},{"text":"She just.","index":190,"end_time":514.04,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":513.64,"speaker_name":"Nigel Sapp"},{"text":"I just went.","index":191,"end_time":514.56,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":514.04,"speaker_name":"Nigel Sapp"},{"text":"Had her do something yesterday and so then she''ll go and do some more today.","index":192,"end_time":518.16,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":514.56,"speaker_name":"Nigel Sapp"},{"text":"Okay, great.","index":193,"end_time":519.6,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":518.88,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"So then as far as publishing any of the ones that we have in the backlog, you want to wait on that as well?","index":194,"end_time":524.28,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":519.76,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"We are not going to publish any upcoming.","index":195,"end_time":526.32,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":524.28,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"We.","index":196,"end_time":527.4,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":527.04,"speaker_name":"Nigel Sapp"},{"text":"We might.","index":197,"end_time":528.16,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":527.4,"speaker_name":"Nigel Sapp"},{"text":"I think actually we might coming up here soon.","index":198,"end_time":531.52,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":528.56,"speaker_name":"Nigel Sapp"},{"text":"I just need to have Nikki go and like, listen to them all.","index":199,"end_time":537.21,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":532.81,"speaker_name":"Nigel Sapp"},{"text":"Like, I''m trying to get her acclimated to like, listening and editing and everything.","index":200,"end_time":541.21,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":537.21,"speaker_name":"Nigel Sapp"},{"text":"And so.","index":201,"end_time":542.33,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":541.61,"speaker_name":"Nigel Sapp"},{"text":"So, yeah, I''ll keep you guys posted on kind of how.","index":202,"end_time":547.21,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":543.69,"speaker_name":"Nigel Sapp"},{"text":"How we advance with that.","index":203,"end_time":548.73,"speaker_i