_id":1,"start_time":273.119,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Like just enough to annoy us all, but we can''t.","index":91,"end_time":278.639,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":275.279,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"But.","index":92,"end_time":279.239,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":278.959,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"And so we''ve been trying different ways of transferring files, like we''re not using Google now.","index":93,"end_time":283.039,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":279.239,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"We''re using a transfer folder.","index":94,"end_time":284.559,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":283.039,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"It''s just.","index":95,"end_time":284.959,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":284.559,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"It''s really weird and it''s driving us all nuts, so.","index":96,"end_time":287.379,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":284.959,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"So, yeah, we can''t quite figure it out.","index":97,"end_time":290.13,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":287.61,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"So it''s no one''s fault.","index":98,"end_time":291.45,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":290.13,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"We just think it''s a technical glitch somewhere and it could be me, Lou.","index":99,"end_time":296.53,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":291.45,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"It could be me.","index":100,"end_time":297.37,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":296.53,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"It could be me.","index":101,"end_time":298.25,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":297.45,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"I don''t know.","index":102,"end_time":299.69,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":299.05,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"I think one other thing we could try is because right now, like, we tried with the transfer folder, but I''m still the one putting it in the transfer folder, so it might make sense if we could get it directly from the designer to that folder.","index":103,"end_time":314.41,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":300.33,"speaker_name