tart_time":512.48,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Would you still like us to include the icons, though?","index":176,"end_time":517.09,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":514.77,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"I think it''s all gotta go.","index":177,"end_time":519.53,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":518.29,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"I don''t think the icons make sense.","index":178,"end_time":520.89,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":519.53,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"So, Linea, what''s happening here is I asked the team if they could take a schwack at the Optimizer solution overview.","index":179,"end_time":527.05,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":520.89,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"And just make it a little bit more swishy.","index":180,"end_time":529.01,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":527.05,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"There''s some things that need to happen with it before.","index":181,"end_time":534.21,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":529.81,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"I was gonna show you, so.","index":182,"end_time":536.61,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":534.21,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"So take it with a grain of salt.","index":183,"end_time":538.05,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":536.69,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"It''s still in a bit of a draft, but just the team did such a lovely job on the intros that I wanted them to take a.","index":184,"end_time":544.21,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":538.05,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"A smack at the overview and see if they could streamline it a little better, make it look a little bit more professional.","index":185,"end_time":551.16,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":545.24,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"The only thing we were talking about were these.","index":186,"end_time":554.6,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":552.44,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"And because this video is global, Natalie, when we add English into the video, that means it''s harder to use in Italy or Germany or anywhere else that does not speak English.","index":187,"end_time":569.32,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":554.76,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"So I think this entire section, I think, has to go, unfortunately.","index":188,"end_time":573.48,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":569.56,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Okay.","index":189,"end_time":575.05,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":574.57,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":190,"end_time":575.93,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":575.45,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Because I don''t want to get into having to translate.","index":191,"end_time":578.97,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":576.73,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"You know, we''re gonna have to have.","index":192,"end_time":580.69,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":579.05,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Some words on it or.","index":193,"end_time":581.97,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":580.69,"speaker_name":"Linnea Wolken"},{"text":"What were you thinking, Roz?","index":194,"end_time":583.05,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":581.97,"speaker_name":"Linnea Wolken"},{"text":"If there''s no words on the screen there.","index":195,"end_time":585.93,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":583.05,"speaker_name":"Linnea Wolken"},{"text":"The original video that we had, we didn''t have this.","index":196,"end_time":588.89,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":586.01,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"We were just test driving this to.","index":197,"end_time":590.45,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":588.89,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"See how it would go.","index":198,"end_time":591.53,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":590.45,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"And I think it just needs to go back to the original where I was talking over the.","index":199,"end_time":598.81,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":592.17,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"I think it was a picture of the optimizer GUI that was here.","index":200,"end_time":602.64,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":598.81,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"I''d have to go back and remind myself.","index":201,"end_time":604.2,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":602.64,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"But this just didn''t ex.","index":202,"end_time":605.28,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":604.2,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"It didn''t even exist in the original because.","index":203,"end_time":608.76,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":605.28,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Yeah, just talking out loud with you folks.","index":204,"end_time":611.08,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":608.84,"speaker_name":"Linnea Wolken"},{"text":"Because if you''re talking, they have to anyway do subtitles for your voiceover, correct?","index":205,"end_time":617.64,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":611.88,"speaker_name":"Linnea Wolken"},{"text":"Yeah, but subtitles is easier to manage.","index":206,"end_time":620.6,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":618.44,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"This is baked right into the actual videos.","index":207,"end_time":626.6,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":620.68,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"So if I''m still talking, like, there''s still a voiceover talking over even this section here.","index":208,"end_time":631.96,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":626.6,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"So how do you translate it?","index":209,"end_time":633.84,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":631.96,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"You know what I mean?","index":210,"end_time":634.36,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":633.84,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"It was like that thing that I had to do for the guys in Germany when they wanted to translate everything over.","index":211,"end_time":640,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":634.36,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"I was able to do that because I created the videos myself and I could, you know, and they gave me that translation directly.","index":212,"end_time":647.84,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":640,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Whereas if we do it, if we do it here, it just opens up a can of worms that I think could be a little bit painful because the.","index":213,"end_time":656,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":649.04,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"The English is baked in while there''s a voiceover going as well.","index":214,"end_time":659.6,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":656.4,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Yeah, no, I totally understand.","index":215,"end_time":661.32,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":660.12,"speaker_name":"Linnea Wolken"},{"text":"So is there a way you''re conveying this instead of having the words on the screen besides talking to it?","index":216,"end_time":666.68,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":661.64,"speaker_name":"Linnea Wolken"},{"text":"But visually?","index":217,"end_time":667.48,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":666.68,"speaker_name":"Linnea Wolken"},{"text":"Yeah, yeah.","index":218,"end_time":669.2,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":668.12,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Like I said, I. I want to say that there was an image of the gui, like, creating a batch as this is happening, like over the top.","index":219,"end_time":680.08,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":669.2,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"I just have to look.","index":220,"end_time":681.08,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":680.08,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"So the image, the imagery does show it.","index":221,"end_time":683.64,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":681.08,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"It''s just some movement on the screen.","index":222,"end_time":685.44,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":683.64,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Yeah, within the gui.","index":223,"end_time":686.76,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":685.44,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Cool.","index":224,"end_time":687.24,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":686.76,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"As long as we visually show it somehow.","index":225,"end_time":689.5,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":687.58,"speaker_name":"Linnea Wolken"},{"text":"Because some people, you know, aren''t listening.","index":226,"end_time":691.66,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":689.5,"speaker_name":"Linnea Wolken"},{"text":"Will say, just viewing it with the sound off.","index":227,"end_time":694.86,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":691.66,"speaker_name":"Linnea Wolken"},{"text":"So.","index":228,"end_time":695.22,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":694.86,"speaker_name":"Linnea Wolken"},{"text":"Yeah, that''s fine.","index":229,"end_time":696.06,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":695.22,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"That''s fine.","index":230,"end_time":696.46,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":696.06,"speaker_name":"Linnea Wolken"},{"text":"I was just curious.","index":231,"end_time":697.02,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":696.46,"speaker_name":"Linnea Wolken"},{"text":"Thanks for.","index":232,"end_time":697.54,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":697.02,"speaker_name":"Linnea Wolken"},{"text":"Yeah, no, no, you''re.","index":233,"end_time":699.18,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":697.54,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"You''re welcome.","index":234,"end_time":699.82,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":699.18,"speaker_name":"Linnea Wolken"},{"text":"Because the front end of it, where it does say Ricoh, you know, total flow optimizer solution overview, that I don''t think I''m really saying too much there, so I was kind of okay with that.","index":235,"end_time":712.54,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":700.62,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"But this in the middle, I was a little hesitant with, so.","index":236,"end_time":716.14,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":712.54,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"And do we have something on integration?","index":237,"end_time":718.34,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":716.7,"speaker_name":"Linnea Wolken"},{"text":"Just because I had to write a statement for a selling thing and I''m like, you know, besides the operations, it was all about automatic processes and integrations.","index":238,"end_time":727.46,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":718.34,"speaker_name":"Linnea Wolken"},{"text":"That''s perfect.","index":239,"end_time":728.1,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":727.46,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Yeah, yeah.","index":240,"end_time":728.82,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":728.1,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"This.","index":241,"end_time":729.1,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":728.82,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"I can send you this script if you like.","index":242,"end_time":731.34,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":729.1,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"I''ll wait till you want to show it to me.","index":243,"end_time":733.98,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":731.98,"speaker_name":"Linnea Wolken"},{"text":"Okay, thank you.","index":244,"end_time":735.18,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":734.22,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"We''re not quite there.","index":245,"end_time":736.98,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":736.14,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"It''s not quite ready for you yet.","index":246,"end_time":738.3,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":736.98,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Because I''m like, no, that''s not going to.","index":247,"end_time":739.66,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":738.3,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":248,"end_time":740.27,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":740.07,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"We''re just doing some final fine tuning on it.","index":249,"end_time":742.79,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":740.27,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"But it is coming along and I like.","index":250,"end_time":745.63,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":742.79,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"The transitions are a bit nicer.","index":251,"end_time":747.75,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":745.63,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Natalie, would you mind just playing this a little bit, the front part of it for linear, so she can just see maybe the first little bit.","index":252,"end_time":754.55,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":748.15,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Don''t have to go through the whole thing.","index":253,"end_time":755.91,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":754.55,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Yeah, yeah.","index":254,"end_time":759.31,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":756.55,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"So there''s movement, solution, overview.","index":255,"end_time":762.71,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":759.31,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"And then it does these nice translations transitions with the balloon.","index":256,"end_time":767.64,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":763.83,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"I know it''s really quick, but that is the balloon.","index":257,"end_time":769.96,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":767.64,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Balloon.","index":258,"end_time":773.44,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":773.08,"speaker_name":"Linnea Wolken"},{"text":"I''m slow.","index":259,"end_time":774.04,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":773.44,"speaker_name":"Linnea Wolken"},{"text":"And then it does this, which we''re.","index":260,"end_time":777.88,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":775.16,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"We''re gonna remove and we''ll do something.","index":261,"end_time":780.4,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":778.2,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"See, there''s the balloon right there.","index":262,"end_time":781.88,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":780.4,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Dumb question.","index":263,"end_time":785.32,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":784.52,"speaker_name":"Linnea Wolken"},{"text":"The font being used, it didn''t look like Ariel or Helvetica or whatever the heck card is.","index":264,"end_time":791.16,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":785.48,"speaker_name":"Linnea Wolken"},{"text":"Well, it''s going.","index":265,"end_time":792.04,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":791.4,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"It''s going away anyway, so.","index":266,"end_time":793.88,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":792.04,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Yeah, I made up the title.","index":267,"end_time":796.19,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":794.19,"speaker_name":"Linnea Wolken"},{"text":"Oh, okay.","index":268,"end_time":797.19,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":796.51,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"We''ll check on that as well.","index":269,"end_time":798.39,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":797.19,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":270,"end_time":798.79,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":798.39,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"If.","index":271,"end_time":799.11,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":798.79,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Natalie, if that could be Frutiger.","index":272,"end_time":802.67,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":799.11,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"I think it is.","index":273,"end_time":803.31,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":802.67,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"It looks.","index":274,"end_time":803.79,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":803.31,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"I knew it wasn''t.","index":275,"end_time":805.15,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":804.35,"speaker_name":"Linnea Wolken"},{"text":"No.","index":276,"end_time":806.63,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":806.27,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Frutiger.","index":277,"end_time":807.19,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":806.63,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Yeah, I think it is Frutiger.","index":278,"end_time":808.87,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":807.19,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"I thought it was Frutiger.","index":279,"end_time":810.03,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":808.87,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"It looked Frutigeri to me.","index":280,"end_time":811.79,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":810.03,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Is that a word?","index":281,"end_time":812.59,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":811.87,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Frutigeri.","index":282,"end_time":813.47,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":812.59,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"But yeah.","index":283,"end_time":816.19,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":815.71,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Natalie, if you could check that for me.","index":284,"end_time":817.79,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":816.19,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Yeah, yeah.","index":285,"end_time":818.63,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":817.95,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"And then we''ll double check.","index":286,"end_time":819.75,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":818.63,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":287,"end_time":820.42,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":820.22,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"And then maybe just with linea looking at it, if those transitions where it.","index":288,"end_time":824.46,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":820.42,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Where it''s showing the balloon can be a little bit slower, I think maybe that would be good.","index":289,"end_time":829.18,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":824.62,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"So you can see it.","index":290,"end_time":830.14,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":829.18,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Because it''s a nice little it.","index":291,"end_time":831.9,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":830.38,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"You know, it''s a nice transition and I don''t want to lose the feel of it.","index":292,"end_time":836.7,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":832.06,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"So.","index":293,"end_time":837.34,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":836.94,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":294,"end_time":837.74,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":837.42,"speaker_name":"Linnea Wolken"},{"text":"Because it was also a cool transition on a PowerPoint with the balloon, the imagination balloon.","index":295,"end_time":842.94,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":837.74,"speaker_name":"Linnea Wolken"},{"text":"And I haven''t even.","index":296,"end_time":843.82,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":842.94,"speaker_name":"Linnea Wolken"},{"text":"Someone showed it to me and I''m like, oh, that''s really cool.","index":297,"end_time":846.7,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":844.06,"speaker_name":"Linnea Wolken"},{"text":"And I still haven''t found it myself because that''s.","index":298,"end_time":849.24,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":846.7,"speaker_name":"Linnea Wolken"},{"text":"How bad is it?","index":299,"end_time":850.96,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":849.24,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"It''s not a morph.","index":300,"end_time":851.8,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":850.96,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Is Might have been the morph.","index":301,"end_time":854.44,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":851.8,"speaker_name":"Linnea Wolken"},{"text":"Yes, I think.","index":302,"end_time":855.24,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":854.44,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Yeah, yeah.","index":303,"end_time":856.32,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":855.32,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"And you have.","index":304,"end_time":856.92,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":856.32,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"The morph is kind of tricky.","index":305,"end_time":858.68,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":857.08,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"I find sometimes you have to plan things exactly right between one slide and the other for the morph to work in a way that makes sense.","index":306,"end_time":866.2,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":858.68,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"So I run into it myself.","index":307,"end_time":869.08,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":866.36,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"So.","index":308,"end_time":870.04,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":869.64,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":309,"end_time":870.48,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":870.12,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Anyway, so I think we''re coming along.","index":310,"end_time":871.76,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":870.48,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Nicely on this one, Natalie.","index":311,"end_time":873.32,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":871.76,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"I would love to do something similar for Info Print Manager and RPD as.","index":312,"end_time":879.17,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":874.13,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Well, because those are looking a little.","index":313,"end_time":880.81,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":879.17,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"They need some help and they''re looking a little dated.","index":314,"end_time":883.01,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":880.81,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"So once we get this one down and Linea, you''ve seen it and you''re happy with it.","index":315,"end_time":886.41,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":883.01,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"I''d like to use this as a maybe a little bit of a template.","index":316,"end_time":889.57,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":886.41,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"The also, one of the things that we added for the first time in this video was the shots of the hardware as well.","index":317,"end_time":900.46,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":891.01,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"That''s a vc.","index":318,"end_time":901.5,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":900.62,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"I was going to ask you a dumb question, but I said, oh, I''ll look at it later and make sure it''s Ricoh equipment.","index":319,"end_time":906.7,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":902.14,"speaker_name":"Linnea Wolken"},{"text":"It is, yeah, it''s, it''s I, I, I pirated, if you will, some VC80000 hardware.","index":320,"end_time":913.5,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":906.78,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Perfect videos.","index":321,"end_time":915.1,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":913.74,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"I''m like, oh, this is great.","index":322,"end_time":916.78,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":915.499,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Let''s slice that in.","index":323,"end_time":918.38,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":917.02,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"So, yeah, it''s a VC80000 you''re looking at.","index":324,"end_time":920.7,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":918.7,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"And yes, absolutely.","index":325,"end_time":921.62,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":920.7,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"It is Ricoh equipment.","index":326,"end_time":922.66,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":921.62,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"I wouldn''t dare put anything else in.","index":327,"end_time":924.3,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":922.66,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"So.","index":328,"end_time":924.7,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":924.3,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"And then will you do one for predictive insight or is that in the works already?","index":329,"end_time":929.09,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":925.57,"speaker_name":"Linnea Wolken"},{"text":"Predictive insight.","index":330,"end_time":931.89,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":930.77,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"I''m waiting on that new GUI from Miriam.","index":331,"end_time":934.45,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":931.89,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Okay.","index":332,"end_time":935.33,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":934.77,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"They''re changing something.","index":333,"end_time":936.69,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":935.41,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Yeah, they''re changing something with the gui and she''s like, don''t even talk to me until that''s done.","index":334,"end_time":941.05,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":937.01,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"I''m like, okay, good.","index":335,"end_time":941.97,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":941.05,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"I''m happy.","index":336,"end_time":942.49,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":941.97,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"I''m fine with that.","index":337,"end_time":943.17,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":942.49,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Thank you.","index":338,"end_time":943.73,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":943.17,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Yeah, that makes perfect sense.","index":339,"end_time":945.73,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":944.45,"speaker_name":"Linnea Wolken"},{"text":"No, I''m so excited.","index":340,"end_time":946.89,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":945.73,"speaker_name":"Linnea Wolken"},{"text":"So this is great.","index":341,"end_time":947.65,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":946.89,"speaker_name":"Linnea Wolken"},{"text":"Looking forward to seeing.","index":342,"end_time":948.45,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":947.65,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":343,"end_time":948.77,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":948.45,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":344,"end_time":949.49,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":949.01,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"So something a little bit new, which I think will be great.","index":345,"end_time":952.29,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":949.49,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"And I think it also is a better feel with the suite of everything else, like with what we''ve been creating with Lou and the, you know, the new templates for the PowerPoint and the brochures and everything else.","index":346,"end_time":965.48,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":952.88,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"I wanted to refresh at least these solution ones.","index":347,"end_time":968.48,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":965.48,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"I didn''t feel like I needed to get into too, too much with the, like, those how to videos that we''ve been doing, but they''ve all got a new, more animated intro anyway, so those have kind of been refreshed in that way as well.","index":348,"end_time":982.93,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":968.719,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"So, yeah, so everything''s getting a little.","index":349,"end_time":984.49,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":982.93,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"A little coat of paint, shall we say?","index":350,"end_time":987.05,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":984.73,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Yeah, yeah.","index":351,"end_time":989.69,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":987.37,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Okay.","index":352,"end_time":990.25,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":989.77,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Looking very good, Natalie.","index":353,"end_time":991.41,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":990.25,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Thank you so much.","index":354,"end_time":992.01,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":991.41,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"And please thank the team for me.","index":355,"end_time":993.25,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":992.01,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"It''s coming along.","index":356,"end_time":993.93,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":993.25,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Of course.","index":357,"end_time":995.25,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":994.73,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":358,"end_time":995.77,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":995.25,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"So, yeah, we''ll, we''ll make the updates to this and then we''ll test out the brochure.","index":359,"end_time":1001.13,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":996.17,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Just sending it through the transfer folder once you add.","index":360,"end_time":1004.49,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1001.29,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Okay.","index":361,"end_time":1005.86,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1005.5,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"And then we will get that change made to the website Linea.","index":362,"end_time":1008.86,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1005.86,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Oh, great.","index":363,"end_time":1010.02,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1009.42,"speaker_name":"Linnea Wolken"},{"text":"Thank you.","index":364,"end_time":1010.54,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1010.02,"speaker_name":"Linnea Wolken"},{"text":"So, quick question.","index":365,"end_time":1011.78,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1010.94,"speaker_name":"Linnea Wolken"},{"text":"Ros and team is so I know the brochure has a new look.","index":366,"end_time":1015.14,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1011.78,"speaker_name":"Linnea Wolken"},{"text":"PowerPoints have done a new look.","index":367,"end_time":1016.74,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1015.14,"speaker_name":"Linnea Wolken"},{"text":"I''m like going through my head, it''s like, okay, we have a sales guy, the battle card.","index":368,"end_time":1020.34,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1016.74,"speaker_name":"Linnea Wolken"},{"text":"We''ve done a new look.","index":369,"end_time":1021.099,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1020.34,"speaker_name":"Linnea Wolken"},{"text":"Does the sales guy have a new look as well?","index":370,"end_time":1023.18,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1021.099,"speaker_name":"Linnea Wolken"},{"text":"Yes, everything.","index":371,"end_time":1024.46,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1023.42,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Yes.","index":372,"end_time":1025.18,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1024.78,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"You''ll be seeing that for the first time with Info Print Manager.","index":373,"end_time":1028.22,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1025.18,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"I''m just.","index":374,"end_time":1028.7,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1028.22,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"The content is just being gone over by Vishnu right now.","index":375,"end_time":1032.06,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1028.7,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"But yeah, you had seen part of it.","index":376,"end_time":1034.62,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1032.3,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"We had talked about the COVID and keeping.","index":377,"end_time":1038,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1034.96,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Yeah, we had before.","index":378,"end_time":1039.6,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1038.32,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Yeah, but we had before.","index":379,"end_time":1040.8,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1039.68,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"When you see it, you''ll be like, oh yeah, I remember now.","index":380,"end_time":1043.28,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1040.88,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"But yes, if that has a new look and feel as well.","index":381,"end_time":1045.6,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1043.28,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Very cool.","index":382,"end_time":1046.8,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1046,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":383,"end_time":1048.24,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1047.84,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"So we''ve done it across all of our assets, basically.","index":384,"end_time":1050.88,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1048.24,"speaker_name":"Linnea Wolken"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":385,"end_time":1051.76,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1051.28,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Yeah, I would say so.","index":386,"end_time":1052.88,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1051.76,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Because we start.","index":387,"end_time":1053.68,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1052.88,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"We also combined a couple of things like the overview and the what''s new PowerPoint are now together so that Roz doesn''t lose her mind.","index":388,"end_time":1060.16,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1053.68,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"And then we''ve also combined the battle card to add that FAQ into it so that it''s positioning as well as the faq.","index":389,"end_time":1067.48,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1060.24,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"So again, we''re not doing two.","index":390,"end_time":1068.96,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1067.48,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Yeah, exactly.","index":391,"end_time":1070.16,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1069.04,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Love it, love it.","index":392,"end_time":1072.08,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1070.72,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"So one other area I was thinking.","index":393,"end_time":1074.12,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1072.48,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"About was the LMS classes and you know, the look and feel of it.","index":394,"end_time":1077.96,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1074.12,"speaker_name":"Linnea Wolken"},{"text":"But also I know we have a meeting later today with Chris is there''s big push and I don''t know if you guys have talked about it yet.","index":395,"end_time":1084.76,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1077.96,"speaker_name":"Linnea Wolken"},{"text":"Roz, I don''t want to reiterate if you have about training changes.","index":396,"end_time":1088.72,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1084.76,"speaker_name":"Linnea Wolken"},{"text":"No, I have not.","index":397,"end_time":1090.16,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1089.12,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Please.","index":398,"end_time":1091.35,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1091.15,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Do you want to address or do you want me to.","index":399,"end_time":1093.35,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1091.35,"speaker_name":"Linnea Wolken"},{"text":"No, go.","index":400,"end_time":1093.87,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1093.35,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Go for it.","index":401,"end_time":1094.35,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1093.87,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"You know more than I do, I think at this point.","index":402,"end_time":1096.19,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1094.35,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"So I don''t know.","index":403,"end_time":1097.11,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1096.19,"speaker_name":"Linnea Wolken"},{"text":"That''s a dangerous thing to say.","index":404,"end_time":1098.75,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1097.11,"speaker_name":"Linnea Wolken"},{"text":"I can''t even blame medicine anymore.","index":405,"end_time":1101.31,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1099.47,"speaker_name":"Linnea Wolken"},{"text":"It''s just stupidity and trying to put my brain back together after surgery.","index":406,"end_time":1105.15,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1101.31,"speaker_name":"Linnea Wolken"},{"text":"So with the training program we''ve been doing all these customer facing classes.","index":407,"end_time":1110.59,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1106.19,"speaker_name":"Linnea Wolken"},{"text":"Not customer, excuse me, internal classes for sellers.","index":408,"end_time":1114.11,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1111.07,"speaker_name":"Linnea Wolken"},{"text":"Teaching about our various products and taking assets you guys have created and they''re beautiful.","index":409,"end_time":1118.99,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1114.11,"speaker_name":"Linnea Wolken"},{"text":"And linking them in to make it more of an engaging experience for these online classes.","index":410,"end_time":1123.93,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1119.07,"speaker_name":"Linnea Wolken"},{"text":"And the shift is really starting where we''ve been asked with our limited bandwidth to also do more of customer facing training.","index":411,"end_time":1134.77,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1124.33,"speaker_name":"Linnea Wolken"},{"text":"So we''ve done RPD so far but there''s a big push to look at our other solutions and offer that.","index":412,"end_time":1140.97,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1134.77,"speaker_name":"Linnea Wolken"},{"text":"And the challenge is first I mentioned is resources and then the second piece is.","index":413,"end_time":1146.33,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1141.37,"speaker_name":"Linnea Wolken"},{"text":"And Roz has done a fantastic job overcoming.","index":414,"end_time":1149.57,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1147.13,"speaker_name":"Linnea Wolken"},{"text":"The second part is.","index":415,"end_time":1150.61,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1149.57,"speaker_name":"Linnea Wolken"},{"text":"So we have learn upon and now we have a second portal that she just, you know, launched and brought to life.","index":416,"end_time":1157.77,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1150.61,"speaker_name":"Linnea Wolken"},{"text":"I''ll say that we can put customer classes in because before it was ugly like we had big letters Internal use only versus customer.","index":417,"end_time":1165.93,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1157.77,"speaker_name":"Linnea Wolken"},{"text":"But now they''re two separate portals.","index":418,"end_time":1167.65,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1165.93,"speaker_name":"Linnea Wolken"},{"text":"But I was just thinking about it and what we can leverage with you folks to help us, you know, bring this to speed faster.","index":419,"end_time":1174.93,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1167.73,"speaker_name":"Linnea Wolken"},{"text":"We have Internal resources to help with the videos.","index":420,"end_time":1178.01,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1175.25,"speaker_name":"Linnea Wolken"},{"text":"Roz does a lot of the editing but everything I feel that is on raw as always to do all of these things and then you know, we go through all these internal checks, things like that.","index":421,"end_time":1188.29,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1178.01,"speaker_name":"Linnea Wolken"},{"text":"But what can we do from a strategy standpoint to have this holistic kind of, you know, knowledge center.","index":422,"end_time":1197.93,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1188.37,"speaker_name":"Linnea Wolken"},{"text":"I''m going to call it for lack.","index":423,"end_time":1199.25,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1197.93,"speaker_name":"Linnea Wolken"},{"text":"I don''t want to use knowledge center because we use that somewhere else.","index":424,"end_time":1201.89,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1199.25,"speaker_name":"Linnea Wolken"},{"text":"But just a learning center for our customers as well.","index":425,"end_time":1206.21,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1201.89,"speaker_name":"Linnea Wolken"},{"text":"Internal is not as important because the regions take our classes and they put it in their learning and development centers but you can''t find them.","index":426,"end_time":1214.73,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1207.17,"speaker_name":"Linnea Wolken"},{"text":"But that''s another challenge for another day.","index":427,"end_time":1216.77,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1214.73,"speaker_name":"Linnea Wolken"},{"text":"We''re not bitter at all about that.","index":428,"end_time":1220.77,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1218.85,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Not at all.","index":429,"end_time":1221.33,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1220.77,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"All these great work and it''s like, okay, so I''m trying to get it assigned in regions so then they''re forced to take it.","index":430,"end_time":1229.33,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1221.33,"speaker_name":"Linnea Wolken"},{"text":"But anyway, the customer one we control more of and can send the invitations to anybody that''s like an admin user.","index":431,"end_time":1236.92,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1229.33,"speaker_name":"Linnea Wolken"},{"text":"So it''s definitely a closer relationship.","index":432,"end_time":1239.36,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1236.92,"speaker_name":"Linnea Wolken"},{"text":"But I don''t know.","index":433,"end_time":1240.24,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1239.36,"speaker_name":"Linnea Wolken"},{"text":"Laraz, do you want to add anything else?","index":434,"end_time":1241.68,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1240.24,"speaker_name":"Linnea Wolken"},{"text":"We''ll have more information but that''s just my high level.","index":435,"end_time":1244.36,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1241.68,"speaker_name":"Linnea Wolken"},{"text":"I was thinking about, you know, the strategy behind it and how do we tie it to all this go to market work we do without recreating wheel.","index":436,"end_time":1253.24,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1244.36,"speaker_name":"Linnea Wolken"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":437,"end_time":1254.28,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1253.72,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"So I''m with you on recreating the wheel.","index":438,"end_time":1258.6,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1254.68,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"We have an area on learn upon.","index":439,"end_time":1264.37,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1260.77,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"For resources and I know Linea, you and I talked about that and I test drove it with the RPD video library and it worked just great.","index":440,"end_time":1272.21,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1264.37,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Shows up as a list, you can click it, download it and you''re off to the races.","index":441,"end_time":1275.97,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1272.53,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"So there is a possibility of using.","index":442,"end_time":1279.49,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1277.49,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Of putting things there.","index":443,"end_time":1280.89,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1279.73,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"But I feel like if you''re a customer taking a class already, you''ve already bought the thing you don''t need.","index":444,"end_time":1287.57,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1280.89,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"I don''t think we need to.","index":445,"end_time":1289.15,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1288.11,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Yeah, we''re not selling.","index":446,"end_time":1290.43,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1289.39,"speaker_name":"Linnea Wolken"},{"text":"But we''re.","index":447,"end_time":1290.91,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1290.43,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Yeah, we''re not selling anything.","index":448,"end_time":1292.39,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1290.99,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"And maybe showing them things they didn''t even know and maybe it is an upsell opportunity.","index":449,"end_time":1296.59,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1292.39,"speaker_name":"Linnea Wolken"},{"text":"Yes.","index":450,"end_time":1298.07,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1297.55,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Seen Natalie, Nina, everybody.","index":451,"end_time":1300.15,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1298.07,"speaker_name":"Linnea Wolken"},{"text":"Lou.","index":452,"end_time":1300.51,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1300.15,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"The learn upon instance that we have.","index":453,"end_time":1302.59,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1300.51,"speaker_name":"Linnea Wolken"},{"text":"I don''t think so.","index":454,"end_time":1304.43,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1303.55,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"No.","index":455,"end_time":1304.71,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1304.43,"speaker_name":"Linnea Wolken"},{"text":"I was gonna say, if we have, it would have been ages ago.","index":456,"end_time":1306.87,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1304.71,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"And I think that might be the first step.","index":457,"end_time":1308.51,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1306.87,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"That''s where my mind went as well.","index":458,"end_time":1309.83,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1308.51,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"To maybe show you guys what that looks like and see what you think.","index":459,"end_time":1312.67,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1309.83,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"I mean, I''d be over the moon.","index":460,"end_time":1314.87,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1313.47,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"For some help with the editing, but the editing can get quite technical and if you don''t know the like, if you don''t, if you don''t have a more intimate knowledge of the software, it can, you know, I don''t know how that would work because this overview is one thing.","index":461,"end_time":1332.16,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1314.87,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"You know, it''s much more high level.","index":462,"end_time":1334.32,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1332.16,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Whereas the stuff that I''m getting into, I mean, linea, all the RPD videos, as an example, that was like 25 odd videos.","index":463,"end_time":1340.8,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1334.32,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"And it was a, you know, it was Kevin and I and all the gentleman who did the videoing for us going back and forth to make sure we had it right.","index":464,"end_time":1348,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1340.96,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"So maybe it gets to a certain point and then you can pass it to them to polish it.","index":465,"end_time":1352.34,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1348.38,"speaker_name":"Linnea Wolken"},{"text":"I don''t.","index":466,"end_time":1352.74,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1352.34,"speaker_name":"Linnea Wolken"},{"text":"Again, just.","index":467,"end_time":1353.38,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1352.74,"speaker_name":"Linnea Wolken"},{"text":"Yeah, do some help.","index":468,"end_time":1354.78,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1353.38,"speaker_name":"Linnea Wolken"},{"text":"Yeah, no, that''s a, it''s a, it''s a good thought.","index":469,"end_time":1357.78,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1355.18,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Like, even if it''s just as simple.","index":470,"end_time":1359.42,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1357.78,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"As saying, hey, can you guys add in the intro, you know, in the exit and just polish up the transitions for me and then send it back?","index":471,"end_time":1366.06,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1359.42,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"That would be helpful.","index":472,"end_time":1366.94,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1366.06,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"That would take a step or two off of my, you know, off of my, my plate.","index":473,"end_time":1372.86,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1366.94,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"So you show them the portal.","index":474,"end_time":1374.98,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1373.02,"speaker_name":"Linnea Wolken"},{"text":"Quick, Ross, I think we have time to just call for another half hour.","index":475,"end_time":1378.38,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1374.98,"speaker_name":"Linnea Wolken"},{"text":"I think so.","index":476,"end_time":1379.42,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1378.9,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Yes, yes.","index":477,"end_time":1380.9,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1379.42,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Just a sec, let me get to it.","index":478,"end_time":1382.98,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1381.3,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"The portal.","index":479,"end_time":1384.18,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1383.22,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"I have too many tabs open.","index":480,"end_time":1387.3,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1385.3,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Sort of like my brain.","index":481,"end_time":1388.7,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1387.46,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"That never happens.","index":482,"end_time":1389.7,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1388.7,"speaker_name":"Linnea Wolken"},{"text":"Oh, funny.","index":483,"end_time":1392.82,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1391.86,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Okay, hold on, let me just share here really quick.","index":484,"end_time":1395.86,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1393.22,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Okay, so I will just switch.","index":485,"end_time":1404.26,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1400.42,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Can you guys see that?","index":486,"end_time":1405.46,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1404.34,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Oh, hold on.","index":487,"end_time":1406.79,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1405.83,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Share.","index":488,"end_time":1407.35,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1406.95,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Sorry.","index":489,"end_time":1408.27,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1407.91,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"There''s that almost that extra step with, with the zoom that I''m not used to.","index":490,"end_time":1412.19,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1408.27,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"So my apologies.","index":491,"end_time":1413.27,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1412.19,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Here it goes.","index":492,"end_time":1414.39,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1413.59,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Okay, so our portal looks very similar to the other one, but isn''t.","index":493,"end_time":1424.11,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1416.95,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"So this is our customer facing portal.","index":494,"end_time":1426.75,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1424.11,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Once it comes up.","index":495,"end_time":1427.99,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1426.75,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"And we already had some banners ready to go for this.","index":496,"end_time":1433.03,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1428.07,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"So this is why you''re seeing.","index":497,"end_time":1434.47,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1433.27,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"This may look a little new to you guys, but this is what we''ve had for a little bit.","index":498,"end_time":1439.35,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1434.47,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"You come in here and I''ve already been messing around in the background.","index":499,"end_time":1444.03,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1440.39,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"So I''ve in essence taken all the classes.","index":500,"end_time":1446.63,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1444.03,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"But you can, if you''re a new person, you can go in, you can see, excuse me, what you''ve already taken.","index":501,"end_time":1452.949,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1446.63,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"So this is one of the classes.","index":502,"end_time":1454.35,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1452.949,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"That we had already.","index":503,"end_time":1456.31,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1454.35,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Again, these little images were already done ahead of time before we started working with you folks.","index":504,"end_time":1463.19,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1457.43,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"But you know, we could maybe do something around those if we need to.","index":505,"end_time":1466.72,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1463.52,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"You go to the catalog to see all the rest of the classes.","index":506,"end_time":1470.28,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1467.76,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"And then there''s this resources and Linea.","index":507,"end_time":1472.92,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1470.28,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"There''s the.","index":508,"end_time":1473.52,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1472.92,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"The video library like I was talking about, which is.","index":509,"end_time":1476.64,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1473.6,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":510,"end_time":1477.08,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1476.72,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Which is nice.","index":511,"end_time":1477.68,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1477.08,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"I like this little resources tab.","index":512,"end_time":1479.08,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1477.68,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"It''s very helpful.","index":513,"end_time":1480.16,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1479.08,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"So thanks for having me.","index":514,"end_time":1481.6,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1480.16,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Yeah, no, you''re welcome.","index":515,"end_time":1483.04,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1481.84,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Like I said, I had to do it for the port, I have to do it for the portal anyway, so it''s perfect.","index":516,"end_time":1488.88,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1484,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"So if you go to the course, if you''re an actual learner, you wouldn''t see this.","index":517,"end_time":1495.63,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1489.83,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"You''re just seeing this because I''m an admin.","index":518,"end_time":1497.03,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1495.63,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"And then if I were to relaunch, the classes look a little bit like this.","index":519,"end_time":1504.95,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1497.83,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"As you can see, I''ve been messing around.","index":520,"end_time":1507.79,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1506.07,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"But it starts here.","index":521,"end_time":1509.03,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1507.79,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Have you guys worked in Learn upon before?","index":522,"end_time":1511.67,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1509.99,"speaker_name":"Linnea Wolken"},{"text":"That was not me directly.","index":523,"end_time":1515.83,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1512.95,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Yeah, that was my.","index":524,"end_time":1518.88,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1518,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"That''s what I''ve got going on up here.","index":525,"end_time":1520.28,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1518.96,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"That''s what all these little orange tabs are.","index":526,"end_time":1521.96,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1520.28,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"These are all classes that are kind of in.","index":527,"end_time":1524,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1521.96,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"In either in the works or something that I''m doing with them with Learn Upon.","index":528,"end_time":1527.6,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1524.16,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"So I drop in all of the information into Learn upon.","index":529,"end_time":1531.6,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1528.4,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"And then it gets, you know, we have like a syllabus like you''re seeing here of like how to do all these wonderful things.","index":530,"end_time":1536.8,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1531.6,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"And then a person starts the course with the intro and you know, and then we''ve got all these videos that fall under each of these categories explaining how to do the thing you click on.","index":531,"end_time":1547.6,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1537.6,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Yeah, yeah, the connection.","index":532,"end_time":1551.1,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1548.22,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"So pretending that you''re installing rpd, it just goes through a little bit of what, you know, what is required.","index":533,"end_time":1559.74,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1551.66,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"And then we have these little drop downs where we can go in and see like where to go to get more information and that kind of thing.","index":534,"end_time":1567.26,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1560.46,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"And then the next is like, hey, this is what you''ll get.","index":535,"end_time":1570.3,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1567.74,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"You know, you''ll get this email, it''ll look like this.","index":536,"end_time":1572.42,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1570.3,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"And then here''s the video walking you through how to do a license install for RPD as an example.","index":537,"end_time":1578.22,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1572.42,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"So it just kind of goes through in that sort of fashion.","index":538,"end_time":1582.41,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1579.45,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Can you show them the video though?","index":539,"end_time":1585.45,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1584.09,"speaker_name":"Linnea Wolken"},{"text":"Because these are the things that we''re talking about.","index":540,"end_time":1587.21,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1585.45,"speaker_name":"Linnea Wolken"},{"text":"We work with the technical team and the product manager to get.","index":541,"end_time":1590.93,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1587.45,"speaker_name":"Linnea Wolken"},{"text":"And then Roz makes magic happen.","index":542,"end_time":1592.65,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1590.93,"speaker_name":"Linnea Wolken"},{"text":"Yeah, so you can do the full thing if you''re really dying to.","index":543,"end_time":1595.73,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1593.05,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"There is voiceover.","index":544,"end_time":1596.61,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1595.73,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"You just can''t hear it.","index":545,"end_time":1597.49,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1596.61,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"I''m sorry, I just killed that.","index":546,"end_time":1598.85,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1597.49,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"So I''m not listening to 15 different things.","index":547,"end_time":1600.61,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1598.85,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"But this is basically there''s a voiceover happening.","index":548,"end_time":1604.01,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1600.61,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"You know, go here to click on this thing.","index":549,"end_time":1606.49,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1604.17,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"It''s very rude.","index":550,"end_time":1609.17,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1608.17,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Like this is starting off obviously as if you''re a brand new and needed the, you know, needed to know how to do this and how to walk through it.","index":551,"end_time":1617.13,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1609.17,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"So yeah, and it goes all the way through.","index":552,"end_time":1620.81,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1617.37,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"So she gets like basically screenshots from the technical folks, they write down stuff and then she massages it into that script.","index":553,"end_time":1629.21,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1620.97,"speaker_name":"Linnea Wolken"},{"text":"Yeah, and then the exit.","index":554,"end_time":1632.89,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1630.89,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"So yeah, they tend to do like a.","index":555,"end_time":1635.21,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1633.05,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"They tend to sort of talk through what they''re doing and then I write a script off of what they''re talking about and distill it down.","index":556,"end_time":1641.99,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1635.83,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"So I might get an, you know, I might.","index":557,"end_time":1643.95,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1641.99,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"One of these might be, I don''t know, 15 minutes.","index":558,"end_time":1646.07,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1643.95,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"That''s pretty, pretty long.","index":559,"end_time":1647.11,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1646.07,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Might be 10 minutes, let''s say of how to do it.","index":560,"end_time":1649.23,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1647.11,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"And I''ll distill it down into a minute and a half in this case or a minute and 40 in this case.","index":561,"end_time":1654.95,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1649.23,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"So yeah, I mean it''s pretty straightforward.","index":562,"end_time":1658.71,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1656.63,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"It''s just gathering all the bits and pieces and putting them in the right place.","index":563,"end_time":1661.79,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1658.71,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"That takes a bit of time.","index":564,"end_time":1663.03,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1661.79,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"So yeah, I don''t know if you guys have any access to Learn upon, but that could potentially actually be a place to help as well.","index":565,"end_time":1669.73,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1663.19,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"I don''t know how we give them access though Linea or if RNA would be willing to do that.","index":566,"end_time":1677.33,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1671.25,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"I would think so.","index":567,"end_time":1679.45,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1678.45,"speaker_name":"Linnea Wolken"},{"text":"They probably.","index":568,"end_time":1680.21,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1679.45,"speaker_name":"Linnea Wolken"},{"text":"I would think so.","index":569,"end_time":1681.65,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1680.69,"speaker_name":"Linnea Wolken"},{"text":"I''m going to be confident in that statement just because they obviously work with agencies as well.","index":570,"end_time":1686.29,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1681.81,"speaker_name":"Linnea Wolken"},{"text":"It''s just if we say, hey, we, you know, need to do a generic email to.","index":571,"end_time":1692.45,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1687.49,"speaker_name":"Linnea Wolken"},{"text":"We can just say New north at Learn upon or something like that.","index":572,"end_time":1695.85,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1692.69,"speaker_name":"Linnea Wolken"},{"text":"Yeah, for our instance, to get them accessed that way.","index":573,"end_time":1699.11,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1695.85,"speaker_name":"Linnea Wolken"},{"text":"Yeah, I got.","index":574,"end_time":1700.19,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1699.35,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"So for instance, this is Learn Upon.","index":575,"end_time":1701.75,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1700.19,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"This is the back end of Learn upon and you can see it looks a little bit different because it''s like adding a page and you know, you can really get into it.","index":576,"end_time":1708.23,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1701.75,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"So if I open up one of these as an example, you''ll see all the, the blocks.","index":577,"end_time":1712.95,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1708.23,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"So I have a described audio here.","index":578,"end_time":1715.71,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1713.91,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"There''s like a text block here.","index":579,"end_time":1717.59,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1715.71,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"We can add links, we can do all kinds of things.","index":580,"end_time":1720.23,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1717.59,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"It''s really quite a great authoring tool.","index":581,"end_time":1723.81,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1720.31,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"But yeah, again, Natalie and Lou, I don''t know if you guys are.","index":582,"end_time":1728.73,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1724.85,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Have used this before or have someone you know on the team that has used this before, but it''s Pretty straightforward stuff.","index":583,"end_time":1734.05,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1728.73,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"So.","index":584,"end_time":1734.85,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1734.45,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Yeah, that''s very cool.","index":585,"end_time":1737.17,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1735.09,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Yeah, I think from seeing that video, that''s definitely an area we can help in.","index":586,"end_time":1743.89,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1738.13,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Just like the solution overview or it''s almost like what we''ve been doing with everything else is just creating a template for it and then yeah, playing like if we just create one a new intro that they all follow, that looks like the solution overview.","index":587,"end_time":1759.06,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1744.13,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Well, those are the new ones that.","index":588,"end_time":1760.9,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1759.7,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"You guys have done for me already.","index":589,"end_time":1762.26,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1760.9,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"That was what the.","index":590,"end_time":1763.42,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1762.66,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"That''s what I was using all those intros for that you did already, right?","index":591,"end_time":1768.18,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1763.42,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Yeah, yeah, like all those animations like on Optimizer and all the rest of it.","index":592,"end_time":1773.38,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1768.34,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Yeah, those are the.","index":593,"end_time":1774.26,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1773.38,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Yeah, those are.","index":594,"end_time":1775.18,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1774.26,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"That''s why I had asked you guys to do those.","index":595,"end_time":1777.06,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1775.18,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Oh gosh, it was months ago now was for these.","index":596,"end_time":1779.61,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1777.53,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"So.","index":597,"end_time":1780.81,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1780.41,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"So yeah, I''m.","index":598,"end_time":1782.49,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1781.45,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"We''re ahead of ourselves.","index":599,"end_time":1783.41,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1782.49,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Yes.","index":600,"end_time":1783.85,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1783.41,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":601,"end_time":1785.93,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1785.45,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"But yeah, let me.","index":602,"end_time":1788.41,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1787.45,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Let me.","index":603,"end_time":1788.89,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1788.41,"speaker_name":"Linnea Wolken"},{"text":"Let me think about it.","index":604,"end_time":1790.73,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1789.05,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"I''ll think about it a little bit.","index":605,"end_time":1792.09,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1790.73,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"I think it will be in the editing though.","index":606,"end_time":1794.33,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1792.09,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"That would be a good place.","index":607,"end_time":1795.61,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1794.33,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Like I said, I don''t know if.","index":608,"end_time":1798.25,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1797.05,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"You guys want access to Easy Generator.","index":609,"end_time":1801.77,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1798.25,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"It is an authoring tool.","index":610,"end_time":1804.01,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1802.57,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"But again, honestly, Lenny, I think that it probably makes sense for me to do this kind of build out with the content that I have and I drop it in.","index":611,"end_time":1812.31,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1804.81,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"So I''m either writing it on a Word document for someone else to do or I''m just dropping it in directly into here.","index":612,"end_time":1818.07,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1812.31,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"I just know you also have to do the recording and that''s something if you have a script somebody else could do.","index":613,"end_time":1824.15,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1819.59,"speaker_name":"Linnea Wolken"},{"text":"I''m just trying to alleviate because my fear is there''s more work coming in this area as you know.","index":614,"end_time":1830.07,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1824.15,"speaker_name":"Linnea Wolken"},{"text":"And yeah, I''m just trying to plan a little bit.","index":615,"end_time":1834.15,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1830.47,"speaker_name":"Linnea Wolken"},{"text":"That''s you.","index":616,"end_time":1835.75,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1835.03,"speaker_name":"Linnea Wolken"},{"text":"Yeah, no, you know what, you bring up a good point.","index":617,"end_time":1838.71,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1836.39,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Like, even if I could get someone.","index":618,"end_time":1840.55,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1838.87,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"If I could drop a script to someone and have someone do the voiceover just as an audio file, that would be super helpful because that takes time as well.","index":619,"end_time":1848.87,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1840.55,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"I''ve been sort of semi helping myself out recently with Firefly.","index":620,"end_time":1854.39,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1850.23,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"They do this speech to.","index":621,"end_time":1856.23,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1854.39,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"They just text to speech generation.","index":622,"end_time":1859.91,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1857.83,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"It''s still in beta.","index":623,"end_time":1861.23,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1859.99,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"It''s really not bad.","index":624,"end_time":1862.39,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1861.23,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"I test drove it with a few people and they couldn''t tell that it was AI generated that I just dropped it in.","index":625,"end_time":1869.55,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1863.71,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"So.","index":626,"end_time":1870.19,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1869.87,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"But even still, it''s still time.","index":627,"end_time":1871.91,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1870.19,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"It''s still time to do it and all the rest of it.","index":628,"end_time":1874.19,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1871.91,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"So yeah, that''s another place that definitely could help would be if I have a script to do the voiceover.","index":629,"end_time":1879.63,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1874.27,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"And just editing, you know, polishing and editing.","index":630,"end_time":1883.87,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1881.23,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"I think that would be really helpful as well, especially in line if you''re seeing more coming down the pipe.","index":631,"end_time":1888.35,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1883.87,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"It is.","index":632,"end_time":1889.31,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1888.83,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"It.","index":633,"end_time":1889.67,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1889.31,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"It is time consuming for sure.","index":634,"end_time":1891.47,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1889.67,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Like editing and all of this takes time.","index":635,"end_time":1893.55,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1891.47,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"So.","index":636,"end_time":1894.19,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1893.79,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":637,"end_time":1895.63,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1895.15,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Think about work through.","index":638,"end_time":1898.19,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1896.91,"speaker_name":"Linnea Wolken"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":639,"end_time":1901.15,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1900.67,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Come up with ways that.","index":640,"end_time":1903.07,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1901.55,"speaker_name":"Linnea Wolken"},{"text":"Just to alleviate workload because I know there''s so many other things to do and wherever they can help you.","index":641,"end_time":1909.47,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1903.15,"speaker_name":"Linnea Wolken"},{"text":"And then the other thing, Ross, that I.","index":642,"end_time":1911.79,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1909.87,"speaker_name":"Linnea Wolken"},{"text":"Anything else on that before we jump off to something else?","index":643,"end_time":1914.64,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1911.79,"speaker_name":"Linnea Wolken"},{"text":"I''m good.","index":644,"end_time":1916.95,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1916.47,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"We''ll work through it.","index":645,"end_time":1918.35,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1917.51,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Nadalie, you and I can work through it.","index":646,"end_time":1919.83,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1918.35,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":647,"end_time":1920.63,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1920.23,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"And I think that that sounds very doable.","index":648,"end_time":1922.31,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1920.63,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"We do a lot of, like, podcasts for clients too, where we deal with hiring people to do voiceovers.","index":649,"end_time":1928.31,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1922.31,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"So even if it''s just like you sending us the screen recording plus the script, we can then get someone to read it and stitch everything together for you.","index":650,"end_time":1935.99,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1928.87,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"That would be helpful.","index":651,"end_time":1937.91,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1937.03,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"That would take a step out for sure.","index":652,"end_time":1939.51,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1937.91,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":653,"end_time":1939.99,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1939.51,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"That''s great.","index":654,"end_time":1941.6,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1941.04,"speaker_name":"Linnea Wolken"},{"text":"Cool.","index":655,"end_time":1942.56,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1942.08,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Rosa, I didn''t know if you wanted help on this or not, but I''m just throwing it out there because I wasted dumb time last night trying to come up with the.","index":656,"end_time":1950.96,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1943.52,"speaker_name":"Linnea Wolken"},{"text":"That image that we were going to work on for the admin workshops.","index":657,"end_time":1956.16,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1951.28,"speaker_name":"Linnea Wolken"},{"text":"Oh, yeah, it''s up to you.","index":658,"end_time":1959.36,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1956.4,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Yeah, no, I''m three quarters done with that.","index":659,"end_time":1963.2,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1961.12,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"I just need to drop in one more image and I''ll be able to show it to you.","index":660,"end_time":1966.76,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1963.2,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"It''s very.","index":661,"end_time":1967.36,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1966.76,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"It''s very quick, quite easy for me.","index":662,"end_time":1970.58,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1967.36,"speaker_name":"Linnea Wolken"},{"text":"Everything''s time consuming like that, so I have a magic wand.","index":663,"end_time":1973.82,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1970.58,"speaker_name":"Linnea Wolken"},{"text":"So.","index":664,"end_time":1974.18,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1973.82,"speaker_name":"Linnea Wolken"},{"text":"And for the rest of the team, it was.","index":665,"end_time":1978.1,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1976.34,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"It''s a.","index":666,"end_time":1978.66,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1978.1,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"It''s just.","index":667,"end_time":1979.3,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1978.66,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Well, not just.","index":668,"end_time":1980.26,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1979.54,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"It''s an email banner.","index":669,"end_time":1981.18,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1980.26,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"We''ll probably use it in a few other places for an upcoming administrator workshop.","index":670,"end_time":1986.66,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1981.18,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Yeah, let me keep that in the back of my mind too, Linea, because there.","index":671,"end_time":1991.94,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1988.58,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"If we want to maybe change the file that we use for the front of the notebooks, we might want to do something around that.","index":672,"end_time":2001.1,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1992.1,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"And in that case, I would definitely send it to this team to do.","index":673,"end_time":2004.62,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2001.1,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Yeah, yeah, that''s what I was thinking.","index":674,"end_time":2006.02,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2004.7,"speaker_name":"Linnea Wolken"},{"text":"I was like, where else could this be over?","index":675,"end_time":2007.7,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2006.02,"speaker_name":"Linnea Wolken"},{"text":"But again, leaving it.","index":676,"end_time":2009.02,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2007.7,"speaker_name":"Linnea Wolken"},{"text":"Yeah, yeah.","index":677,"end_time":2010.46,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2009.74,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Let me, let me.","index":678,"end_time":2011.38,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2010.46,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Let me just get it into a place where you''re happy with it and we''ll go from there happily.","index":679,"end_time":2016.58,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2011.38,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"One of the things we had to do for the animations was we needed to have a vector file of all of the HERO images, which in some instances was much easier than others.","index":680,"end_time":2028.7,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2016.58,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Yeah, the one for IPM drove us all Crazy.","index":681,"end_time":2032.37,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2030.13,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"So.","index":682,"end_time":2032.85,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2032.45,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"So we do have those vector files now, which is the good news.","index":683,"end_time":2036.37,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2033.57,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"So if we do want to do something where it might be a little bit not as, you know, not as fine a detail, kind of like what happened with the first notebook, we might be able to do something with that.","index":684,"end_time":2047.01,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2036.37,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"That banner image.","index":685,"end_time":2048.17,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2047.09,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"So, yeah, leave it.","index":686,"end_time":2049.25,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2048.17,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Leave it with me.","index":687,"end_time":2049.93,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2049.25,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"And we''ll, you know, get into a place where we like it, and then we can see if there''s something that we can do for the notebook.","index":688,"end_time":2055.17,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2049.93,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Because it''d be nice to kind of carry that.","index":689,"end_time":2057.01,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2055.17,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"That.","index":690,"end_time":2057.34,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2057.18,"speaker_name":"Linnea Wolken"},{"text":"That image, that banner through on other things.","index":691,"end_time":2059.5,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2057.34,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Perfect.","index":692,"end_time":2060.78,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2060.06,"speaker_name":"Linnea Wolken"},{"text":"And then I was just thinking one other area I''ve been working, and I''ve literally been taking the Rico, US elements, graphic arts, etc, and it''s the ones with the mountains.","index":693,"end_time":2072.26,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2062.22,"speaker_name":"Linnea Wolken"},{"text":"Let me see if I can share so you guys can laugh at my artistry.","index":694,"end_time":2075.9,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2072.26,"speaker_name":"Linnea Wolken"},{"text":"So this up here, this image, can you guys see it yet, or is it.","index":695,"end_time":2085.18,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2081.34,"speaker_name":"Linnea Wolken"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":696,"end_time":2085.92,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2085.6,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Oh, you can.","index":697,"end_time":2086.88,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2086.24,"speaker_name":"Linnea Wolken"},{"text":"Okay, great.","index":698,"end_time":2087.52,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2086.88,"speaker_name":"Linnea Wolken"},{"text":"So this is something the US has, and they do these VIP customer events here in Boulder, and we''re going to be doing one for Latin America, another region of ours.","index":699,"end_time":2097.76,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2087.92,"speaker_name":"Linnea Wolken"},{"text":"And I was just lifting and shifting some of their, you know, creative here.","index":700,"end_time":2103.04,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2097.76,"speaker_name":"Linnea Wolken"},{"text":"But this is Linea and not knowing, you know, I''m not great at this stuff.","index":701,"end_time":2107.08,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2103.04,"speaker_name":"Linnea Wolken"},{"text":"As I was like, okay, I don''t, like, I want to keep it in our brand colors because I''m a dork.","index":702,"end_time":2112.08,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2107.08,"speaker_name":"Linnea Wolken"},{"text":"And I was, like, looking here, Roz, this is what I. Oh, dear.","index":703,"end_time":2115.97,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2112.32,"speaker_name":"Linnea Wolken"},{"text":"Yes.","index":704,"end_time":2116.53,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2116.05,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"I fix this because I''m like, oh, my God, it''s so ugly.","index":705,"end_time":2119.97,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2116.69,"speaker_name":"Linnea Wolken"},{"text":"And then.","index":706,"end_time":2120.97,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2120.45,"speaker_name":"Linnea Wolken"},{"text":"Yeah, all right.","index":707,"end_time":2121.93,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2120.97,"speaker_name":"Linnea Wolken"},{"text":"So then I went on the web and literally, I pulled this.","index":708,"end_time":2124.73,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2121.93,"speaker_name":"Linnea Wolken"},{"text":"But I don''t mind that.","index":709,"end_time":2125.89,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2124.73,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"I mean, I don''t mind that.","index":710,"end_time":2127.33,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2126.05,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"A little gray.","index":711,"end_time":2128.29,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2127.33,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"It''s, like, seems dingy.","index":712,"end_time":2129.73,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2128.29,"speaker_name":"Linnea Wolken"},{"text":"But anyway, so these are things that I do that I''m like, okay, I need help, because I''m not very good at it.","index":713,"end_time":2135.69,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2129.97,"speaker_name":"Linnea Wolken"},{"text":"And then.","index":714,"end_time":2136.01,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2135.69,"speaker_name":"Linnea Wolken"},{"text":"Wait, there''s one more.","index":715,"end_time":2136.93,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2136.01,"speaker_name":"Linnea Wolken"},{"text":"Let me grab this.","index":716,"end_time":2137.89,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2136.93,"speaker_name":"Linnea Wolken"},{"text":"I don''t know where the Wham.","index":717,"end_time":2140.69,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2138.37,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Colors, though.","index":718,"end_time":2141.73,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2140.77,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Why the white colors?","index":719,"end_time":2143.49,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2141.89,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"I''m like, oh, I don''t.","index":720,"end_time":2145.83,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2144.23,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Give me one sec because I''m trying to.","index":721,"end_time":2148.63,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2146.79,"speaker_name":"Linnea Wolken"},{"text":"Oh, here it is.","index":722,"end_time":2149.27,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2148.63,"speaker_name":"Linnea Wolken"},{"text":"Let me drop it in so you guys can see.","index":723,"end_time":2151.03,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2149.27,"speaker_name":"Linnea Wolken"},{"text":"So today, the US Team was showing the agenda they did for their VIP event and.","index":724,"end_time":2157.43,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2151.03,"speaker_name":"Linnea Wolken"},{"text":"Oh.","index":725,"end_time":2157.99,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2157.51,"speaker_name":"Linnea Wolken"},{"text":"Oh, no, no.","index":726,"end_time":2160.23,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2158.87,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Oh, why?","index":727,"end_time":2161.11,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2160.39,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"So I''m hoping to, like, you know, Roger, you have enough on your plate.","index":728,"end_time":2166.55,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2161.99,"speaker_name":"Linnea Wolken"},{"text":"Is this something to get a quick turnaround on?","index":729,"end_time":2170.39,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2166.55,"speaker_name":"Linnea Wolken"},{"text":"And just.","index":730,"end_time":2170.99,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2170.39,"speaker_name":"Linnea Wolken"},{"text":"I don''t want it in, like, Roz says, wham.","index":731,"end_time":2173.53,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2170.99,"speaker_name":"Linnea Wolken"},{"text":"Colors that''s not like a thing.","index":732,"end_time":2175.41,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2173.53,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"It''s all I see when every time I see it all, I hear George.","index":733,"end_time":2177.89,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2175.41,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Michael singing in the background.","index":734,"end_time":2179.29,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2177.89,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"That''s all I hear.","index":735,"end_time":2180.05,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2179.29,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Well, and it''s hard to see this.","index":736,"end_time":2182.05,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2180.53,"speaker_name":"Linnea Wolken"},{"text":"It''s hard to read.","index":737,"end_time":2183.09,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2182.13,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Yeah, yeah, exactly.","index":738,"end_time":2184.57,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2183.17,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"I''m like, I struggle with this in many ways, so.","index":739,"end_time":2188.05,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2184.57,"speaker_name":"Linnea Wolken"},{"text":"But I. I''m asking.","index":740,"end_time":2189.33,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2188.21,"speaker_name":"Linnea Wolken"},{"text":"I''m trying to get the actual design file from them, so.","index":741,"end_time":2192.05,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2189.33,"speaker_name":"Linnea Wolken"},{"text":"Okay.","index":742,"end_time":2192.53,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2192.05,"speaker_name":"Linnea Wolken"},{"text":"Easier.","index":743,"end_time":2193.41,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2192.85,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"But I didn''t know.","index":744,"end_time":2194.17,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2193.41,"speaker_name":"Linnea Wolken"},{"text":"Roz, if this something I give to you or you can put in to the team here to help quick on it.","index":745,"end_time":2200.29,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2194.17,"speaker_name":"Linnea Wolken"},{"text":"I would see.","index":746,"end_time":2201.63,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2201.15,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"I would say if we can give it to the team, even if you''ve got that original image where it''s not got the Wham.","index":747,"end_time":2207.03,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2201.63,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Colors on it, I think we could jump from there.","index":748,"end_time":2209.71,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2207.03,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Lou, jump in anytime on this one for me.","index":749,"end_time":2212.39,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2210.19,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"But I think, you know, we can have.","index":750,"end_time":2213.79,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2212.39,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"I think you could probably layer any color you need to over it, as long as you''ve got the original image.","index":751,"end_time":2218.35,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2213.79,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Well, this one I stole from, like, the Internet, but I''m going to get the file shortly from someone in the North America.","index":752,"end_time":2225.39,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2218.99,"speaker_name":"Linnea Wolken"},{"text":"So once I get it, Roz, can I send it to you to help?","index":753,"end_time":2229.23,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2225.71,"speaker_name":"Linnea Wolken"},{"text":"Yeah, yeah, absolutely.","index":754,"end_time":2231.55,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2230.47,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"If you send me all the, like.","index":755,"end_time":2233.03,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2231.55,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"All the, like, all the, like, the where you''re using it and how.","index":756,"end_time":2237.59,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2233.03,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Like, I. I mean, I see a banner across the top here.","index":757,"end_time":2239.91,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2237.59,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"I see it being used on a full page.","index":758,"end_time":2241.67,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2239.91,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Like, just.","index":759,"end_time":2242.11,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2241.67,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"If you can just give us an idea of what you''re using it for.","index":760,"end_time":2244.47,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2242.11,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"For sure.","index":761,"end_time":2245.59,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2244.87,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"For sure.","index":762,"end_time":2246.39,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2245.83,"speaker_name":"Linnea Wolken"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":763,"end_time":2246.79,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2246.39,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Okay.","index":764,"end_time":2247.39,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2246.87,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"I just wanted to ask because I''m like, oh, I can''t do this.","index":765,"end_time":2250.55,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2247.39,"speaker_name":"Linnea Wolken"},{"text":"Oh, it''s really.","index":766,"end_time":2251.91,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2250.95,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"It''s really difficult to read with that purple.","index":767,"end_time":2254.47,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2251.99,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"I know.","index":768,"end_time":2255.44,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2255.04,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Yeah, I find that really hard to read personally.","index":769,"end_time":2258.96,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2255.84,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"So.","index":770,"end_time":2259.52,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2259.12,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Yeah, no, I agree.","index":771,"end_time":2260.56,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2259.52,"speaker_name":"Linnea Wolken"},{"text":"And I was like, this kills me too.","index":772,"end_time":2262.32,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2260.64,"speaker_name":"Linnea Wolken"},{"text":"But I''m like, okay.","index":773,"end_time":2263.36,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2262.32,"speaker_name":"Linnea Wolken"},{"text":"Anyway, all right, so we''ll send that in to you guys later today.","index":774,"end_time":2267.64,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2264.24,"speaker_name":"Linnea Wolken"},{"text":"Or I can even do it, but you guys will laugh at me when I put it in.","index":775,"end_time":2272,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2267.64,"speaker_name":"Linnea Wolken"},{"text":"Anyway.","index":776,"end_time":2274.88,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2274.32,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Thank you.","index":777,"end_time":2275.68,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2275.2,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Yeah, no, yeah, that''s.","index":778,"end_time":2277,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2275.68,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"That should be relatively easy to change those colors.","index":779,"end_time":2280.52,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2277,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Yeah, yeah.","index":780,"end_time":2281.51,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2280.52,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Have the team do it.","index":781,"end_time":2282.51,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2281.51,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"And is that agenda, does that need to be adjusted completely as well?","index":782,"end_time":2286.35,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2282.67,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Like, would you need the document.","index":783,"end_time":2287.87,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2286.43,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Okay, so, yeah, I just need the background template.","index":784,"end_time":2291.07,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2287.87,"speaker_name":"Linnea Wolken"},{"text":"And then I don''t know if you guys have, like.","index":785,"end_time":2293.15,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2291.07,"speaker_name":"Linnea Wolken"},{"text":"Because I can just.","index":786,"end_time":2293.79,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2293.15,"speaker_name":"Linnea Wolken"},{"text":"It''s just a table.","index":787,"end_time":2294.67,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2293.79,"speaker_name":"Linnea Wolken"},{"text":"But I am not using theirs because it is hard to read, as you saw.","index":788,"end_time":2298.03,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2294.83,"speaker_name":"Linnea Wolken"},{"text":"Yeah, yeah.","index":789,"end_time":2299.31,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2298.43,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"If you can send us that original document as well, though, just so we have it, that would Be helpful too.","index":790,"end_time":2303.63,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2299.31,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Yeah, totally.","index":791,"end_time":2304.59,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2303.71,"speaker_name":"Linnea Wolken"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":792,"end_time":2304.99,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2304.59,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":793,"end_time":2305.39,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2304.99,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Because we may need to adjust the image so that it''s got, you know.","index":794,"end_time":2311.19,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2305.39,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Well, that''s another question.","index":795,"end_time":2312.79,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2311.27,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"See, that image to print as it sits right now is super color saturated.","index":796,"end_time":2317.71,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2313.11,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"So if someone wants to print that on a home computer or whatever, like.","index":797,"end_time":2321.51,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2317.71,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"That''S going to be wet when it comes off because there''s so much ink being shot on that page.","index":798,"end_time":2326.35,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2321.51,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Do you want something you see?","index":799,"end_time":2328.07,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2326.35,"speaker_name":"Linnea Wolken"},{"text":"Oh, okay.","index":800,"end_time":2329.47,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2328.55,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Oh, all right.","index":801,"end_time":2330.07,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2329.47,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Well, that''s helpful.","index":802,"end_time":2330.87,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2330.07,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Actually.","index":803,"end_time":2331.31,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2330.95,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"That''s.","index":804,"end_time":2331.71,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2331.31,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"That''s way more helpful so we don''t have to worry about saturation.","index":805,"end_time":2335.27,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2331.71,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Okay, all right, that''s helpful.","index":806,"end_time":2336.92,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2335.27,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"But, yeah, but yeah, looking at it.","index":807,"end_time":2339.68,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2337.88,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Send you a list of things and then I''m getting the assets from one of the team members right now, so.","index":808,"end_time":2344,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2339.68,"speaker_name":"Linnea Wolken"},{"text":"I''ll soon get it.","index":809,"end_time":2345.8,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2344,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Okay, yeah, no, that should, that should be fine.","index":810,"end_time":2348.64,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2345.96,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"If you could send us everything, the original image and then whatever documents you need made from it, that would be helpful.","index":811,"end_time":2355,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2348.64,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Okay, cool.","index":812,"end_time":2356.28,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2355.32,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"All right, perfect.","index":813,"end_time":2358.28,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2356.6,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Anything else from the team or are we good?","index":814,"end_time":2361.64,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2359.56,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"That was all my bits and pieces.","index":815,"end_time":2363.08,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2361.64,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Yeah, I think that''s everything.","index":816,"end_time":2365.13,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2364.01,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"So we have two things to send over to you.","index":817,"end_time":2368.41,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2366.41,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"The video and the images.","index":818,"end_time":2370.41,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2368.41,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"And then we''ll send over the brochure again into the new transfer folder.","index":819,"end_time":2375.53,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2371.45,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Yeah, yeah, that would be perfect.","index":820,"end_time":2377.29,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2375.77,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Well, you guys can grab the one that I''ve.","index":821,"end_time":2379.05,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2377.29,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"I''ve been mucking around with as well.","index":822,"end_time":2380.69,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2379.05,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"There was just some minor, minor adjustments.","index":823,"end_time":2383.21,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2380.69,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Like I just moved like the.","index":824,"end_time":2384.89,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2383.53,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"The top image on the top page over a tiny bit, so it just has a little, tiny bit more breathing space.","index":825,"end_time":2390.01,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2384.89,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"You know, just like little things like that.","index":826,"end_time":2391.85,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2390.01,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"So use that, that image or, sorry, use that file, if you wouldn''t mind.","index":827,"end_time":2395.7,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2391.85,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"It''s the January 2025 file.","index":828,"end_time":2398.18,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2395.7,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"And then, Lou, I will add you so you can grab it.","index":829,"end_time":2401.62,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2398.98,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Yeah, cool.","index":830,"end_time":2404.5,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2402.18,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Okay, Fingers.","index":831,"end_time":2405.38,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2404.5,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"And then I owe you some breeze.","index":832,"end_time":2406.66,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2405.38,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Yeah, yeah, yeah.","index":833,"end_time":2409.22,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2407.38,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"It''s so weird.","index":834,"end_time":2410.42,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2409.54,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"It''s just very weird.","index":835,"end_time":2411.7,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2410.42,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":836,"end_time":2412.26,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2411.78,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"So anyway, our next step will be maybe trying through Creative Cloud.","index":837,"end_time":2417.38,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2413.06,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"I know Colin said that you could share files that way.","index":838,"end_time":2419.94,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2417.46,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Yep.","index":839,"end_time":2420.97,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2420.57,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"You can.","index":840,"end_time":2422.01,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2421.45,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Yeah, absolutely you can.","index":841,"end_time":2423.69,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2422.17,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"I don''t use it as much because we.","index":842,"end_time":2427.93,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2424.89,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"We do everything.","index":843,"end_time":2428.65,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2427.93,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Our sharing, like internally is all on teams and through SharePoint.","index":844,"end_time":2432.61,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2428.65,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"So I don''t use it as much.","index":845,"end_time":2433.69,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2432.61,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"So maybe that''s a nice place to potentially use it for us because then I''d know everything going through there would be, you know, coming from you guys.","index":846,"end_time":2440.41,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2433.69,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"So, yeah, that''s definitely another way to, to do it.","index":847,"end_time":2444.09,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2440.57,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Let''s, let''s.","index":848,"end_time":2444.93,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2444.09,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"If this doesn''t work, let''s talk about that Because I wouldn''t, I wouldn''t say no to it.","index":849,"end_time":2448.61,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2444.93,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Going through Creative Cloud.","index":850,"end_time":2449.72,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2448.61,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Okay.","index":851,"end_time":2450.83,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2450.43,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":852,"end_time":2451.19,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2450.83,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"I have another crazy project that I hadn''t really thought of involving you guys in, but just going to throw it out there in case you have some ideas for where to put it.","index":853,"end_time":2460.19,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2451.19,"speaker_name":"Linnea Wolken"},{"text":"So we are starting to do what we''re calling discovery with customers and it literally is like for now, 30 minute call with a customer before they come in for a briefing or visit us in Boulder or it could be anywhere in the world.","index":854,"end_time":2473.11,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2460.35,"speaker_name":"Linnea Wolken"},{"text":"But right now this is specific to the US team and we collect information on kind of like a template.","index":855,"end_time":2478.93,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2473.11,"speaker_name":"Linnea Wolken"},{"text":"And then I''ve been asked like, hey, can you put this information in the portal?","index":856,"end_time":2483.61,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2479.25,"speaker_name":"Linnea Wolken"},{"text":"And I''m like no, because it''s stagnant and if we want to update like what''s happening with the customer and it should go on a CRM.","index":857,"end_time":2491.93,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2483.61,"speaker_name":"Linnea Wolken"},{"text":"But that''s another whole issue of Ricoh.","index":858,"end_time":2493.93,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2491.93,"speaker_name":"Linnea Wolken"},{"text":"To be honest.","index":859,"end_time":2494.61,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2493.93,"speaker_name":"Linnea Wolken"},{"text":"I miss HubSpot dearly and.","index":860,"end_time":2497.65,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2495.09,"speaker_name":"Linnea Wolken"},{"text":"But they.","index":861,"end_time":2498.45,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2497.81,"speaker_name":"Linnea Wolken"},{"text":"It won''t go into the CRM.","index":862,"end_time":2500.37,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2498.61,"speaker_name":"Linnea Wolken"},{"text":"Salespeople for software typically use Excel files and so I''m trying to think through what other tools are available that we could somehow create kind of a shared environment.","index":863,"end_time":2511.75,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2500.61,"speaker_name":"Linnea Wolken"},{"text":"It still, it has to be locked down because it''ll have customer information in it.","index":864,"end_time":2515.75,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2511.91,"speaker_name":"Linnea Wolken"},{"text":"But something like that, you know, a CRM but not a CRM smile.","index":865,"end_time":2521.59,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2515.99,"speaker_name":"Linnea Wolken"},{"text":"Any ideas, thoughts?","index":866,"end_time":2524.15,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2522.15,"speaker_name":"Linnea Wolken"},{"text":"Well, we have internally we have like I don''t.","index":867,"end_time":2531.33,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2526.71,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Creative Cloud wouldn''t work for this.","index":868,"end_time":2532.65,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2531.33,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"That''s Creative Cloud is something completely different.","index":869,"end_time":2534.81,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2532.65,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"It''s more for design elements and whatnot.","index":870,"end_time":2537.25,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2534.81,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"So I would kind of exclude that off the top we obviously have SharePoint which can get a little crazy.","index":871,"end_time":2543.29,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2537.25,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"I''m thinking maybe Confluence.","index":872,"end_time":2547.29,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2544.65,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"The only problem is only certain people can get into Confluence and the goal would be for sellers to be able to get in.","index":873,"end_time":2557.53,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2549.69,"speaker_name":"Linnea Wolken"},{"text":"Roger, the CEC team and they started this, it''s called insight360.360 tool which allows them to handle the briefings.","index":874,"end_time":2567.51,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2557.53,"speaker_name":"Linnea Wolken"},{"text":"It''s.","index":875,"end_time":2567.91,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2567.51,"speaker_name":"Linnea Wolken"},{"text":"It''s a customer engagement piece but it''s not direct to customer.","index":876,"end_time":2570.83,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2567.91,"speaker_name":"Linnea Wolken"},{"text":"I forgot what they technically call it Customer experience piece but it''s internal use only right now.","index":877,"end_time":2576.27,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2570.83,"speaker_name":"Linnea Wolken"},{"text":"So I didn''t know if there are any other kind of tools.","index":878,"end_time":2579.47,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2576.27,"speaker_name":"Linnea Wolken"},{"text":"I mean because yeah, SharePoint, at least now they''re more global in nature.","index":879,"end_time":2583.27,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2579.47,"speaker_name":"Linnea Wolken"},{"text":"I don''t know.","index":880,"end_time":2585.15,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2584.71,"speaker_name":"Linnea Wolken"},{"text":"I trying to think of what other.","index":881,"end_time":2586.95,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2585.15,"speaker_name":"Linnea Wolken"},{"text":"You guys have any ideas?","index":882,"end_time":2589.73,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2588.13,"speaker_name":"Linnea Wolken"},{"text":"Yeah, I haven''t used any tool like that.","index":883,"end_time":2593.53,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2591.81,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"I can do some help with some research for sure.","index":884,"end_time":2595.49,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2593.53,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"I haven''t used anything like that myself though.","index":885,"end_time":2598.21,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2595.97,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":886,"end_time":2599.49,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2599.01,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":887,"end_time":2600.21,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2599.89,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"With Linear with, with the like.","index":888,"end_time":2602.57,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2600.21,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"So would there only be a certain.","index":889,"end_time":2604.13,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2602.57,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Amount of people that would actually be able to manipulate and add or take away information on this form and you just need a whole bunch of people to be able to see it or is that even up for debate right now?","index":890,"end_time":2615.41,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2604.13,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Everything''s up for debate, as you know.","index":891,"end_time":2617.6,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2615.92,"speaker_name":"Linnea Wolken"},{"text":"And that''s why I keep pushing it back to Roger and team because I''m like this Insight360 tool should have that because they''re booking.","index":892,"end_time":2624.48,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2617.92,"speaker_name":"Linnea Wolken"},{"text":"It''s a good resource but I don''t know why if it''s.","index":893,"end_time":2629.24,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2625.36,"speaker_name":"Linnea Wolken"},{"text":"I don''t know what the issue is behind it.","index":894,"end_time":2630.76,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2629.24,"speaker_name":"Linnea Wolken"},{"text":"So I just figured if something rang a bell for anybody, I just haven''t really.","index":895,"end_time":2634.8,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2630.76,"speaker_name":"Linnea Wolken"},{"text":"What do we have now that I was thinking about our website and is there something that we create?","index":896,"end_time":2640.08,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2634.96,"speaker_name":"Linnea Wolken"},{"text":"You know we have the internal portal but that is not dynamic.","index":897,"end_time":2644.04,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2640.16,"speaker_name":"Linnea Wolken"},{"text":"Is there no else that we create that could have post that there?","index":898,"end_time":2648.24,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2644.04,"speaker_name":"Linnea Wolken"},{"text":"But again, I''m just like, it seems complex for what the need is.","index":899,"end_time":2652.16,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2648.24,"speaker_name":"Linnea Wolken"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":900,"end_time":2653.04,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2652.56,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"And I definitely would suggest not using Asana for this.","index":901,"end_time":2657.4,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2653.2,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"If, if North America says oh, let''s do that, I''m like, oh God, please don''t do it.","index":902,"end_time":2662.64,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2657.4,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Like you will be inundated.","index":903,"end_time":2664.16,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2662.64,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Send us.","index":904,"end_time":2664.88,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2664.32,"speaker_name":"Linnea Wolken"},{"text":"Is there anything there.","index":905,"end_time":2666.64,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2665.36,"speaker_name":"Linnea Wolken"},{"text":"That''S public facing.","index":906,"end_time":2670.32,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2669.12,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"But is there something behind it that isn''t?","index":907,"end_time":2673.36,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2671.04,"speaker_name":"Linnea Wolken"},{"text":"No, I don''t know, I''m just throwing ideas.","index":908,"end_time":2676.8,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2674.8,"speaker_name":"Linnea Wolken"},{"text":"Yeah, no, no, no, I get, yeah.","index":909,"end_time":2678.68,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2676.88,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"I get where you''re going with it.","index":910,"end_time":2680.24,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2678.68,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Zendesk.","index":911,"end_time":2681.44,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2680.72,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Yeah, yeah.","index":912,"end_time":2683.8,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2682.08,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Zendesk is so particular.","index":913,"end_time":2685.12,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2683.8,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Like we have poor Glenn.","index":914,"end_time":2688.36,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2685.52,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"He has more problems with that software than I think he knows what to do with Blossoms.","index":915,"end_time":2693.36,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2688.36,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"So yeah, it''s all, it''s all customer facing.","index":916,"end_time":2696.41,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2693.36,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Unfortunately there''s no kind of like lockdown area where you could, you know, send someone to and say, hey, grab this, you know, file or whatever.","index":917,"end_time":2704.41,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2696.41,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Yeah, okay.","index":918,"end_time":2707.05,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2705.05,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Natalie, Lou, Nina, any thoughts?","index":919,"end_time":2709.21,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2707.05,"speaker_name":"Linnea Wolken"},{"text":"You said that they''re.","index":920,"end_time":2711.61,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2710.65,"speaker_name":"Linnea Wolken"},{"text":"They''re using a spreadsheet right now, right?","index":921,"end_time":2713.61,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2711.69,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Excel.","index":922,"end_time":2714.65,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2714.01,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Excel, everybody.","index":923,"end_time":2716.37,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2714.97,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"And they have their own.","index":924,"end_time":2717.29,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2716.37,"speaker_name":"Linnea Wolken"},{"text":"Oh God.","index":925,"end_time":2718.89,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2718.09,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"So that''s the biggest Monday, maybe Monday.","index":926,"end_time":2725.62,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2721.38,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Monday''s like a sauna though.","index":927,"end_time":2728.02,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2726.26,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Oh yeah, I don''t know.","index":928,"end_time":2731.34,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2728.98,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"I haven''t looked so I can.","index":929,"end_time":2732.5,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2731.34,"speaker_name":"Linnea Wolken"},{"text":"Oh, so linear.","index":930,"end_time":2735.46,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2734.02,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"What about that, that Microsoft to do.","index":931,"end_time":2739.54,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2735.46,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Thing that I''ve been using with the pms?","index":932,"end_time":2741.62,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2739.54,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Well, the challenge is it''s not just task related so I''ve been looking into Microsoft for other options that they might have.","index":933,"end_time":2749.9,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2743.22,"speaker_name":"Linnea Wolken"},{"text":"But I did again was trying to figure out because you know, Microsoft too has its challenges.","index":934,"end_time":2754.65,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2749.9,"speaker_name":"Linnea Wolken"},{"text":"So.","index":935,"end_time":2755.05,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2754.65,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":936,"end_time":2755.53,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2755.13,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Anyway, yeah, just something to think about.","index":937,"end_time":2757.29,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2755.53,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"If you guys have any ideas, let us know and just again, not have to do is tomorrow, but soon.","index":938,"end_time":2763.37,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2757.45,"speaker_name":"Linnea Wolken"},{"text":"And I really don''t want to put it on the portal because, like, that''s another whole issue and stagnant.","index":939,"end_time":2769.17,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2763.37,"speaker_name":"Linnea Wolken"},{"text":"And then we got to replace them and update them and I''m like, no, thank you.","index":940,"end_time":2773.21,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2769.17,"speaker_name":"Linnea Wolken"},{"text":"Yeah, yeah, that''s.","index":941,"end_time":2775.25,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2773.29,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"That would be my problem with it as well.","index":942,"end_time":2776.94,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2775.25,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":943,"end_time":2777.89,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2777.57,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Anyway, and oh, one other thing.","index":944,"end_time":2780.45,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2778.45,"speaker_name":"Linnea Wolken"},{"text":"Just thank you guys and please thank Colin.","index":945,"end_time":2782.73,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2780.45,"speaker_name":"Linnea Wolken"},{"text":"I''ll shoot him an email too, but I got a coffee mug and a hat that''s really cute.","index":946,"end_time":2787.33,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2782.73,"speaker_name":"Linnea Wolken"},{"text":"I should use it if I could go outside, but I can''t.","index":947,"end_time":2789.81,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2787.33,"speaker_name":"Linnea Wolken"},{"text":"That has New north on it.","index":948,"end_time":2792.29,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2790.69,"speaker_name":"Linnea Wolken"},{"text":"Or not New North.","index":949,"end_time":2793.089,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2792.29,"speaker_name":"Linnea Wolken"},{"text":"Marketers in demand.","index":950,"end_time":2794.05,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2793.089,"speaker_name":"Linnea Wolken"},{"text":"So thank you, boys.","index":951,"end_time":2797.21,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2794.85,"speaker_name":"Linnea Wolken"},{"text":"You''re welcome.","index":952,"end_time":2797.89,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2797.21,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"You''re welcome.","index":953,"end_time":2799.01,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2798.29,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Where is.","index":954,"end_time":2802.61,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2802.05,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Okay, anything else?","index":955,"end_time":2804.48,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2803.36,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Sorry, Roz, I''m a talker.","index":956,"end_time":2806.24,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2804.8,"speaker_name":"Linnea Wolken"},{"text":"No, no, I think we''re good.","index":957,"end_time":2807.6,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2806.32,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"I. I''ve covered all my points.","index":958,"end_time":2810,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2807.68,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Anything else from the rest of the team?","index":959,"end_time":2813.2,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2811.52,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"I don''t think so.","index":960,"end_time":2814.96,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2814.16,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"That''s everything from me.","index":961,"end_time":2816,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2814.96,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Okay, awesome.","index":962,"end_time":2817.92,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2816.24,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Well, thanks, guys.","index":963,"end_time":2818.8,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2817.92,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Appreciate it.","index":964,"end_time":2819.68,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2818.96,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"And Happy New Year again.","index":965,"end_time":2821.04,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2819.68,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"And yeah, Natalie, you know where I am if you need anything.","index":966,"end_time":2824.32,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2821.2,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"So please just send a note if anything crops up.","index":967,"end_time":2826.44,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2824.32,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Otherwise, I will do my best to send the battle card over.","index":968,"end_time":2829.96,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2826.44,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"And of course, I will give that access to.","index":969,"end_time":2831.57,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2829.96,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"To Lou on the file.","index":970,"end_time":2832.68,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2831.72,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Great.","index":971,"end_time":2833.6,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":2833.24,"speaker_name":"Lou Bogani"},{"text":"Perfect.","index":972,"end_time":2834.04,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2833.6,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Excellent.","index":973,"end_time":2835,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2834.36,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"All right, thank you, everyone.","index":974,"end_time":2836.84,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2835.48,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Bye.","index":975,"end_time":2838.52,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2838.2,"speaker_name":"Linnea Wolken"},{"text":"Bye, Sam.","index":976,"end_time":2868.99,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2838.52,"speaker_name":"Roz"}],"dateString":"2026-01-08T17:30:00.000Z","host_email":"nathalie.mintjens@marketersindemand.com","meeting_link":"https://us02web.zoom.us/j/85828735088?pwd=b9W3cDKwBeJQyK00Qs0iP3vvCmTxIZ.1","participants":["nathalie.mintjens@marketersindemand.com,colin.costigan@marketersindemand.com,lou.bogani@marketersindemand.com,kiyan.klocker@marketersindemand.com,nina.belina@marketersindemand.com,rosalynne.regan@ricoh.ca,linnea.wolken@ricoh-usa.com","colin.costigan@marketersindemand.com","lou.bogani@marketersindemand.com","kiyan.klocker@marketersindemand.com","nina.belina@marketersindemand.com","rosalynne.regan@ricoh.ca","linnea.wolken@ricoh-usa.com"],"transcript_url":"https://app.fireflies.ai/view/01KE4R0W33605Y1KNBM1P1Q1Y5","organizer_email":"nathalie.mintjens@marketersindemand.com"}'::jsonb,
    '{"label":"positive","confidence":0.93,"bullets":["Resolved brochure color skew by switching file transfer to avoid Google-based rendering issues.","Removed English text from Optimizer video to ensure global usability and easier localization.","Roz confirmed refreshed look and feel spans brochures, sales guides, and battle cards.","Team aligned on LearnUpon support roles, with Natalie offering post-production assistance.","Planning initiated for customer-facing training expansion with potential agency editing support."],"highlights":[{"quote":"Just a few alterations and I think we''ll be good here with this.","speaker":"Roz"},{"quote":"I''m so excited. So this is great.","speaker":"Linnea Wolken"},{"quote":"I think we''re coming along nicely on this one, Natalie.","speaker":"Roz"}],"topics":["delivery","training","video","collaboration","design"],"model":"openai/gpt-4-vision","version":1,"generated_at":"2026-01-09T00:00:00Z"}'::jsonb,
    '{"fireflies_summary":{"notes":"## **Branding and Visual Assets Refinement**\n\nThe team is finalizing visual assets with minor adjustments to improve usability and brand consistency.\n\n- **Roz confirmed the logo issues are minor and fixable, with most visuals ready for flexible use across templates** (00:00)  \n    - Images featuring mail batches are intended for postal optimization contexts, not detailed traceability use, per Roz’s explanation.  \n    - Linnea emphasized the importance of realistic use cases, noting that commercial printers would avoid leaving mail haphazardly in offices.  \n    - Roz clarified that images will be edited and cropped to avoid clutter and maintain professionalism in final layouts.  \n    - The visuals are mostly lifestyle shots rather than raw, unedited images, supporting broader brand storytelling.\n\n- **Color consistency issues in the Process Director brochure were identified as a file transfer glitch, prompting a new file-sharing approach** (03:59)  \n    - Roz and Lou traced the red color skew to transferring via Google platforms and are moving to a dedicated transfer folder to avoid this.  \n    - Natalie will upload files directly to the folder once Lou is granted access, aiming to stabilize color integrity before final reviews.  \n    - Kevin has already expressed satisfaction with the brochure’s current look, supporting continued minor content polishing.  \n    - Roz plans to send the Process Director battle card next for template clean-up, with sales guide updates forthcoming.\n\n- **Linnea and Roz confirmed a unified new look and feel across all sales and marketing assets** (16:49)  \n    - Info Print Manager will debut the new visual style shortly, with content currently under review by Vishnu.  \n    - PowerPoints and battle cards have been combined or updated to reduce redundant materials and streamline sales messaging.  \n    - This consolidation aims to improve sales team usability and reduce cognitive load, a priority to Roz to \"not lose her mind.\"\n\n- **A request to refresh and improve customer event visuals for Latin America is underway, with design support offered by Roz’s team** (34:20)  \n    - Linnea shared concerns about brand color adherence and readability challenges in current graphics lifted from US assets.  \n    - Roz confirmed the team can rework colors and backgrounds for better clarity and printing efficiency once original files arrive.  \n    - The deliverable includes redesigned banner images and potentially agenda templates with adjusted saturation to avoid over-inking in print.  \n    - This work is planned as a quick turnaround to maintain brand standards and enhance regional event presentation.\n\n## **Video Content Strategy and Localization Challenges**\n\nVideo updates focus on streamlining messaging and improving global usability by removing embedded text.\n\n- **Roz decided to remove on-screen text and icons from the Optimizer solution overview video to simplify localization** (08:25)  \n    - The embedded English text conflicted with voiceover, complicating translation for global markets like Italy and Germany.  \n    - Roz prefers voiceover with subtitles as a more flexible approach to multilingual video content.  \n    - Linnea requested visuals still convey key steps without text for viewers watching without sound; Roz confirmed GUI animations will suffice.  \n    - This shift reflects a strategy to reduce localization costs and improve video adaptability.\n\n- **Video refreshes include updated intros, hardware shots, and refined transitions to modernize the solution suite’s presentation** (14:09)  \n    - Roz integrated VC80000 Ricoh hardware footage to enhance authenticity and product recognition.  \n    - The team plans similar updates for Info Print Manager and RPD once new GUIs are ready, awaiting Miriam’s design changes.  \n    - The new video style aligns with updated PowerPoint and brochure templates, creating a consistent brand story across media.  \n    - Roz praised the animation work done by the creative team and requested minor timing adjustments to key transitions for clarity.\n\n- **Natalie and Lou will continue refining the video content and testing file transfers using the new folder system** (16:36)  \n    - The goal is to finalize videos quickly and ensure color and content integrity across platforms.  \n    - Roz will grant Lou access to the transfer folder to streamline file sharing and reduce technical glitches disrupting workflows.  \n    - Creative Cloud was proposed as an alternative transfer method if issues persist, reflecting openness to new tools improving collaboration.  \n    - This process improvement is designed to speed up final approvals and reduce technical frustrations.\n\n## **Learning Management System (LMS) and Training Content Development**\n\nThe team is expanding internal and customer-facing training with a focus on scalability and resource efficiency.\n\n- **Linnea outlined a strategic shift to increase customer-facing training amid limited internal bandwidth** (18:09)  \n    - Internal sales classes have been built using existing beautiful assets, but now there is pressure to replicate for customers.  \n    - Two separate portals (internal and customer) now exist, improving usability and branding for each audience.  \n    - Linnea seeks collaboration to speed up content creation without reinventing the wheel, balancing quality and resource limits.  \n    - Roz acknowledged the time-intensive nature of video editing and content polishing, highlighting a need for additional help.\n\n- **Roz demonstrated the customer-facing Learn Upon portal, showcasing video libraries and course catalog features** (23:08)  \n    - The portal supports tracking completed courses and offers resources, which aligns with Linnea’s vision of a holistic learning center.  \n    - Course content includes scripted and edited videos distilled from longer technical recordings, ensuring clarity and accessibility.  \n    - Natalie confirmed the ability to create standardized templates and intros to streamline future video productions and maintain brand consistency.  \n    - Roz suggested partial delegation of editing tasks, such as adding intros and polishing transitions, to alleviate workload.\n\n- **The team discussed potential outsourcing of voiceover recording to speed production and improve quality** (30:19)  \n    - Roz shared experience with AI text-to-speech tools but acknowledged human voiceovers remain time-consuming yet valuable.  \n    - Natalie offered support via podcast production experience to hire voice talent and stitch scripts with recordings, reducing Roz’s burden.  \n    - Linnea emphasized the importance of planning for increased training content demand and exploring scalable workflows.  \n    - Roz and Natalie agreed to collaborate on workflow optimization, balancing content creation speed with quality.\n\n- **Additional design tasks for admin workshop assets are underway, with Roz’s team ready to assist** (32:22)  \n    - Linnea proposed quick banner image edits, which Roz confirmed are nearly complete and can extend to other collateral like notebooks.  \n    - Vector files for hero images now exist, enabling flexibility in resizing and repurposing across formats.  \n    - The team aims to maintain visual cohesion and brand alignment across all training and marketing materials.  \n    - This approach supports a more integrated go-to-market strategy using consistent assets.\n\n## **Customer Engagement Data Management Exploration**\n\nThe group explored options for securely managing customer discovery data outside traditional CRMs.\n\n- **Linnea introduced a current challenge: capturing and managing 30-minute customer discovery calls data efficiently** (40:51)  \n    - The US team collects structured info pre-briefing but lacks a dynamic, shared tool that integrates with CRM systems.  \n    - Salespeople often use Excel, but this creates data silos and lacks real-time updates, posing risks to accuracy.  \n    - Linnea sought suggestions for a secure, accessible system permitting controlled data entry and dynamic updates.  \n    - Roz ruled out Creative Cloud for this use, citing its design focus and lack of data management features.\n\n- **Potential platforms discussed included SharePoint, Confluence, Insight360, and Microsoft tools, each with limitations** (42:29)  \n    - Confluence is restricted to limited users, conflicting with the need for wide seller access.  \n    - Insight360, an internal customer engagement tool, currently lacks external or broader integration for this purpose.  \n    - Microsoft To Do and similar apps were considered but may not align with needs beyond task management.  \n    - Roz cautioned against Asana due to potential overload and lack of data governance controls.\n\n- **The team agreed further research is needed, with Natalie offering to assist in exploring suitable tools** (43:11)  \n    - Linnea emphasized urgency but stressed the solution should avoid portal stagnation and manual replacements.  \n    - Roz highlighted data security and access control as critical factors for selecting any platform.  \n    - The ongoing dialogue reflects a strategic focus on improving sales and customer data workflows to increase efficiency.  \n    - This initiative aims to support sales readiness and customer engagement quality without adding complexity.\n\n## **Process and File Management Improvements**\n\nFile transfer and collaboration processes are being optimized to reduce technical issues and improve efficiency.\n\n- **The current file transfer issues causing color shifts in marketing materials are attributed to Google platform glitches** (04:08)  \n    - Roz and Lou tested multiple export approaches, confirming the need to avoid Google Docs or Drive for final files.  \n    - Moving to a dedicated transfer folder with direct designer access aims to prevent file corruption and color skew.  \n    - Natalie will coordinate testing of files once Lou is added to the folder, targeting stable workflows.  \n    - Creative Cloud was identified as a possible alternative, pending further evaluation.\n\n- **Roz and Linnea highlighted internal file sharing practices favoring Teams and SharePoint for design collaboration** (40:20)  \n    - The team is open to adopting new tools if they reduce confusion and improve version control.  \n    - Roz’s preference for Microsoft environments reflects existing infrastructure alignment and user familiarity.  \n    - The focus is on minimizing friction points that delay approvals and cause repeated work.  \n    - Effective file management is seen as foundational to maintaining brand quality and accelerating deliverables.\n\n- **Efforts to integrate vector files for hero images across collateral will simplify asset reuse and reduce production time** (33:29)  \n    - The team encountered challenges with certain images (e.g., Info Print Manager) that delayed design progress.  \n    - Converting key images to vector format enables scaling without quality loss and supports diverse output formats.  \n    - This technical upgrade reflects a commitment to long-term efficiency and brand consistency.  \n    - Roz plans to leverage this capability to extend branding elements across multiple platforms and media.\n\n## **Team Collaboration and Support**\n\nThe meeting reinforced strong inter-team collaboration with shared responsibilities and resource planning.\n\n- **Roz expressed appreciation for the creative team’s work and encouraged continued support in editing and voiceover tasks** (16:34)  \n    - She welcomed offers to delegate polishing steps to alleviate workload for video and content finalization.  \n    - Linnea committed to planning and resource allocation to handle increasing content demands effectively.  \n    - Natalie offered professional podcast and voiceover services support, enhancing production quality.  \n    - This collaborative approach aims to sustain quality while scaling output efficiently.\n\n- **Linnea and Roz coordinated on upcoming deliverables and asset handoffs to maintain momentum** (39:24)  \n    - Key deliverables include updated videos, images, and brochures, shared through the new transfer folder system.  \n    - Roz will grant Lou access promptly to ensure smooth communication and file exchange.  \n    - The team agreed to monitor technical issues closely and pivot file sharing methods as needed.  \n    - Clear communication and accountability were emphasized to keep projects on track.\n\n- **Team members shared informal appreciation and morale boosters, reflecting a positive working culture** (46:18)  \n    - Linnea thanked Colin for branded swag, reinforcing team identity and motivation.  \n    - Roz encouraged open communication, inviting colleagues to reach out with questions or support needs.  \n    - The friendly tone and mutual respect support ongoing collaboration despite workload pressures.  \n    - This cultural strength underpins the team’s ability to adapt and deliver high-quality results.","outline":null,"keywords":["Process Director","LearnUpon","Video Production","File Transfer","Customer Training","VIP Event Graphics"],"overview":"- **Visual Assets Finalization:** Team is making minor adjustments to visuals for usability and brand consistency across templates.  \n- **Color Consistency Fixes:** New file-sharing approach will improve color integrity after glitches were traced to Google platforms.  \n- **Unified Sales Assets:** All sales materials will adopt a new look to improve usability and streamline messaging for the sales team.  \n- **Video Content Refresh:** Simplifying videos by removing on-screen text will enhance localization and reduce expenses across global markets.  \n- **Training Content Expansion:** Focus on customer-facing training with potential outsourcing options for voiceover recording to speed production.  \n- **Data Management Solutions:** Discussions ongoing to find a secure tool for managing customer discovery call data outside traditional CRMs.","action_items":"\n**Roz Regan**\nAdd Lou Bogani to the transfer folder to improve direct file sharing and solve color skew issues for brochure (05:00)\nContinue internal review and finalize the Process Director brochure content with Lisa and Linnea (06:00)\nSend Process Director battle card to the team to clean up template and content placement by next day (07:00)\nReview and finalize Optimizer video removing English text overlays, ensure voiceover and visuals support global usage (08:00)\nCheck and confirm font type (Frutiger) on video titles and coordinate slowing balloon transitions for better visibility (13:00)\nAwait updated Predictive Insight GUI from Miriam for video development (15:00)\nShare LearnUpon portal overview and discuss access options with Linnea and Natalie to explore editing support (23:00)\nFinalize admin workshop email banner and consider extending design across collateral using vector files (32:00)\nAssist in redesigning VIP event graphics for Latin America branding once original files are received (37:00)\nPrepare and share updated video, images, and brochure via new transfer folder and coordinate Creative Cloud fallback (39:00)\nCollaborate with Natalie and Linnea to explore feasible tools/platforms for customer discovery data sharing, avoiding spreadsheet chaos (40:00)\n\n**Linnea Wolken**\nProvide original VIP event graphics and agenda template to Roz for redesign (36:00)\nCoordinate follow-up with Roger and CEC team on Insight360 tool and CRM limitations related to customer discovery data entry (40:00)\nShare further details about customer and internal class training requirements and strategic alignment with marketing assets (18:00)\n\n**Nathalie Mintjens**\nAssist in uploading fixed brochure files to transfer folder and coordinate test uploads (06:00)\nSupport voiceover hiring and audio editing for internal training videos (32:00)\nConduct research on suitable platforms for locked-down customer data sharing (43:00)\n\n**Lou Bogani**\nAccept transfer folder access and download finalized brochure files (06:00)\nSupport design team with recoloring VIP event graphics (36:00)\n"},"migrated_from":"contract_meetings","original_id":"fd015750-d929-4d80-9ed9-d02f2859d417","master_marketer":{"status":"migrated"}}'::jsonb,
