ets (18:00)","completed":false},{"text":"Assist in uploading fixed brochure files to transfer folder and coordinate test uploads (06:00)","completed":false},{"text":"Support voiceover hiring and audio editing for internal training videos (32:00)","completed":false},{"text":"Conduct research on suitable platforms for locked-down customer data sharing (43:00)","completed":false},{"text":"Accept transfer folder access and download finalized brochure files (06:00)","completed":false},{"text":"Support design team with recoloring VIP event graphics (36:00)","completed":false}]'::jsonb,
