  '[{"text":"Review the updated IT services and consulting contact lists, suggest companies to exclude, and provide comments in Teams chat (09:18)","completed":false},{"text":"Review ABM email sequence and campaign plan documents for customer resonance and feedback over the weekend (10:39)","completed":false},{"text":"Review email content, ABM plan, and contact list materials, despite current health issues, aiming for feedback availability early next week (07:14)","completed":false},{"text":"Evaluate the inclusion of RFP messaging in campaigns based on potential client inquiries and internal readiness (18:44)","completed":false},{"text":"Share ad copy and design materials once finalized to support the campaign launch (20:30)","completed":false},{"text":"Monitor Wi-Fi and connection stability during meetings due to current hotel location (07:49)","completed":false},{"text":"Consolidate feedback from the team, update lists and email content accordingly for campaign readiness (09:23)","completed":false},{"text":"Coordinate translations of finalized email content into German for effective regional outreach (10:17)","completed":false},{"text":"Build landing page with options for prospect interest selection to gather insights on service focus areas (18:58)","completed":false}]'::jsonb,
